3061 /*members "\b", "\t", "\n", "\f", "\r", "\"", JSON, "\\", apply,
3062     charCodeAt, floor, getUTCDate, getUTCFullYear, getUTCHours,
3063     getUTCMinutes, getUTCMonth, getUTCSeconds, hasOwnProperty, join, length,
3064     parse, propertyIsEnumerable, prototype, push, replace, stringify, test,
3065     toJSON, toString
3066 */
3067 
3068 if (!this.JSON) {
3069 
3070     JSON = function () {
3071 
3072         function f(n) {    // Format integers to have at least two digits.
3073             return n < 10 ? '0' + n : n;
3074         }
3075 
3076         Date.prototype.toJSON = function () {
3077 
3078 // Eventually, this method will be based on the date.toISOString method.
3079 
3080             return this.getUTCFullYear()   + '-' +
3081                  f(this.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' +
3082                  f(this.getUTCDate())      + 'T' +
3083                  f(this.getUTCHours())     + ':' +
3084                  f(this.getUTCMinutes())   + ':' +
3085                  f(this.getUTCSeconds())   + 'Z';
3086         };
3087 
3088 
3089         var m = {    // table of character substitutions
3090             '\b': '\\b',
3091             '\t': '\\t',
3092             '\n': '\\n',
3093             '\f': '\\f',
3094             '\r': '\\r',
3095             '"' : '\\"',
3096             '\\': '\\\\'
3097         };
3098 
3099         function stringify(value, whitelist) {
3100             var a,          // The array holding the partial texts.
3101                 i,          // The loop counter.
3102                 k,          // The member key.
3103                 l,          // Length.
3104                 r = /["\\\x00-\x1f\x7f-\x9f]/g,
3105                 v;          // The member value.
3106 
3107             switch (typeof value) {
3108             case 'string':
3109 
3110 // If the string contains no control characters, no quote characters, and no
3111 // backslash characters, then we can safely slap some quotes around it.
3112 // Otherwise we must also replace the offending characters with safe sequences.
3113 
3114                 return r.test(value) ?
3115                     '"' + value.replace(r, function (a) {
3116                         var c = m[a];
3117                         if (c) {
3118                             return c;
3119                         }
3120                         c = a.charCodeAt();
3121                         return '\\u00' + Math.floor(c / 16).toString(16) +
3122                                                    (c % 16).toString(16);
3123                     }) + '"' :
3124                     '"' + value + '"';
3125 
3126             case 'number':
3127 
3128 // JSON numbers must be finite. Encode non-finite numbers as null.
3129 
3130                 return isFinite(value) ? String(value) : 'null';
3131 
3132             case 'boolean':
3133             case 'null':
3134                 return String(value);
3135 
3136             case 'object':
3137 
3138 // Due to a specification blunder in ECMAScript,
3139 // typeof null is 'object', so watch out for that case.
3140 
3141                 if (!value) {
3142                     return 'null';
3143                 }
3144 
3145 // If the object has a toJSON method, call it, and stringify the result.
3146 
3147                 if (typeof value.toJSON === 'function') {
3148                     return stringify(value.toJSON());
3149                 }
3150                 a = [];
3151                 if (typeof value.length === 'number' &&
3152                         !(value.propertyIsEnumerable('length'))) {
3153 
3154 // The object is an array. Stringify every element. Use null as a placeholder
3155 // for non-JSON values.
3156 
3157                     l = value.length;
3158                     for (i = 0; i < l; i += 1) {
3159                         a.push(stringify(value[i], whitelist) || 'null');
3160                     }
3161 
3162 // Join all of the elements together and wrap them in brackets.
3163 
3164                     return '[' + a.join(',') + ']';
3165                 }
3166                 if (whitelist) {
3167 
3168 // If a whitelist (array of keys) is provided, use it to select the components
3169 // of the object.
3170 
3171                     l = whitelist.length;
3172                     for (i = 0; i < l; i += 1) {
3173                         k = whitelist[i];
3174                         if (typeof k === 'string') {
3175                             v = stringify(value[k], whitelist);
3176                             if (v) {
3177                                 a.push(stringify(k) + ':' + v);
3178                             }
3179                         }
3180                     }
3181                 } else {
3182 
3183 // Otherwise, iterate through all of the keys in the object.
3184 
3185                     for (k in value) {
3186                         if (typeof k === 'string') {
3187                             v = stringify(value[k], whitelist);
3188                             if (v) {
3189                                 a.push(stringify(k) + ':' + v);
3190                             }
3191                         }
3192                     }
3193                 }
3194 
3195 // Join all of the member texts together and wrap them in braces.
3196 
3197                 return '{' + a.join(',') + '}';
3198             }
3199         }
3200 
3201         return {
3202             stringify: stringify,
3203             parse: function (text, filter) {
3204                 var j;
3205 
3206                 function walk(k, v) {
3207                     var i, n;
3208                     if (v && typeof v === 'object') {
3209                         for (i in v) {
3210                             if (Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.apply(v, [i])) {
3211                                 n = walk(i, v[i]);
3212                                 if (n !== undefined) {
3213                                     v[i] = n;
3214                                 }
3215                             }
3216                         }
3217                     }
3218                     return filter(k, v);
3219                 }
3220 
3221 
3222 // Parsing happens in three stages. In the first stage, we run the text against
3223 // regular expressions that look for non-JSON patterns. We are especially
3224 // concerned with '()' and 'new' because they can cause invocation, and '='
3225 // because it can cause mutation. But just to be safe, we want to reject all
3226 // unexpected forms.
3227 
3228 // We split the first stage into 4 regexp operations in order to work around
3229 // crippling inefficiencies in IE's and Safari's regexp engines. First we
3230 // replace all backslash pairs with '@' (a non-JSON character). Second, we
3231 // replace all simple value tokens with ']' characters. Third, we delete all
3232 // open brackets that follow a colon or comma or that begin the text. Finally,
3233 // we look to see that the remaining characters are only whitespace or ']' or
3234 // ',' or ':' or '{' or '}'. If that is so, then the text is safe for eval.
3235 
3236                 if (/^[\],:{}\s]*$/.test(text.replace(/\\./g, '@').
3237 replace(/"[^"\\\n\r]*"|true|false|null|-?\d+(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][+\-]?\d+)?/g, ']').
3238 replace(/(?:^|:|,)(?:\s*\[)+/g, ''))) {
3239 
3240 // In the second stage we use the eval function to compile the text into a
3241 // JavaScript structure. The '{' operator is subject to a syntactic ambiguity
3242 // in JavaScript: it can begin a block or an object literal. We wrap the text
3243 // in parens to eliminate the ambiguity.
3244 
3245                     j = eval('(' + text + ')');
3246 
3247 // In the optional third stage, we recursively walk the new structure, passing
3248 // each name/value pair to a filter function for possible transformation.
3249 
3250                     return typeof filter === 'function' ? walk('', j) : j;
3251                 }
3252 
3253 // If the text is not JSON parseable, then a SyntaxError is thrown.
3254 
3255                 throw new SyntaxError('parseJSON');
3256             }
3257         };
3258     }();
3259 }

3279 Date.prototype.dateFormat = function(format) {
3280     if (Date.formatFunctions[format] == null) {
3281         Date.createNewFormat(format);
3282     }
3283     var func = Date.formatFunctions[format];
3284     return this[func]();
3285 }
3286 
3287 Date.createNewFormat = function(format) {
3288     var funcName = "format" + Date.formatFunctions.count++;
3289     Date.formatFunctions[format] = funcName;
3290     var code = "Date.prototype." + funcName + " = function(){return ";
3291     var special = false;
3292     var ch = '';
3293     for (var i = 0; i < format.length; ++i) {
3294         ch = format.charAt(i);
3295         if (!special && ch == "\\") {
3296             special = true;
3297         }
3298         else if (special) {
3299             special = false;
3300             code += "'" + Date.escape(ch) + "' + ";
3301         }
3302         else {
3303             code += Date.getFormatCode(ch);
3304         }
3305     }
3306     eval(code.substring(0, code.length - 3) + ";}");
3307 }
3308 
3309 Date.getFormatCode = function(character) {
3310     switch (character) {
3311     case "d":
3312         return "Date.leftPad(this.getDate(), 2, '0') + ";
3313     case "D":
3314         return "Date.dayNames[this.getDay()].substring(0, 3) + ";
3315     case "j":
3316         return "this.getDate() + ";
3317     case "l":
3318         return "Date.dayNames[this.getDay()] + ";
3319     case "S":
3320         return "this.getSuffix() + ";
3321     case "w":
3322         return "this.getDay() + ";
3323     case "z":
3324         return "this.getDayOfYear() + ";
3325     case "W":
3326         return "this.getWeekOfYear() + ";
3327     case "F":
3328         return "Date.monthNames[this.getMonth()] + ";
3329     case "m":
3330         return "Date.leftPad(this.getMonth() + 1, 2, '0') + ";
3331     case "M":
3332         return "Date.monthNames[this.getMonth()].substring(0, 3) + ";
3333     case "n":
3334         return "(this.getMonth() + 1) + ";
3335     case "t":
3336         return "this.getDaysInMonth() + ";
3337     case "L":
3338         return "(this.isLeapYear() ? 1 : 0) + ";
3339     case "Y":
3340         return "this.getFullYear() + ";
3341     case "y":
3342         return "('' + this.getFullYear()).substring(2, 4) + ";
3343     case "a":
3344         return "(this.getHours() < 12 ? 'am' : 'pm') + ";
3345     case "A":
3346         return "(this.getHours() < 12 ? 'AM' : 'PM') + ";
3347     case "g":
3348         return "((this.getHours() %12) ? this.getHours() % 12 : 12) + ";
3349     case "G":
3350         return "this.getHours() + ";
3351     case "h":
3352         return "Date.leftPad((this.getHours() %12) ? this.getHours() % 12 : 12, 2, '0') + ";
3353     case "H":
3354         return "Date.leftPad(this.getHours(), 2, '0') + ";
3355     case "i":
3356         return "Date.leftPad(this.getMinutes(), 2, '0') + ";
3357     case "s":
3358         return "Date.leftPad(this.getSeconds(), 2, '0') + ";
3359     case "O":
3360         return "this.getGMTOffset() + ";
3361     case "T":
3362         return "this.getTimezone() + ";
3363     case "Z":
3364         return "(this.getTimezoneOffset() * -60) + ";
3365     default:
3366         return "'" + Date.escape(character) + "' + ";
3367     }
3368 }

3370 Date.parseDate = function(input, format) {
3371     if (Date.parseFunctions[format] == null) {
3372         Date.createParser(format);
3373     }
3374     var func = Date.parseFunctions[format];
3375     return Date[func](input);
3376 }
3377 
3378 Date.createParser = function(format) {
3379     var funcName = "parse" + Date.parseFunctions.count++;
3380     var regexNum = Date.parseRegexes.length;
3381     var currentGroup = 1;
3382     Date.parseFunctions[format] = funcName;
3383 
3384     var code = "Date." + funcName + " = function(input){\n"
3385         + "var y = -1, m = -1, d = -1, h = -1, i = -1, s = -1;\n"
3386         + "var d = new Date();\n"
3387         + "y = d.getFullYear();\n"
3388         + "m = d.getMonth();\n"
3389         + "d = d.getDate();\n"
3390         + "var results = input.match(Date.parseRegexes[" + regexNum + "]);\n"
3391         + "if (results && results.length > 0) {"
3392     var regex = "";
3393 
3394     var special = false;
3395     var ch = '';
3396     for (var i = 0; i < format.length; ++i) {
3397         ch = format.charAt(i);
3398         if (!special && ch == "\\") {
3399             special = true;
3400         }
3401         else if (special) {
3402             special = false;
3403             regex += Date.escape(ch);
3404         }
3405         else {
3406             var obj = Date.formatCodeToRegex(ch, currentGroup);
3407             currentGroup += obj.g;
3408             regex += obj.s;
3409             if (obj.g && obj.c) {
3410                 code += obj.c;
3411             }
3412         }
3413     }
3414 
3415     code += "if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0 && h >= 0 && i >= 0 && s >= 0)\n"
3416         + "{return new Date(y, m, d, h, i, s);}\n"
3417         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0 && h >= 0 && i >= 0)\n"
3418         + "{return new Date(y, m, d, h, i);}\n"
3419         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0 && h >= 0)\n"
3420         + "{return new Date(y, m, d, h);}\n"
3421         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0)\n"
3422         + "{return new Date(y, m, d);}\n"
3423         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0)\n"
3424         + "{return new Date(y, m);}\n"
3425         + "else if (y > 0)\n"
3426         + "{return new Date(y);}\n"
3427         + "}return null;}";
3428 
3429     Date.parseRegexes[regexNum] = new RegExp("^" + regex + "$");
3430     eval(code);
3431 }

3433 Date.formatCodeToRegex = function(character, currentGroup) {
3434     switch (character) {
3435     case "D":
3436         return {g:0,
3437         c:null,
3438         s:"(?:Sun|Mon|Tue|Wed|Thu|Fri|Sat)"};
3439     case "j":
3440     case "d":
3441         return {g:1,
3442             c:"d = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
3443             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
3444     case "l":
3445         return {g:0,
3446             c:null,
3447             s:"(?:" + Date.dayNames.join("|") + ")"};
3448     case "S":
3449         return {g:0,
3450             c:null,
3451             s:"(?:st|nd|rd|th)"};
3452     case "w":
3453         return {g:0,
3454             c:null,
3455             s:"\\d"};
3456     case "z":
3457         return {g:0,
3458             c:null,
3459             s:"(?:\\d{1,3})"};
3460     case "W":
3461         return {g:0,
3462             c:null,
3463             s:"(?:\\d{2})"};
3464     case "F":
3465         return {g:1,
3466             c:"m = parseInt(Date.monthNumbers[results[" + currentGroup + "].substring(0, 3)], 10);\n",
3467             s:"(" + Date.monthNames.join("|") + ")"};
3468     case "M":
3469         return {g:1,
3470             c:"m = parseInt(Date.monthNumbers[results[" + currentGroup + "]], 10);\n",
3471             s:"(Jan|Feb|Mar|Apr|May|Jun|Jul|Aug|Sep|Oct|Nov|Dec)"};
3472     case "n":
3473     case "m":
3474         return {g:1,
3475             c:"m = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10) - 1;\n",
3476             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
3477     case "t":
3478         return {g:0,
3479             c:null,
3480             s:"\\d{1,2}"};
3481     case "L":
3482         return {g:0,
3483             c:null,
3484             s:"(?:1|0)"};
3485     case "Y":
3486         return {g:1,
3487             c:"y = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
3488             s:"(\\d{4})"};
3489     case "y":
3490         return {g:1,
3491             c:"var ty = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n"
3492                 + "y = ty > Date.y2kYear ? 1900 + ty : 2000 + ty;\n",
3493             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
3494     case "a":
3495         return {g:1,
3496             c:"if (results[" + currentGroup + "] == 'am') {\n"
3497                 + "if (h == 12) { h = 0; }\n"
3498                 + "} else { if (h < 12) { h += 12; }}",
3499             s:"(am|pm)"};
3500     case "A":
3501         return {g:1,
3502             c:"if (results[" + currentGroup + "] == 'AM') {\n"
3503                 + "if (h == 12) { h = 0; }\n"
3504                 + "} else { if (h < 12) { h += 12; }}",
3505             s:"(AM|PM)"};
3506     case "g":
3507     case "G":
3508     case "h":
3509     case "H":
3510         return {g:1,
3511             c:"h = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
3512             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
3513     case "i":
3514         return {g:1,
3515             c:"i = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
3516             s:"(\\d{2})"};
3517     case "s":
3518         return {g:1,
3519             c:"s = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
3520             s:"(\\d{2})"};
3521     case "O":
3522         return {g:0,
3523             c:null,
3524             s:"[+-]\\d{4}"};
3525     case "T":
3526         return {g:0,
3527             c:null,
3528             s:"[A-Z]{3}"};
3529     case "Z":
3530         return {g:0,
3531             c:null,
3532             s:"[+-]\\d{1,5}"};
3533     default:
3534         return {g:0,
3535             c:null,
3536             s:Date.escape(character)};
3537     }
3538 }

3540 Date.prototype.getTimezone = function() {
3541     return this.toString().replace(
3542         /^.*? ([A-Z]{3}) [0-9]{4}.*$/, "$1").replace(
3543         /^.*?\(([A-Z])[a-z]+ ([A-Z])[a-z]+ ([A-Z])[a-z]+\)$/, "$1$2$3");
3544 }
3545 
3546 Date.prototype.getGMTOffset = function() {
3547     return (this.getTimezoneOffset() > 0 ? "-" : "+")
3548         + Date.leftPad(Math.floor(this.getTimezoneOffset() / 60), 2, "0")
3549         + Date.leftPad(this.getTimezoneOffset() % 60, 2, "0");
3550 }
3551 
3552 Date.prototype.getDayOfYear = function() {
3553     var num = 0;
3554     Date.daysInMonth[1] = this.isLeapYear() ? 29 : 28;
3555     for (var i = 0; i < this.getMonth(); ++i) {
3556         num += Date.daysInMonth[i];
3557     }
3558     return num + this.getDate() - 1;
3559 }
3560 
3561 Date.prototype.getWeekOfYear = function() {
3562     // Skip to Thursday of this week
3563     var now = this.getDayOfYear() + (5 - this.getDay());
3564     // Find the first Thursday of the year
3565     var jan1 = new Date(this.getFullYear(), 0, 1);
3566     var then = (5 - jan1.getDay());
3567     return parseInt(Date.leftPad(((now - then) / 7) + 1, 2, "0"));
3568 }
3569 
3570 Date.prototype.isLeapYear = function() {
3571     var year = this.getFullYear();
3572     return ((year & 3) == 0 && (year % 100 || (year % 400 == 0 && year)));
3573 }
3574 
3575 Date.prototype.getFirstDayOfMonth = function() {
3576     var day = (this.getDay() - (this.getDate() - 1)) % 7;
3577     return (day < 0) ? (day + 7) : day;
3578 }
3579 
3580 Date.prototype.getLastDayOfMonth = function() {
3581     var day = (this.getDay() + (Date.daysInMonth[this.getMonth()] - this.getDate())) % 7;
3582     return (day < 0) ? (day + 7) : day;
3583 }
3584 
3585 Date.prototype.getDaysInMonth = function() {
3586     Date.daysInMonth[1] = this.isLeapYear() ? 29 : 28;
3587     return Date.daysInMonth[this.getMonth()];
3588 }
3589 
3590 Date.prototype.getSuffix = function() {
3591     switch (this.getDate()) {
3592         case 1:
3593         case 21:
3594         case 31:
3595             return "st";
3596         case 2:
3597         case 22:
3598             return "nd";
3599         case 3:
3600         case 23:
3601             return "rd";
3602         default:
3603             return "th";
3604     }
3605 }
3606 
3607 Date.escape = function(string) {
3608     return string.replace(/('|\\)/g, "\\$1");
3609 }

3611 Date.leftPad = function (val, size, ch) {
3612     var result = new String(val);
3613     if (ch == null) {
3614         ch = " ";
3615     }
3616     while (result.length < size) {
3617         result = ch + result;
3618     }
3619     return result;
3620 }

3694 /** Get a widget by name */
3695 hui.ui.get = function(nameOrWidget) {
3696 	if (nameOrWidget) {
3697 		if (nameOrWidget.element) {
3698 			return nameOrWidget;
3699 		}
3700 		return hui.ui.objects[nameOrWidget];
3701 	}
3702 	return null;
3703 };

3705 hui.onReady(function() {
3706 	if (window.dwr && window.dwr.engine && window.dwr.engine.setErrorHandler) {
3707 		window.dwr.engine.setErrorHandler(function(msg,e) {
3708 			hui.log(msg);
3709 			hui.log(e);
3710 		});
3711 	}
3712 	hui.ui.callSuperDelegates(this,'ready');
3713 	hui.listen(window,'resize',hui.ui._resize);
3714 	hui.ui._resize();
3715 	hui.ui.domReady = true;
3716 	if (window.parent && window.parent.hui && window.parent.hui.ui) {
3717 		window.parent.hui.ui._frameLoaded(window);
3718 	}
3719 });

3722 	hui.ui.callSuperDelegates(this,'frameLoaded',win);
3723 }

3725 /** @private */
3726 hui.ui._resize = function() {
3727 	for (var i = hui.ui.layoutWidgets.length - 1; i >= 0; i--){
3728 		hui.ui.layoutWidgets[i]['$$layout']();
3729 	};
3730 }

3732 hui.ui.confirmOverlay = function(options) {
3733 	var node = options.element || options.widget.getElement(),
3734 		overlay;
3735 	if (hui.ui.confirmOverlays[node]) {
3736 		overlay = hui.ui.confirmOverlays[node];
3737 		overlay.clear();
3738 	} else {
3739 		overlay = hui.ui.Overlay.create({modal:true});
3740 		hui.ui.confirmOverlays[node] = overlay;
3741 	}
3742 	if (options.text) {
3743 		overlay.addText(options.text);
3744 	}
3745 	var ok = hui.ui.Button.create({text:options.okText || 'OK',highlighted:'true'});
3746 	ok.click(function() {
3747 		if (options.onOk) {
3748 			options.onOk();
3749 		}
3750 		overlay.hide();
3751 	});
3752 	overlay.add(ok);
3753 	var cancel = hui.ui.Button.create({text:options.cancelText || 'Cancel'});
3754 	cancel.onClick(function() {
3755 		overlay.hide();
3756 	});
3757 	overlay.add(cancel);
3758 	overlay.show({element:node});
3759 }

3761 hui.ui.destroy = function(widget) {

3766 hui.ui.destroyDescendants = function(element) {
3767 	var desc = hui.ui.getDescendants(element);
3768 	var objects = hui.ui.objects;
3769 	for (var i=0; i < desc.length; i++) {
3770 		var obj  = delete(objects[desc[i].name]);
3771 		if (!obj) {
3772 			hui.log('not found: '+desc[i].name);
3773 		}
3774 	};
3775 }

3777 /** Gets all ancestors of a widget
3778 	@param {Widget} A widget
3779 	@returns {Array} An array of all ancestors
3780 */
3781 hui.ui.getAncestors = function(widget) {
3782 	var desc = [];
3783 	var e = widget.element;
3784 	if (e) {
3785 		var a = hui.getAncestors(e);
3786 		var o = [];
3787 		for (var key in hui.ui.objects) {
3788 			o.push(hui.ui.objects[key]);
3789 		}
3790 		for (var i=0; i < a.length; i++) {
3791 			for (var j=0; j < o.length; j++) {
3792 				if (o[j].element==a[i]) {
3793 					desc.push(o[j]);
3794 				}
3795 			}
3796 		}
3797 	}
3798 	return desc;
3799 }
3800 
3801 hui.ui.getDescendants = function(widgetOrElement) {
3802 	var desc = [],e = widgetOrElement.getElement ? widgetOrElement.getElement() : widgetOrElement;
3803 	if (e) {
3804 		var d = e.getElementsByTagName('*');
3805 		var o = [];
3806 		for (var key in hui.ui.objects) {
3807 			o.push(hui.ui.objects[key]);
3808 		}
3809 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
3810 			for (var j=0; j < o.length; j++) {
3811 				if (d[i]==o[j].element) {
3812 					desc.push(o[j]);
3813 				}
3814 			};
3815 			
3816 		};
3817 	}
3818 	return desc;
3819 }
3820 
3821 hui.ui.getAncestor = function(widget,cls) {
3822 	var a = hui.ui.getAncestors(widget);
3823 	for (var i=0; i < a.length; i++) {
3824 		if (hui.hasClass(a[i].getElement(),cls)) {
3825 			return a[i];
3826 		}
3827 	};
3828 	return null;
3829 }

3833 hui.ui.changeState = function(state) {
3834 	if (hui.ui.state===state) {return;}
3835 	var all = hui.ui.objects,
3836 		key,obj;
3837 	for (key in all) {
3838 		obj = all[key];
3839 		if (obj.options && obj.options.state) {
3840 			if (obj.options.state==state) {
3841 				obj.show();
3842 			} else {
3843 				obj.hide();
3844 			}
3845 		}
3846 	}
3847 	hui.ui.state=state;
3848 }

3874 hui.ui.showCurtain = function(options,zIndex) {

3881 			}
3882 		};

3884 		if (!body) {
3885 			body=document.body;
3886 		}
3887 		body.appendChild(widget.curtain);
3888 	}
3889 	if (options.color) {
3890 		widget.curtain.style.backgroundColor=options.color;
3891 	}
3892 	if (hui.browser.msie) {
3893 		widget.curtain.style.height=hui.getDocumentHeight()+'px';
3894 	} else {

3896 		widget.curtain.style.top='0';

3899 		widget.curtain.style.right='0';
3900 	}
3901 	widget.curtain.style.zIndex=options.zIndex;
3902 	hui.setOpacity(widget.curtain,0);
3903 	widget.curtain.style.display='block';
3904 	hui.ani(widget.curtain,'opacity',0.7,1000,{ease:hui.ease.slowFastSlow});

3915 hui.ui.confirm = function(options) {
3916 	if (!options.name) {
3917 		options.name = 'huiConfirm';
3918 	}
3919 	var alert = hui.ui.get(options.name);
3920 	var ok;
3921 	if (!alert) {
3922 		alert = hui.ui.Alert.create(options);
3923 		var cancel = hui.ui.Button.create({name:name+'_cancel',text : options.cancel || 'Cancel',highlighted:options.highlighted==='cancel'});
3924 		cancel.listen({$click:function(){
3925 			alert.hide();
3926 			if (options.onCancel) {
3927 				options.onCancel();
3928 			}
3929 			hui.ui.callDelegates(alert,'cancel');
3930 		}});
3931 		alert.addButton(cancel);
3932 	
3933 		ok = hui.ui.Button.create({name:name+'_ok',text : options.ok || 'OK',highlighted:options.highlighted==='ok'});
3934 		alert.addButton(ok);
3935 	} else {
3936 		alert.update(options);
3937 		ok = hui.ui.get(name+'_ok');
3938 		ok.setText(options.ok || 'OK');
3939 		ok.setHighlighted(options.highlighted=='ok');
3940 		ok.clearDelegates();
3941 		hui.ui.get(name+'_cancel').setText(options.ok || 'Cancel');
3942 		hui.ui.get(name+'_cancel').setHighlighted(options.highlighted=='cancel');
3943 		if (options.cancel) {hui.ui.get(name+'_cancel').setText(options.cancel);}
3944 	}
3945 	ok.listen({$click:function(){
3946 		alert.hide();
3947 		if (options.onOK) {
3948 			options.onOK();
3949 		}
3950 		hui.ui.callDelegates(alert,'ok');
3951 	}});
3952 	alert.show();
3953 }
3954 
3955 hui.ui.alert = function(options) {
3956 	if (!this.alertBox) {
3957 		this.alertBox = hui.ui.Alert.create(options);
3958 		this.alertBoxButton = hui.ui.Button.create({name:'huiAlertBoxButton',text : 'OK'});
3959 		this.alertBoxButton.listen({
3960 			$click$huiAlertBoxButton : function() {
3961 				hui.ui.alertBox.hide();
3962 				if (hui.ui.alertBoxCallBack) {
3963 					hui.ui.alertBoxCallBack();
3964 					hui.ui.alertBoxCallBack = null;
3965 				}
3966 			}
3967 		});
3968 		this.alertBox.addButton(this.alertBoxButton);
3969 	} else {
3970 		this.alertBox.update(options);
3971 	}
3972 	this.alertBoxCallBack = options.onOK;
3973 	this.alertBoxButton.setText(options.button ? options.button : 'OK');
3974 	this.alertBox.show();
3975 };

3977 hui.ui.showMessage = function(options) {
3978 	if (typeof(options)=='string') {
3979 		// TODO: Backwards compatibility
3980 		options={text:options};
3981 	}
3982 	if (options.delay) {
3983 		hui.ui.messageDelayTimer = window.setTimeout(function() {
3984 			options.delay=null;
3985 			hui.ui.showMessage(options);
3986 		},options.delay);
3987 		return;
3988 	}
3989 	window.clearTimeout(hui.ui.messageDelayTimer);
3990 	if (!hui.ui.message) {
3991 		hui.ui.message = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_message',html:'<div><div></div></div>'});
3992 		if (!hui.browser.msie) {
3993 			hui.setOpacity(hui.ui.message,0);
3994 		}
3995 		document.body.appendChild(hui.ui.message);
3996 	}
3997 	var inner = hui.ui.message.getElementsByTagName('div')[1];
3998 	if (options.icon) {
3999 		hui.dom.clear(inner);
4000 		inner.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(options.icon,24));
4001 		hui.dom.addText(inner,options.text);
4002 	}
4003 	else if (options.busy) {
4004 		inner.innerHTML='<span class="hui_message_busy"></span>';
4005 		hui.dom.addText(inner,options.text);
4006 	} else {
4007 		hui.dom.setText(inner,options.text);
4008 	}
4009 	hui.ui.message.style.display = 'block';
4010 	hui.ui.message.style.zIndex = hui.ui.nextTopIndex();
4011 	hui.ui.message.style.marginLeft = (hui.ui.message.clientWidth/-2)+'px';
4012 	hui.ui.message.style.marginTop = hui.getScrollTop()+'px';
4013 	if (hui.browser.opacity) {
4014 		hui.ani(hui.ui.message,'opacity',1,300);
4015 	}
4016 	window.clearTimeout(hui.ui.messageTimer);
4017 	if (options.duration) {
4018 		hui.ui.messageTimer = window.setTimeout(hui.ui.hideMessage,options.duration);
4019 	}
4020 };
4021 
4022 hui.ui.hideMessage = function() {
4023 	window.clearTimeout(hui.ui.messageDelayTimer);
4024 	if (hui.ui.message) {
4025 		if (hui.browser.opacity) {
4026 			hui.ani(hui.ui.message,'opacity',0,300,{hideOnComplete:true});
4027 		} else {
4028 			hui.ui.message.style.display='none';
4029 		}
4030 	}
4031 };

4033 hui.ui.showToolTip = function(options) {
4034 	var key = options.key || 'common';
4035 	var t = hui.ui.toolTips[key];
4036 	if (!t) {
4037 		t = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_tooltip',style:'display:none;',html:'<div><div></div></div>',parent:document.body});
4038 		hui.ui.toolTips[key] = t;
4039 	}
4040 	t.onclick = function() {hui.ui.hideToolTip(options);};
4041 	var n = hui.get(options.element);
4042 	var pos = hui.getPosition(n);
4043 	hui.dom.setText(t.getElementsByTagName('div')[1],options.text);
4044 	if (t.style.display=='none' && hui.browser.opacity) {
4045 		hui.setOpacity(t,0);
4046 	}
4047 	hui.setStyle(t,{'display':'block',zIndex:hui.ui.nextTopIndex()});
4048 	hui.setStyle(t,{left:(pos.left-t.clientWidth+4)+'px',top:(pos.top+2-(t.clientHeight/2)+(n.clientHeight/2))+'px'});
4049 	if (hui.browser.opacity) {
4050 		hui.ani(t,'opacity',1,300);
4051 	}
4052 };

4059 			hui.ani(t,'opacity',0,300,{hideOnComplete:true});
4060 		} else {
4061 			hui.style.display = 'none';
4062 		}
4063 	}
4064 };

4077 hui.ui.isWithin = function(e,element) {
4078 	e = new hui.Event(e);
4079 	var offset = {left:hui.getLeft(element),top:hui.getTop(element)};
4080 	var dims = {width:element.clientWidth,height:element.clientHeight};
4081 	return e.left()>offset.left && e.left()<offset.left+dims.width && e.top()>offset.top && e.top()<offset.top+dims.height;
4082 };

4127 hui.ui.NumberValidator = function(options) {
4128 	hui.override({allowNull:false,min:0,max:10},options)
4129 	this.min = options.min;
4130 	this.max = options.max;
4131 	this.allowNull = options.allowNull;
4132 	this.middle = Math.max(Math.min(this.max,0),this.min);
4133 }
4134 
4135 hui.ui.NumberValidator.prototype = {
4136 	validate : function(value) {
4137 		if (hui.isBlank(value) && this.allowNull) {
4138 			return {valid:true,value:null};
4139 		}
4140 		var number = parseFloat(value);
4141 		if (isNaN(number)) {
4142 			return {valid:false,value:this.middle};
4143 		} else if (number<this.min) {
4144 			return {valid:false,value:this.min};
4145 		} else if (number>this.max) {
4146 			return {valid:false,value:this.max};
4147 		}
4148 		return {valid:true,value:number};
4149 	}
4150 }

4154 hui.ui.fadeIn = function(node,time) {
4155 	if (hui.getStyle(node,'display')=='none') {
4156 		hui.setStyle(node,{opacity:0,display:''});
4157 	}
4158 	hui.animate(node,'opacity',1,time);
4159 };
4160 
4161 hui.ui.fadeOut = function(node,time) {
4162 	hui.animate(node,'opacity',0,time,{hideOnComplete:true});
4163 };

4165 hui.ui.bounceIn = function(node,time) {
4166 	if (hui.browser.msie) {
4167 		hui.setStyle(node,{'display':'block',visibility:'visible'});
4168 	} else {
4169 		hui.setStyle(node,{'display':'block','opacity':0,visibility:'visible'});
4170 		hui.animate(node,'transform','scale(0.1)',0);// rotate(10deg)
4171 		window.setTimeout(function() {
4172 			hui.animate(node,'opacity',1,300);
4173 			hui.animate(node,'transform','scale(1)',400,{ease:hui.ease.backOut}); // rotate(0deg)
4174 		});
4175 	}
4176 };

4178 //////////////////////////// Positioning /////////////////////////////
4179 
4180 hui.ui.positionAtElement = function(element,target,options) {
4181 	options = options || {};
4182 	element = hui.get(element);
4183 	target = hui.get(target);
4184 	var origDisplay = hui.getStyle(element,'display');
4185 	if (origDisplay=='none') {
4186 		hui.setStyle(element,{'visibility':'hidden','display':'block'});
4187 	}
4188 	var left = hui.getLeft(target),
4189 		top = hui.getTop(target);
4190 	var vert=options.vertical || null;
4191 	if (options.horizontal && options.horizontal=='right') {
4192 		left = left+target.clientWidth-element.clientWidth;
4193 	}
4194 	if (vert=='topOutside') {
4195 		top = top-element.clientHeight;
4196 	} else if (vert=='bottomOutside') {
4197 		top = top+target.clientHeight;
4198 	}
4199 	left+=(options.left || 0);
4200 	top+=(options.top || 0);
4201 	hui.setStyle(element,{'left':left+'px','top':top+'px'});
4202 	if (origDisplay=='none') {
4203 		hui.setStyle(element,{'visibility':'visible','display':'none'});
4204 	}
4205 };

4207 hui.ui.getTextAreaHeight = function(input) {
4208 	var t = this.textAreaDummy;
4209 	if (!t) {
4210 		t = this.textAreaDummy = document.createElement('div');
4211 		t.className='hui_textarea_dummy';
4212 		document.body.appendChild(t);
4213 	}
4214 	var html = input.value;
4215 	if (html[html.length-1]==='\n') {
4216 		html+='x';
4217 	}
4218 	html = hui.escape(html).replace(/\n/g,'<br/>');
4219 	t.innerHTML = html;
4220 	t.style.width=(input.clientWidth)+'px';
4221 	return t.clientHeight;
4222 }

4224 //////////////////// Delegating ////////////////////
4225 
4226 hui.ui.extend = function(obj,options) {
4227 	if (!obj.name) {
4228 		hui.ui.latestObjectIndex++;
4229 		obj.name = 'unnamed'+hui.ui.latestObjectIndex;
4230 	}
4231 	if (options!==undefined) {
4232 		if (obj.options) {
4233 			obj.options = hui.override(obj.options,options);
4234 		}
4235 		obj.element = hui.get(options.element);
4236 		obj.name = options.name;
4237 	}
4238 	hui.ui.objects[obj.name] = obj;
4239 	obj.delegates = [];
4240 	obj.listen = function(delegate) {
4241 		hui.addToArray(this.delegates,delegate);
4242 		return this;
4243 	}
4244 	obj.removeDelegate = function(delegate) {
4245 		hui.removeFromArray(this.delegates,delegate);
4246 	}
4247 	obj.clearDelegates = function() {
4248 		this.delegates = [];
4249 	}
4250 	obj.fire = function(method,value,event) {
4251 		hui.ui.callDelegates(this,method,value,event);
4252 	}
4253 	obj.fireProperty = function(key,value) {
4254 		hui.ui.firePropertyChange(this,key,value);
4255 	}
4256 	if (!obj.getElement) {
4257 		obj.getElement = function() {
4258 			return this.element;
4259 		}
4260 	}
4261 	if (!obj.valueForProperty) {
4262 		obj.valueForProperty = function(p) {return this[p]};
4263 	}
4264 	if (obj['$$layout']) {
4265 		hui.ui.layoutWidgets.push(obj);
4266 	}
4267 };
4268 
4269 hui.ui.callDelegatesDrop = function(dragged,dropped) {
4270 	for (var i=0; i < hui.ui.delegates.length; i++) {
4271 		if (hui.ui.delegates[i]['$drop$'+dragged.kind+'$'+dropped.kind]) {
4272 			hui.ui.delegates[i]['$drop$'+dragged.kind+'$'+dropped.kind](dragged,dropped);
4273 		}
4274 	}
4275 };

4277 hui.ui.callAncestors = function(obj,method,value,event) {
4278 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
4279 	var d = hui.ui.getAncestors(obj);
4280 	for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
4281 		if (d[i][method]) {
4282 			d[i][method](value,event);
4283 		}
4284 	};
4285 };
4286 
4287 hui.ui.callDescendants = function(obj,method,value,event) {
4288 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') {
4289 		value=obj;
4290 	}
4291 	if (!method[0]=='$') {
4292 		method = '$'+method;
4293 	}
4294 	var d = hui.ui.getDescendants(obj);
4295 	for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
4296 		if (d[i][method]) {
4297 			thisResult = d[i][method](value,event);
4298 		}
4299 	};
4300 };

4302 hui.ui.callVisible = function(widget) {
4303 	hui.ui.callDescendants(widget,'$visibilityChanged');
4304 }

4306 hui.ui.listen = function(delegate) {
4307 	hui.ui.delegates.push(delegate);

4310 hui.ui.callDelegates = function(obj,method,value,event) {
4311 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') {
4312 		value=obj;
4313 	}
4314 	var result = null;
4315 	if (obj.delegates) {
4316 		for (var i=0; i < obj.delegates.length; i++) {
4317 			var delegate = obj.delegates[i];
4318 			var thisResult = null;
4319 			if (obj.name && delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name]) {
4320 				thisResult = delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name](value,event);
4321 			} else if (delegate['$'+method]) {
4322 				thisResult = delegate['$'+method](value,event);
4323 			}
4324 			if (result==null && thisResult!=null && typeof(thisResult)!='undefined') {
4325 				result = thisResult;
4326 			}
4327 		};
4328 	}
4329 	var superResult = hui.ui.callSuperDelegates(obj,method,value,event);
4330 	if (result==null && superResult!=null) {
4331 		result = superResult;
4332 	}
4333 	return result;
4334 };
4335 
4336 hui.ui.callSuperDelegates = function(obj,method,value,event) {
4337 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
4338 	var result = null;
4339 	for (var i=0; i < hui.ui.delegates.length; i++) {
4340 		var delegate = hui.ui.delegates[i];
4341 		var thisResult = null;
4342 		if (obj.name && delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name]) {
4343 			thisResult = delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name](value,event);
4344 		} else if (delegate['$'+method]) {
4345 			thisResult = delegate['$'+method](value,event);
4346 		}
4347 		if (result==null && thisResult!=null && typeof(thisResult)!='undefined') {
4348 			result = thisResult;
4349 		}
4350 	};
4351 	return result;
4352 };
4353 
4354 hui.ui.resolveImageUrl = function(widget,img,width,height) {
4355 	for (var i=0; i < widget.delegates.length; i++) {
4356 		if (widget.delegates[i].$resolveImageUrl) {
4357 			return widget.delegates[i].$resolveImageUrl(img,width,height);
4358 		}
4359 	};
4360 	for (var j=0; j < hui.ui.delegates.length; j++) {
4361 		var delegate = hui.ui.delegates[j];
4362 		if (delegate.$resolveImageUrl) {
4363 			return delegate.$resolveImageUrl(img,width,height);
4364 		}
4365 	}
4366 	return null;
4367 };

4371 hui.ui.firePropertyChange = function(obj,name,value) {
4372 	hui.ui.callDelegates(obj,'propertyChanged',{property:name,value:value});

4375 hui.ui.bind = function(expression,delegate) {
4376 	if (expression.charAt(0)=='@') {
4377 		var pair = expression.substring(1).split('.');
4378 		var obj = hui.ui.get(pair[0]);
4379 		if (!obj) {
4380 			hui.log('Unable to bind to '+expression);
4381 			return;
4382 		}
4383 		var p = pair.slice(1).join('.');
4384 		obj.listen({
4385 			$propertyChanged : function(prop) {
4386 				if (prop.property==p) {
4387 					delegate(prop.value);
4388 				}
4389 			}
4390 		});
4391 		return obj.valueForProperty(p);
4392 	}
4393 	return expression;
4394 };

4398 hui.ui.request = function(options) {
4399 	options = hui.override({method:'post',parameters:{}},options);
4400 	if (options.json) {
4401 		for (var key in options.json) {
4402 			options.parameters[key]=hui.toJSON(options.json[key]);
4403 		}
4404 	}
4405 	var onSuccess = options.onSuccess;
4406 	var message = options.message;
4407 	options.onSuccess=function(t) {
4408 		if (message) {
4409 			if (message.success) {
4410 				hui.ui.showMessage({text:message.success,icon:'common/success',duration:message.duration || 2000});
4411 			} else if (message.start) {
4412 				hui.ui.hideMessage();
4413 			}
4414 		}
4415 		var str,json;
4416 		if (typeof(onSuccess)=='string') {
4417 			if (!hui.request.isXMLResponse(t)) {
4418 				str = t.responseText.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, '');
4419 				if (str.length>0) {
4420 					json = hui.fromJSON(t.responseText);
4421 				} else {
4422 					json = '';
4423 				}
4424 				hui.ui.callDelegates(json,'success$'+onSuccess);
4425 			} else {
4426 				hui.ui.callDelegates(t,'success$'+onSuccess);
4427 			}
4428 		} else if (hui.request.isXMLResponse(t) && options.onXML) {
4429 			options.onXML(t.responseXML);
4430 		} else if (options.onJSON) {
4431 			str = t.responseText.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, '');
4432 			if (str.length>0) {
4433 				json = hui.fromJSON(t.responseText);
4434 			} else {
4435 				json = null;
4436 			}
4437 			options.onJSON(json);
4438 		} else if (typeof(onSuccess)=='function') {
4439 			onSuccess(t);
4440 		} else if (options.onText) {
4441 			options.onText(t.responseText);
4442 		}
4443 	};
4444 	var onFailure = options.onFailure;
4445 	options.onFailure = function(t) {
4446 		if (typeof(onFailure)=='string') {
4447 			hui.ui.callDelegates(t,'failure$'+onFailure)
4448 		} else if (typeof(onFailure)=='function') {
4449 			onFailure(t);
4450 		}
4451 	}
4452 	options.onException = function(t,e) {
4453 		hui.log(t);
4454 		hui.log(e);
4455 	};
4456 	if (options.message && options.message.start) {
4457 		hui.ui.showMessage({text:options.message.start,busy:true,delay:options.message.delay});
4458 	}
4459 	hui.request(options);
4460 };

4462 hui.ui.parseItems = function(doc) {
4463 	var root = doc.documentElement;
4464 	var out = [];
4465 	hui.ui.parseSubItems(root,out);
4466 	return out;

4469 hui.ui.parseSubItems = function(parent,array) {
4470 	var children = parent.childNodes;
4471 	for (var i=0; i < children.length; i++) {
4472 		var node = children[i];
4473 		if (node.nodeType==1 && node.nodeName=='title') {
4474 			array.push({title:node.getAttribute('title'),type:'title'})
4475 		} else if (node.nodeType==1 && node.nodeName=='item') {
4476 			var sub = [];
4477 			hui.ui.parseSubItems(node,sub);
4478 			array.push({
4479 				title:node.getAttribute('title'),
4480 				value:node.getAttribute('value'),
4481 				icon:node.getAttribute('icon'),
4482 				kind:node.getAttribute('kind'),
4483 				badge:node.getAttribute('badge'),
4484 				children:sub
4485 			});
4486 		}
4487 	};
4488 }

4514  */
4515 hui.ui.Source = function(options) {
4516 	this.options = hui.override({url:null,dwr:null,parameters:[],lazy:false},options);
4517 	this.name = options.name;
4518 	this.data = null;
4519 	this.parameters = this.options.parameters;
4520 	hui.ui.extend(this);
4521 	if (options.delegate) {
4522 		this.listen(options.delegate);
4523 	}
4524 	this.busy=false;
4525 	hui.ui.onReady(this.init.bind(this));
4526 };
4527 
4528 hui.ui.Source.prototype = {
4529 	/** @private */
4530 	init : function() {
4531 		var self = this;
4532 		hui.each(this.parameters,function(parm) {
4533 			var val = hui.ui.bind(parm.value,function(value) {
4534 				self.changeParameter(parm.key,value);
4535 			});
4536 			parm.value = self.convertValue(val);
4537 		});
4538 		if (!this.options.lazy) {
4539 			this.refresh();
4540 		}
4541 	},
4542 	/** @private */
4543 	convertValue : function(value) {		
4544 		if (value && value.getTime) {
4545 			return value.getTime();
4546 		}
4547 		return value;
4548 	},
4549 	/** Refreshes the data source */
4550 	refresh : function() {
4551 		if (this.delegates.length==0) {
4552 			return;
4553 		}
4554 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
4555 			var d = this.delegates[i];
4556 			if (d['$sourceShouldRefresh'] && d['$sourceShouldRefresh']()==false) {
4557 				return;
4558 			}
4559 		};
4560 		if (this.busy) {
4561 			this.pendingRefresh = true;
4562 			return;
4563 		}
4564 		this.pendingRefresh = false;
4565 		var self = this;
4566 		if (this.options.url) {
4567 			var prms = {};
4568 			for (var j=0; j < this.parameters.length; j++) {
4569 				var p = this.parameters[j];
4570 				prms[p.key] = p.value;
4571 			};
4572 			this.busy=true;
4573 			hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsBusy');
4574 			hui.request({
4575 				method:'post',
4576 				url:this.options.url,
4577 				parameters:prms,
4578 				onSuccess : function(t) {self.parse(t)},
4579 				onException : function(e,t) {
4580 					hui.log('Exception while loading source...')
4581 					hui.log(e)
4582 				},
4583 				onFailure : function(t) {
4584 					hui.ui.callDelegates(self,'sourceFailed');
4585 				}
4586 			});
4587 		} else if (this.options.dwr) {
4588 			var pair = this.options.dwr.split('.');
4589 			var facade = eval(pair[0]);
4590 			var method = pair[1];
4591 			var args = facade[method].argumentNames();
4592 			for (var k=0; k < args.length; k++) {
4593 				if (this.parameters[k]) {
4594 					args[k]=this.parameters[k].value===undefined ? null : this.parameters[k].value;
4595 				}
4596 			};
4597 			args[args.length-1]=function(r) {self.parseDWR(r)};
4598 			this.busy=true;
4599 			hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsBusy');
4600 			facade[method].apply(facade,args);
4601 		}
4602 	},
4603 	/** @private */
4604 	end : function() {
4605 		this.busy=false;
4606 		if (this.pendingRefresh) {
4607 			this.refresh();
4608 		} else {
4609 			hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsNotBusy');
4610 		}
4611 	},
4612 	/** @private */
4613 	parse : function(t) {
4614 		if (t.responseXML && t.responseXML.documentElement && t.responseXML.documentElement.nodeName!='parsererror') {
4615 			this.parseXML(t.responseXML);
4616 		} else {
4617 			var str = t.responseText.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, ''),
4618 				json = null;
4619 			if (str.length>0) {
4620 				json = hui.fromJSON(t.responseText);
4621 			}
4622 			this.fire('objectsLoaded',json);
4623 		}
4624 		this.end();
4625 	},
4626 	/** @private */
4627 	parseXML : function(doc) {
4628 		if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='items') {
4629 			this.data = hui.ui.parseItems(doc);
4630 			this.fire('itemsLoaded',this.data);
4631 		} else if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='list') {
4632 			this.fire('listLoaded',doc);
4633 		} else if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='articles') {
4634 			this.fire('articlesLoaded',doc);
4635 		}
4636 	},
4637 	/** @private */
4638 	parseDWR : function(data) {
4639 		this.data = data;
4640 		this.fire('objectsLoaded',data);
4641 		this.end();
4642 	},
4643 	addParameter : function(parm) {
4644 		//hui.log(parm.value);
4645 		this.parameters.push(parm);
4646 	},
4647 	changeParameter : function(key,value) {
4648 		value = this.convertValue(value);
4649 		for (var i=0; i < this.parameters.length; i++) {
4650 			var p = this.parameters[i]
4651 			if (p.key==key) {
4652 				p.value=value;
4653 			}
4654 		};
4655 		window.clearTimeout(this.paramDelay);
4656 		this.paramDelay = window.setTimeout(function() {
4657 			this.refresh();
4658 		}.bind(this),100)
4659 	}
4660 }

4670 hui.ui.startDrag = function(e,element,options) {
4671 	e = new hui.Event(e);
4672 	var info = element.dragDropInfo;
4673 	hui.ui.dropTypes = hui.ui.findDropTypes(info);
4674 	if (!hui.ui.dropTypes) return;
4675 	var proxy = hui.ui.getDragProxy();
4676 	hui.listen(document.body,'mousemove',hui.ui.dragListener);
4677 	hui.listen(document.body,'mouseup',hui.ui.dragEndListener);
4678 	hui.ui.dragInfo = info;
4679 	if (info.icon) {
4680 		proxy.style.backgroundImage = 'url('+hui.ui.getIconUrl(info.icon,1)+')';
4681 	}
4682 	hui.ui.startDragPos = {top:e.top(),left:e.left()};
4683 	proxy.innerHTML = info.title ? '<span>'+hui.escape(info.title)+'</span>' : '###';
4684 	hui.ui.dragging = true;
4685 	document.body.onselectstart = function () { return false; };
4686 };

4688 hui.ui.findDropTypes = function(drag) {
4689 	var gui = hui.ui;
4690 	var drops = null;
4691 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
4692 		if (gui.delegates[i].dragDrop) {
4693 			for (var j=0; j < gui.delegates[i].dragDrop.length; j++) {
4694 				var rule = gui.delegates[i].dragDrop[j];
4695 				if (rule.drag==drag.kind) {
4696 					if (drops==null) drops={};
4697 					drops[rule.drop] = {};
4698 				}
4699 			};
4700 		}
4701 	}
4702 	return drops;
4703 };

4705 hui.ui.dragListener = function(e) {
4706 	e = new hui.Event(e);
4707 	hui.ui.dragProxy.style.left = (e.left()+10)+'px';
4708 	hui.ui.dragProxy.style.top = e.top()+'px';
4709 	hui.ui.dragProxy.style.display='block';
4710 	var target = hui.ui.findDropTarget(e.getElement());
4711 	if (target && hui.ui.dropTypes[target.dragDropInfo['kind']]) {
4712 		if (hui.ui.latestDropTarget) {
4713 			hui.removeClass(hui.ui.latestDropTarget,'hui_drop');
4714 		}
4715 		hui.addClass(target,'hui_drop');
4716 		hui.ui.latestDropTarget = target;
4717 	} else if (hui.ui.latestDropTarget) {
4718 		hui.removeClass(hui.ui.latestDropTarget,'hui_drop');
4719 		hui.ui.latestDropTarget = null;
4720 	}
4721 	return false;
4722 };

4728 		}

4730 	}
4731 	return null;

4741 		hui.ui.dragProxy.style.display='none';
4742 	} else {

4744 		hui.animate(hui.ui.dragProxy,'top',(hui.ui.startDragPos.top-5)+'px',200,{ease:hui.ease.fastSlow,hideOnComplete:true});

4810 		this.titlebar.onmousedown = function(e) {self.startDrag(e);return false;};
4811 		hui.listen(this.element,'mousedown',function() {
4812 			self.element.style.zIndex=hui.ui.nextPanelIndex();
4813 		});
4814 	},
4815 	setTitle : function(title) {
4816 		hui.dom.setText(this.title,title);
4817 	},
4818 	show : function(options) {
4819 		if (this.visible) {return}
4820 		options = options || {};
4821 		hui.setStyle(this.element,{
4822 			zIndex : hui.ui.nextPanelIndex(), visibility : 'hidden', display : 'block'
4823 		})
4824 		var width = this.element.clientWidth;
4825 		hui.setStyle(this.element,{
4826 			width : width+'px' , visibility : 'visible'
4827 		});
4828 		if (options.avoid) {
4829 			hui.place({insideViewPort : true, target : {element : options.avoid, vertical : .5, horizontal : 1}, source : {element : this.element, vertical : .5, horizontal : 0} });
4830 		} else {
4831 			if (!this.element.style.top) {
4832 				this.element.style.top = (hui.getScrollTop()+40)+'px';
4833 			}
4834 			if (!this.element.style.left) {
4835 				this.element.style.left = Math.round((hui.getViewPortWidth()-width)/2)+'px';
4836 			}			
4837 		}
4838 		if (hui.browser.opacity) {
4839 			hui.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,0);
4840 		}
4841 		this.visible = true;
4842 		hui.ui.callVisible(this);
4843 	},
4844 	toggle : function() {
4845 		(this.visible ? this.hide() : this.show() );
4846 	},
4847 	hide : function() {
4848 		if (!this.visible) return;
4849 		if (hui.browser.opacity) {
4850 			hui.ani(this.element,'opacity',0,200,{hideOnComplete:true});
4851 		} else {
4852 			this.element.style.display='none';
4853 		}
4854 		this.visible = false;
4855 	},
4856 	add : function(widgetOrNode) {
4857 		if (widgetOrNode.getElement) {
4858 			this.content.appendChild(widgetOrNode.getElement());
4859 		} else {
4860 			this.content.appendChild(widgetOrNode);
4861 		}
4862 	},
4863 	addToBack : function(widgetOrNode) {
4864 		if (!this.back) {
4865 			this.back = hui.build('div',{className:'hui_window_back'});
4866 			this.element.insertBefore(this.back,this.front);
4867 			hui.effect.makeFlippable({container:this.element,front:this.front,back:this.back});
4868 		}
4869 		this.back.appendChild(hui.ui.getElement(widgetOrNode));
4870 	},
4871 	setVariant : function(variant) {
4872 		hui.removeClass(this.element,'hui_window_dark');
4873 		hui.removeClass(this.element,'hui_window_light');
4874 		if (variant=='dark' || variant=='light') {
4875 			hui.addClass(this.element,'hui_window_'+variant);
4876 		}
4877 	},
4878 	flip : function() {
4879 		if (this.back) {
4880 			this.back.style.minHeight = this.element.clientHeight+'px';
4881 			hui.effect.flip({element:this.element});
4882 		}
4883 	},

4885 ////////////////////////////// Dragging ////////////////////////////////
4886 
4887 	/** @private */
4888 	startDrag : function(e) {
4889 		var event = new hui.Event(e);
4890 		this.element.style.zIndex=hui.ui.nextPanelIndex();
4891 		var pos = { top : hui.getTop(this.element), left : hui.getLeft(this.element) };
4892 		this.dragState = {left:event.left()-pos.left,top:event.top()-pos.top};
4893 		this.latestPosition = {left: this.dragState.left, top:this.dragState.top};
4894 		this.latestTime = new Date().getMilliseconds();
4895 		var self = this;
4896 		this.moveListener = function(e) {self.drag(e)};
4897 		this.upListener = function(e) {self.endDrag(e)};
4898 		hui.listen(document,'mousemove',this.moveListener);
4899 		hui.listen(document,'mouseup',this.upListener);
4900 		hui.listen(document,'mousedown',this.upListener);
4901 		event.stop();
4902 		document.body.onselectstart = function () { return false; };
4903 		return false;
4904 	},
4905 	/** @private */
4906 	calc : function(top,left) {
4907 		// TODO: No need to do this all the time
4908 		this.a = this.latestPosition.left-left;
4909 		this.b = this.latestPosition.top-top;
4910 		this.dist = Math.sqrt(Math.pow((this.a),2),Math.pow((this.b),2));
4911 		this.latestTime = new Date().getMilliseconds();
4912 		this.latestPosition = {'top':top,'left':left};
4913 	},
4914 	/** @private */
4915 	drag : function(e) {
4916 		var event = new hui.Event(e);
4917 		this.element.style.right = 'auto';
4918 		var top = (event.top()-this.dragState.top);
4919 		var left = (event.left()-this.dragState.left);
4920 		this.element.style.top = Math.max(top,0)+'px';
4921 		this.element.style.left = Math.max(left,0)+'px';
4922 		//this.calc(top,left);
4923 		return false;
4924 	},
4925 	/** @private */
4926 	endDrag : function(e) {
4927 		hui.unListen(document,'mousemove',this.moveListener);
4928 		hui.unListen(document,'mouseup',this.upListener);
4929 		hui.unListen(document,'mousedown',this.upListener);
4930 		document.body.onselectstart = null;
4931 	}
4932 }

4965 	},
4966 	/** Returns a map of all values of descendants */
4967 	getValues : function() {
4968 		var data = {};
4969 		var d = hui.ui.getDescendants(this);
4970 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
4971 			if (d[i].options && d[i].options.key && d[i].getValue) {
4972 				data[d[i].options.key] = d[i].getValue();
4973 			} else if (d[i].name && d[i].getValue) {
4974 				data[d[i].name] = d[i].getValue();
4975 			}
4976 		};
4977 		return data;
4978 	},
4979 	/** Sets the values of the descendants */
4980 	setValues : function(values) {
4981 		var d = hui.ui.getDescendants(this);
4982 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
4983 			if (d[i].options && d[i].options.key) {
4984 				var key = d[i].options.key;
4985 				if (key && values[key]!=undefined) {
4986 					d[i].setValue(values[key]);
4987 				}
4988 			}
4989 		}
4990 	},
4991 	/** Sets focus in the first found child */
4992 	focus : function() {
4993 		var d = hui.ui.getDescendants(this);
4994 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
4995 			if (d[i].focus) {
4996 				d[i].focus();
4997 				return;
4998 			}
4999 		}
5000 	},

5004 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
5005 			if (d[i].reset) {
5006 				d[i].reset();
5007 			}
5008 		}
5009 	},

5022 	/** Builds and adds a new group according to a recipe
5023 	 * @returns {'hui.ui.Formula.Group'} group

5031 			}

5033 				var w = hui.ui.Formula[item.type].create(item.options);
5034 				g.add(w);
5035 			}
5036 		});
5037 		return g;
5038 	},

5136 hui.ui.Formula.Text.create = function(options) {
5137 	options = hui.override({lines:1},options);

5149 		}

5151 		node.appendChild(input);

5157 	return new hui.ui.Formula.Text(options);

5160 hui.ui.Formula.Text.prototype = {
5161 	/** @private */
5162 	addBehavior : function() {
5163 		hui.ui.addFocusClass({element:this.input,classElement:this.element,'class':'hui_field_focused'});
5164 		hui.listen(this.input,'keyup',this.onKeyUp.bind(this));
5165 		var p = this.element.getElementsByTagName('em')[0];

5168 			hui.listen(p,'mousedown',function() {
5169 				window.setTimeout(function() {
5170 					this.input.focus();
5171 					this.input.select();
5172 				}.bind(this)
5173 			)}.bind(this));
5174 			hui.listen(p,'mouseup',function() {
5175 				this.input.focus();
5176 				this.input.select();
5177 			}.bind(this));
5178 		}
5179 	},
5180 	updateClass : function() {
5181 		hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_field_dirty',this.value.length>0);
5182 	},
5183 	/** @private */
5184 	onKeyUp : function(e) {
5185 		if (!this.multiline && e.keyCode===hui.KEY_RETURN) {
5186 			this.fire('submit');
5187 			var form = hui.ui.getAncestor(this,'hui_formula');
5188 			if (form) {form.submit();}
5189 			return;
5190 		}
5191 		if (this.input.value==this.value) {return;}
5192 		this.value=this.input.value;
5193 		this.updateClass();
5194 		this.expand(true);
5195 		hui.ui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.input.value);
5196 		this.fire('valueChanged',this.input.value);
5197 	},
5198 	updateFromNode : function(node) {
5199 		if (node.firstChild) {
5200 			this.setValue(node.firstChild.nodeValue);
5201 		} else {
5202 			this.setValue(null);
5203 		}
5204 	},
5205 	updateFromObject : function(data) {
5206 		this.setValue(data.value);
5207 	},
5208 	focus : function() {
5209 		try {
5210 			this.input.focus();
5211 		} catch (e) {}
5212 	},
5213 	select : function() {
5214 		try {
5215 			this.input.focus();
5216 			this.input.select();
5217 		} catch (e) {}
5218 	},
5219 	reset : function() {
5220 		this.setValue('');
5221 	},
5222 	setValue : function(value) {
5223 		if (value===undefined || value===null) {
5224 			value='';
5225 		}
5226 		this.value = value;
5227 		this.input.value = value;
5228 		this.expand(true);
5229 	},
5230 	getValue : function() {
5231 		return this.input.value;
5232 	},
5233 	getLabel : function() {
5234 		return this.options.label;
5235 	},
5236 	isEmpty : function() {
5237 		return this.input.value=='';
5238 	},
5239 	isBlank : function() {
5240 		return hui.isBlank(this.input.value);
5241 	},
5242 	setError : function(error) {
5243 		var isError = error ? true : false;
5244 		hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_field_error',isError);
5245 		if (typeof(error) == 'string') {
5246 			hui.ui.showToolTip({text:error,element:this.element,key:this.name});
5247 		}
5248 		if (!isError) {
5249 			hui.ui.hideToolTip({key:this.name});
5250 		}
5251 	},
5252 	// Expanding
5253 	
5254 	$visibilityChanged : function() {
5255 		window.setTimeout(this.expand.bind(this));
5256 	},
5257 	/** @private */
5258 	expand : function(animate) {
5259 		if (!this.multiline) {return};
5260 		if (!hui.dom.isVisible(this.element)) {return};
5261 		var textHeight = hui.ui.getTextAreaHeight(this.input);
5262 		textHeight = Math.max(32,textHeight);
5263 		textHeight = Math.min(textHeight,this.options.maxHeight);
5264 		if (animate) {
5265 			this.updateOverflow();
5266 			hui.animate(this.input,'height',textHeight+'px',300,{ease:hui.ease.slowFastSlow,onComplete:function() {
5267 				this.updateOverflow();
5268 				}.bind(this)
5269 			});
5270 		} else {
5271 			this.input.style.height=textHeight+'px';
5272 			this.updateOverflow();
5273 		}
5274 	},
5275 	updateOverflow : function() {
5276 		if (!this.multiline) return;
5277 		this.input.style.overflowY=this.input.clientHeight>=this.options.maxHeight ? 'auto' : 'hidden';
5278 	}

5283 /**
5284  * A date and time field
5285  * @constructor
5286  */
5287 hui.ui.Formula.DateTime = function(o) {
5288 	this.inputFormats = ['d-m-Y','d/m-Y','d/m/Y','d-m-Y H:i:s','d/m-Y H:i:s','d/m/Y H:i:s','d-m-Y H:i','d/m-Y H:i','d/m/Y H:i','d-m-Y H','d/m-Y H','d/m/Y H','d-m','d/m','d','Y','m-d-Y','m-d','m/d'];
5289 	this.outputFormat = 'd-m-Y H:i:s';
5290 	this.name = o.name;
5291 	this.element = hui.get(o.element);
5292 	this.input = hui.firstByTag(this.element,'input');
5293 	this.options = hui.override({returnType:null,label:null,allowNull:true,value:null},o);
5294 	this.value = this.options.value;
5295 	hui.ui.extend(this);
5296 	this.addBehavior();
5297 	this.updateUI();
5298 }

5300 hui.ui.Formula.DateTime.create = function(options) {
5301 	var node = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_formula_text_singleline'});
5302 	hui.build('input',{'class':'hui_formula_text',parent:node});
5303 	options.element = hui.ui.wrapInField(node);
5304 	return new hui.ui.Formula.DateTime(options);

5307 hui.ui.Formula.DateTime.prototype = {
5308 	addBehavior : function() {
5309 		hui.ui.addFocusClass({element:this.input,classElement:this.element,'class':'hui_field_focused'});
5310 		hui.listen(this.input,'blur',this.check.bind(this));
5311 	},
5312 	updateFromNode : function(node) {
5313 		if (node.firstChild) {
5314 			this.setValue(node.firstChild.nodeValue);
5315 		} else {
5316 			this.setValue(null);
5317 		}
5318 	},
5319 	updateFromObject : function(data) {
5320 		this.setValue(data.value);
5321 	},
5322 	focus : function() {
5323 		try {this.input.focus();} catch (ignore) {}
5324 	},
5325 	reset : function() {
5326 		this.setValue('');
5327 	},
5328 	setValue : function(value) {
5329 		if (!value) {
5330 			this.value = null;
5331 		} else if (value.constructor==Date) {
5332 			this.value = value;
5333 		} else {
5334 			this.value = new Date();
5335 			this.value.setTime(parseInt(value)*1000);
5336 		}
5337 		this.updateUI();
5338 	},
5339 	check : function() {
5340 		var str = this.input.value;
5341 		var parsed = null;
5342 		for (var i=0; i < this.inputFormats.length && parsed==null; i++) {
5343 			parsed = Date.parseDate(str,this.inputFormats[i]);
5344 		};
5345 		if (this.options.allowNull || parsed!=null) {
5346 			this.value = parsed;
5347 		}
5348 		this.updateUI();
5349 	},
5350 	getValue : function() {
5351 		if (this.value!=null && this.options.returnType=='seconds') {
5352 			return Math.round(this.value.getTime()/1000);
5353 		}
5354 		return this.value;
5355 	},
5356 	getElement : function() {
5357 		return this.element;
5358 	},
5359 	getLabel : function() {
5360 		return this.options.label;
5361 	},
5362 	updateUI : function() {
5363 		if (this.value) {
5364 			this.input.value = this.value.dateFormat(this.outputFormat);
5365 		} else {
5366 			this.input.value = ''
5367 		}
5368 	}
5369 }

5377 hui.ui.Formula.Number = function(o) {
5378 	this.options = hui.override({min:0,max:10000,value:null,decimals:0,allowNull:false},o);	
5379 	this.name = o.name;
5380 	var e = this.element = hui.get(o.element);
5381 	this.input = hui.firstByTag(e,'input');
5382 	this.up = hui.firstByClass(e,'hui_number_up');
5383 	this.down = hui.firstByClass(e,'hui_number_down');
5384 	this.value = this.options.value;
5385 	hui.ui.extend(this);
5386 	this.addBehavior();
5387 }
5388 
5389 hui.ui.Formula.Number.create = function(o) {
5390 	o.element = hui.build('span',{
5391 		'class':'hui_number',
5392 		html:'<span><span><input type="text" value="'+(o.value!==undefined ? o.value : '0')+'"/><a class="hui_number_up"></a><a class="hui_number_down"></a></span></span>'
5393 	});
5394 	return new hui.ui.Formula.Number(o);
5395 }
5396 
5397 hui.ui.Formula.Number.prototype = {
5398 	addBehavior : function() {
5399 		var e = this.element;
5400 		hui.listen(this.input,'focus',function() {hui.addClass(e,'hui_number_focused')});
5401 		hui.listen(this.input,'blur',this.blurEvent.bind(this));
5402 		hui.listen(this.input,'keyup',this.keyEvent.bind(this));
5403 		hui.listen(this.up,'mousedown',this.upEvent.bind(this));
5404 		hui.listen(this.down,'mousedown',this.downEvent.bind(this));
5405 	},
5406 	blurEvent : function() {
5407 		hui.removeClass(this.element,'hui_number_focused');
5408 		this.updateField();
5409 	},
5410 	keyEvent : function(e) {
5411 		e = e || window.event;
5412 		if (e.keyCode==hui.KEY_UP) {
5413 			hui.stop(e);
5414 			this.upEvent();
5415 		} else if (e.keyCode==hui.KEY_DOWN) {
5416 			this.downEvent();
5417 		} else {
5418 			var parsed = parseInt(this.input.value,10);
5419 			if (!isNaN(parsed)) {
5420 				this.setLocalValue(parsed,true);
5421 			} else {
5422 				this.setLocalValue(null,true);
5423 			}
5424 		}
5425 	},
5426 	downEvent : function() {
5427 		if (this.value===null) {
5428 			this.setLocalValue(this.options.min,true);
5429 		} else {
5430 			this.setLocalValue(this.value-1,true);
5431 		}
5432 		this.updateField();
5433 	},
5434 	upEvent : function() {
5435 		this.setLocalValue(this.value+1,true);
5436 		this.updateField();
5437 	},
5438 	focus : function() {
5439 		try {
5440 			this.input.focus();
5441 		} catch (e) {}
5442 	},
5443 	getValue : function() {
5444 		return this.value;
5445 	},
5446 	getLabel : function() {
5447 		return this.options.label;
5448 	},
5449 	setValue : function(value) {
5450 		value = parseInt(value,10);
5451 		if (!isNaN(value)) {
5452 			this.setLocalValue(value,false);
5453 		}
5454 		this.updateField();
5455 	},
5456 	updateField : function() {
5457 		this.input.value = this.value===null || this.value===undefined ? '' : this.value;
5458 	},
5459 	setLocalValue : function(value,fire) {
5460 		var orig = this.value;
5461 		if (value===null || value===undefined && this.options.allowNull) {
5462 			this.value = null;
5463 		} else {
5464 			this.value = Math.min(Math.max(value,this.options.min),this.options.max);
5465 		}
5466 		if (fire && orig!==this.value) {
5467 			hui.ui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.value);
5468 			this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
5469 		}
5470 	},
5471 	reset : function() {
5472 		if (this.options.allowNull) {
5473 			this.value = null;
5474 		} else {
5475 			this.value = Math.min(Math.max(0,this.options.min),this.options.max);
5476 		}
5477 		this.updateField();
5478 	}
5479 }

5483 /**
5484  * A drop down selector
5485  * @constructor
5486  */
5487 hui.ui.Formula.DropDown = function(o) {
5488 	this.options = hui.override({label:null,placeholder:null,url:null,source:null},o);
5489 	this.name = o.name;
5490 	var e = this.element = hui.get(o.element);
5491 	this.inner = e.getElementsByTagName('strong')[0];
5492 	this.items = o.items || [];
5493 	this.index = -1;
5494 	this.value = this.options.value || null;
5495 	this.dirty = true;
5496 	hui.ui.extend(this);
5497 	this._addBehavior();
5498 	this._updateIndex();
5499 	this._updateUI();
5500 	if (this.options.url) {
5501 		this.options.source = new hui.ui.Source({url:this.options.url,delegate:this});
5502 	} else if (this.options.source) {
5503 		this.options.source.listen(this);
5504 	}
5505 }

5507 hui.ui.Formula.DropDown.create = function(options) {
5508 	options = options || {};
5509 	options.element = hui.build('a',{
5510 		'class':'hui_dropdown',href:'#',
5511 		html:'<span><span><strong></strong></span></span>'
5512 	});

5515 
5516 hui.ui.Formula.DropDown.prototype = {
5517 	/** @private */
5518 	_addBehavior : function() {
5519 		hui.ui.addFocusClass({element:this.element,'class':'hui_dropdown_focused'});
5520 		hui.listen(this.element,'click',this._click.bind(this));
5521 		hui.listen(this.element,'blur',this._hideSelector.bind(this));
5522 		hui.listen(this.element,'keydown',this._keyDown.bind(this));
5523 	},
5524 	/** @private */
5525 	_updateIndex : function() {
5526 		this.index=-1;
5527 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
5528 			if (this.items[i].value==this.value) {
5529 				this.index=i;
5530 			}
5531 		};
5532 	},
5533 	/** @private */
5534 	_updateUI : function() {
5535 		var selected = this.items[this.index];
5536 		if (selected) {
5537 			var text = selected.label || selected.title || '';
5538 			this.inner.innerHTML='';
5539 			hui.dom.addText(this.inner,hui.wrap(text));
5540 		} else if (this.options.placeholder) {
5541 			this.inner.innerHTML='';
5542 			this.inner.appendChild(hui.build('em',{text:hui.escape(this.options.placeholder)}));
5543 		} else {
5544 			this.inner.innerHTML='';
5545 		}
5546 		if (!this.selector) {
5547 			return;
5548 		}
5549 		var as = this.selector.getElementsByTagName('a');
5550 		for (var i=0; i < as.length; i++) {
5551 			if (this.index==i) {
5552 				hui.addClass(as[i],'hui_selected');
5553 			} else {
5554 				as[i].className='';
5555 			}
5556 		};
5557 	},
5558 	/** @private */
5559 	_click : function(e) {
5560 		hui.stop(e);
5561 		this._buildSelector();
5562 		var el = this.element, s=this.selector;
5563 		el.focus();
5564 		if (!this.items) return;
5565 		var docHeight = hui.getDocumentHeight();
5566 		if (docHeight<200) {
5567 			var left = hui.getLeft(this.element);
5568 			hui.setStyle(this.selector,{'left':left+'px',top:'5px'});
5569 		} else {
5570 			hui.place({
5571 				target:{element:this.element,vertical:1,horizontal:0},
5572 				source:{element:this.selector,vertical:0,horizontal:0}
5573 			});
5574 		}
5575 		hui.setStyle(s,{visibility:'hidden',display:'block',width:''});
5576 		var height = Math.min(docHeight-hui.getTop(s)-5,200);
5577 		var width = Math.max(el.clientWidth-5,100,s.clientWidth+20);
5578 		var space = hui.getViewPortWidth()-hui.getLeft(el)-20;
5579 		width = Math.min(width,space);
5580 		hui.setStyle(s,{visibility:'visible',width:width+'px',zIndex:hui.ui.nextTopIndex(),maxHeight:height+'px'});
5581 	},
5582 	/** @private */
5583 	_keyDown : function(e) {
5584 		if (this.items.length==0) {
5585 			return;
5586 		}
5587 		if (e.keyCode==40) {
5588 			hui.stop(e);
5589 			if (this.index>=this.items.length-1) {
5590 				this.value=this.items[0].value;
5591 			} else {
5592 				this.value=this.items[this.index+1].value;
5593 			}
5594 			this._updateIndex();
5595 			this._updateUI();
5596 			this._fireChange();
5597 		} else if (e.keyCode==38) {
5598 			hui.stop(e);
5599 			if (this.index>0) {
5600 				this.index--;
5601 			} else {
5602 				this.index = this.items.length-1;
5603 			}
5604 			this.value = this.items[this.index].value;
5605 			this._updateUI();
5606 			this._fireChange();
5607 		}
5608 	},
5609 	selectFirst : function() {
5610 		if (this.items.length>0) {
5611 			this.setValue(this.items[0].value);
5612 		}
5613 	},
5614 	getValue : function() {
5615 		return this.value;
5616 	},
5617 	setValue : function(value) {
5618 		this.value = value;
5619 		this._updateIndex();
5620 		this._updateUI();
5621 	},
5622 	reset : function() {
5623 		this.setValue(null);
5624 	},
5625 	getLabel : function() {
5626 		return this.options.label;
5627 	},
5628 	refresh : function() {
5629 		if (this.options.source) {
5630 			this.options.source.refresh();
5631 		}
5632 	},
5633 	// TODO: Is this used?
5634 	getItem : function() {
5635 		if (this.index>=0) {
5636 			return this.items[this.index];
5637 		}
5638 		return 0;
5639 	},
5640 	addItem : function(item) {
5641 		this.items.push(item);
5642 		this.dirty = true;
5643 		this._updateIndex();
5644 		this._updateUI();
5645 	},
5646 	setItems : function(items) {
5647 		this.items = items;
5648 		this.dirty = true;
5649 		this.index = -1;
5650 		this._updateIndex();
5651 		this._updateUI();
5652 	},
5653 	/** @private */
5654 	$itemsLoaded : function(items) {
5655 		this.setItems(items);
5656 	},
5657 	/** @private */
5658 	_hideSelector : function() {
5659 		if (!this.selector) return;
5660 		this.selector.style.display='none';
5661 	},
5662 	/** @private */
5663 	_buildSelector : function() {
5664 		if (!this.dirty || !this.items) {return};
5665 		if (!this.selector) {
5666 			this.selector = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_dropdown_selector'});
5667 			document.body.appendChild(this.selector);
5668 			hui.listen(this.selector,'mousedown',function(e) {hui.stop(e)});
5669 		} else {
5670 			this.selector.innerHTML='';
5671 		}
5672 		var self = this;
5673 		hui.each(this.items,function(item,i) {
5674 			var e = hui.build('a',{href:'#',text:item.label || item.title});
5675 			hui.listen(e,'mousedown',function(e) {
5676 				hui.stop(e);
5677 				self._itemClicked(item,i);
5678 			})
5679 			if (i==self.index) {
5680 				hui.addClass(e,'hui_selected')
5681 			};
5682 			self.selector.appendChild(e);
5683 		});
5684 		this.dirty = false;
5685 	},
5686 	/** @private */
5687 	_itemClicked : function(item,index) {
5688 		this.index = index;
5689 		var changed = this.value!=this.items[index].value;
5690 		this.value = this.items[index].value;
5691 		this._updateUI();
5692 		this._hideSelector();
5693 		if (changed) {
5694 			this._fireChange();
5695 		}
5696 	},
5697 	_fireChange : function() {
5698 		hui.ui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.value);
5699 		this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
5700 	}
5701 }

5726 		for (var i=0; i < this.radios.length; i++) {
5727 			var radio = this.radios[i];

5743 		var element = hui.get(radio.id);
5744 		var self = this;
5745 		element.onclick = function() {

5748 		}

5858 hui.ui.Formula.Checkboxes.prototype = {
5859 	/** @private */
5860 	addBehavior : function() {
5861 		var checks = hui.byClass(this.element,'hui_checkbox');
5862 		hui.each(checks,function(check,i) {
5863 			hui.listen(check,'click',function(e) {
5864 				hui.stop(e);
5865 				this.flipValue(this.items[i].value);
5866 			}.bind(this))
5867 		}.bind(this))
5868 	},
5869 	getValue : function() {
5870 		return this.values;
5871 	},
5872 	/** @deprecated */
5873 	getValues : function() {
5874 		return this.values;
5875 	},
5876 	checkValues : function() {
5877 		var newValues = [];
5878 		for (var i=0; i < this.values.length; i++) {
5879 			var value = this.values[i],
5880 				found = false,
5881 				j;
5882 			for (j=0; j < this.items.length; j++) {
5883 				found = found || this.items[j].value===value;
5884 			}
5885 			for (j=0; j < this.subItems.length; j++) {
5886 				found = found || this.subItems[j].hasValue(value);
5887 			};
5888 			if (found) {
5889 				newValues.push(value);
5890 			}
5891 		};
5892 		this.values=newValues;
5893 	},
5894 	setValue : function(values) {
5895 		this.values=values;
5896 		this.checkValues();
5897 		this.updateUI();
5898 	},
5899 	/** @deprecated */
5900 	setValues : function(values) {
5901 		this.setValue(values);
5902 	},
5903 	flipValue : function(value) {
5904 		hui.flipInArray(this.values,value);
5905 		this.checkValues();
5906 		this.updateUI();
5907 		this.fire('valueChanged',this.values);
5908 		hui.ui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.values);
5909 	},
5910 	updateUI : function() {
5911 		var i,item,found;
5912 		for (i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
5913 			this.subItems[i].updateUI();
5914 		};
5915 		var nodes = hui.byClass(this.element,'hui_checkbox');
5916 		for (i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
5917 			item = this.items[i];
5918 			found = hui.inArray(this.values,item.value);
5919 			hui.setClass(nodes[i],'hui_checkbox_selected',found);
5920 		};
5921 	},
5922 	refresh : function() {
5923 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
5924 			this.subItems[i].refresh();
5925 		};
5926 	},
5927 	reset : function() {
5928 		this.setValues([]);
5929 	},
5930 	registerSource : function(source) {
5931 		source.parent = this;
5932 		this.sources.push(source);
5933 	},
5934 	registerItem : function(item) {
5935 		// If it is a number, treat it as such
5936 		if (parseInt(item.value)==item.value) {
5937 			item.value = parseInt(item.value);
5938 		}
5939 		this.items.push(item);
5940 	},
5941 	registerItems : function(items) {
5942 		items.parent = this;
5943 		this.subItems.push(items);
5944 	},
5945 	getLabel : function() {
5946 		return this.options.label;
5947 	},
5948 	$itemsLoaded : function(items) {
5949 		hui.each(items,function(item) {
5950 			var node = hui.build('a',{'class':'hui_checkbox',href:'javascript:void(0);',html:'<span><span></span></span>'+hui.escape(item.title)});
5951 			hui.listen(node,'click',function(e) {
5952 				hui.stop(e);
5953 				this.flipValue(item.value);
5954 			}.bind(this))
5955 			hui.ui.addFocusClass({element:node,'class':'hui_checkbox_focused'});
5956 			this.element.appendChild(node);
5957 			this.items.push(item);
5958 		}.bind(this));
5959 		this.checkValues();
5960 		this.updateUI();
5961 	}
5962 }

5964 /////////////////////// Checkbox items ///////////////////
5965 
5966 /**
5967  * Check box items
5968  * @constructor
5969  */
5970 hui.ui.Formula.Checkboxes.Items = function(options) {
5971 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
5972 	this.name = options.name;
5973 	this.parent = null;
5974 	this.options = options;
5975 	this.checkboxes = [];
5976 	hui.ui.extend(this);
5977 	if (this.options.source) {

6015 		};

6017 			alert(typeof(this.parent.values));
6018 			alert(e);
6019 		}
6020 	},

6022 		for (var i=0; i < this.checkboxes.length; i++) {
6023 			if (this.checkboxes[i].value==value) {

6107 }/**
6108  * <p><strong>Events:</strong></p>
6109  * <ul>
6110  * <li>listRowWasOpened - When a row is double clicked (rename to open)</li>
6111  * <li>selectionChanged - When a row is selected (rename to select)</li>
6112  * <li>selectionReset - When a selection is removed</li>
6113  * </ul>
6114  * <p><strong>Bindings:</strong></p>
6115  * <ul>
6116  * <li><del>window</del></li>
6117  * <li>window.page</li>
6118  * <li>sort.direction</li>
6119  * <li>sort.key</li>
6120  * </ul>
6121  * <p><strong>XML:</strong></p>
6122  * <code>
6123  * <list name="list" source="sourcesListSource" state="list"/>
6124  * <br/>
6125  * <list name="list" url="my_list_data.xml" state="list"/>
6126  * </code>
6127  *
6128  * @constructor
6129  * @param {Object} options The options : {url:null,source:null}
6130  */
6131 hui.ui.List = function(options) {
6132 	this.options = hui.override({url:null,source:null},options);
6133 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
6134 	this.name = options.name;
6135 	if (this.options.source) {
6136 		this.options.source.listen(this);
6137 	}
6138 	this.url = options.url;
6139 	this.table = hui.firstByTag(this.element,'table');
6140 	this.head = hui.firstByTag(this.element,'thead');
6141 	this.body = hui.firstByTag(this.element,'tbody');
6142 	this.columns = [];
6143 	this.rows = [];
6144 	this.selected = [];
6145 	this.navigation = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_list_navigation');
6146 	this.count = hui.firstByClass(this.navigation,'hui_list_count');
6147 	this.windowPage = hui.firstByClass(this.navigation,'window_page');
6148 	this.windowPageBody = hui.firstByClass(this.navigation,'window_page_body');
6149 	this.parameters = {};
6150 	this.sortKey = null;
6151 	this.sortDirection = null;
6152 	
6153 	this.window = {size:null,page:0,total:0};
6154 	if (options.windowSize!='') {
6155 		this.window.size = parseInt(options.windowSize);
6156 	}
6157 	hui.ui.extend(this);
6158 	if (this.url)  {
6159 		this.refresh();
6160 	}
6161 }

6269 	valueForProperty : function(p) {
6270 		if (p=='window.page') return this.window.page;
6271 		if (p=='window.page') return this.window.page;
6272 		else if (p=='sort.key') return this.sortKey;
6273 		else if (p=='sort.direction') return (this.sortDirection || 'ascending');
6274 		else return this[p];
