6278 		return this.element.style.display!='none';
6279 	},
6280 	/** @private */
6281 	refresh : function() {
6282 		if (this.options.source) {
6283 			this.options.source.refresh();
6284 			return;
6285 		}
6286 		if (!this.url) return;
6287 		var url = this.url;
6288 		if (typeof(this.window.page)=='number') {
6289 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
6290 			url+='windowPage='+this.window.page;
6291 		}
6292 		if (this.window.size) {
6293 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
6294 			url+='windowSize='+this.window.size;
6295 		}
6296 		if (this.sortKey) {
6297 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
6298 			url+='sort='+this.sortKey;
6299 		}
6300 		if (this.sortDirection) {
6301 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
6302 			url+='direction='+this.sortDirection;
6303 		}
6304 		for (var key in this.parameters) {
6305 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
6306 			url+=key+'='+this.parameters[key];
6307 		}
6308 		this._setBusy(true);
6309 		hui.ui.request({
6310 			url:url,
6311 			onJSON : function(obj) {this._setBusy(false);this.$objectsLoaded(obj)}.bind(this),
6312 			onXML : function(obj) {this._setBusy(false);this.$listLoaded(obj)}.bind(this)
6313 		});
6314 	},
6315 	/** @private */
6316 	sort : function(index) {
6317 		var key = this.columns[index].key;
6318 		if (key==this.sortKey) {
6319 			this.sortDirection = this.sortDirection=='ascending' ? 'descending' : 'ascending';
6320 			hui.ui.firePropertyChange(this,'sort.direction',this.sortDirection);
6321 		} else {
6322 			hui.ui.firePropertyChange(this,'sort.key',key);
6323 		}
6324 		this.sortKey = key;
6325 	},
6326 
6327 	/** @private */
6328 	$listLoaded : function(doc) {
6329 		this.selected = [];
6330 		this.parseWindow(doc);
6331 		this.buildNavigation();
6332 		hui.dom.clear(this.head);
6333 		hui.dom.clear(this.body);
6334 		this.rows = [];
6335 		this.columns = [];
6336 		var headTr = document.createElement('tr');
6337 		var sort = doc.getElementsByTagName('sort');
6338 		this.sortKey=null;
6339 		this.sortDirection=null;
6340 		if (sort.length>0) {
6341 			this.sortKey=sort[0].getAttribute('key');
6342 			this.sortDirection=sort[0].getAttribute('direction');
6343 		}
6344 		var headers = doc.getElementsByTagName('header');
6345 		var i;
6346 		for (i=0; i < headers.length; i++) {
6347 			var className = '';
6348 			var th = document.createElement('th');
6349 			var width = headers[i].getAttribute('width');
6350 			var key = headers[i].getAttribute('key');
6351 			var sortable = headers[i].getAttribute('sortable')=='true';
6352 			if (width && width!='') {
6353 				th.style.width=width+'%';
6354 			}
6355 			if (sortable) {
6356 				var self = this;
6357 				th.huiIndex = i;
6358 				th.onclick=function() {self.sort(this.huiIndex)};
6359 				className+='sortable';
6360 			}
6361 			if (this.sortKey && key==this.sortKey) {
6362 				className+=' sort_'+this.sortDirection;
6363 			}
6364 			th.className=className;
6365 			var span = document.createElement('span');
6366 			th.appendChild(span);
6367 			span.appendChild(document.createTextNode(headers[i].getAttribute('title') || ''));
6368 			headTr.appendChild(th);
6369 			this.columns.push({'key':key,'sortable':sortable,'width':width});
6370 		};
6371 		this.head.appendChild(headTr);
6372 		var frag = document.createDocumentFragment();
6373 		var rows = doc.getElementsByTagName('row');
6374 		for (i=0; i < rows.length; i++) {
6375 			var cells = rows[i].getElementsByTagName('cell');
6376 			var row = document.createElement('tr');
6377 			row.setAttribute('data-index',i);
6378 			var icon = rows[i].getAttribute('icon');
6379 			var title = rows[i].getAttribute('title');
6380 			for (var j=0; j < cells.length; j++) {
6381 				var td = document.createElement('td');
6382 				if (cells[j].getAttribute('wrap')=='false') {
6383 					td.style.whiteSpace='nowrap';
6384 				}
6385 				if (cells[j].getAttribute('vertical-align')) {
6386 					td.style.verticalAlign=cells[j].getAttribute('vertical-align');
6387 				}
6388 				this.parseCell(cells[j],td);
6389 				row.appendChild(td);
6390 				if (!title) {
6391 					title = hui.dom.getText(cells[j]);
6392 				}
6393 				if (!icon) {
6394 					icon = cells[j].getAttribute('icon');
6395 				}
6396 			};
6397 			var info = {id:rows[i].getAttribute('id'),kind:rows[i].getAttribute('kind'),icon:icon,title:title,index:i};
6398 			row.dragDropInfo = info;
6399 			this.addRowBehavior(row,i);
6400 			frag.appendChild(row);
6401 			this.rows.push(info);
6402 		};
6403 		this.body.appendChild(frag);
6404 		this.fire('selectionReset');
6405 	},

6428 		this.busy = busy;
6429 		window.clearTimeout(this.busytimer);
6430 		if (busy) {
6431 			var e = this.element;
6432 			this.busytimer = window.setTimeout(function() {
6433 				hui.addClass(e,'hui_list_busy');
6434 			},300);
6435 		} else {
6436 			hui.removeClass(this.element,'hui_list_busy');
6437 		}

6439 	
6440 	/** @private 
6441 	filter : function(str) {
6442 		var len = 20;
6443 		var regex = new RegExp("[\\w]{"+len+",}","g");
6444 		var match = regex.exec(str);
6445 		if (match) {
6446 			for (var i=0; i < match.length; i++) {
6447 				var rep = '';
6448 				for (var j=0; j < match[i].length; j++) {
6449 					rep+=match[i][j];
6450 					if ((j+1)%len==0) rep+='\u200B';
6451 				};
6452 				str = str.replace(match[i],rep);
6453 			};
6454 		}
6455 		return str;
6456 	},*/
6457 	
6458 	/** @private */
6459 	parseCell : function(node,cell) {
6460 		var icon = node.getAttribute('icon');
6461 		if (icon!=null && icon!='') {
6462 			cell.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(icon,1));
6463 		}
6464 		for (var i=0; i < node.childNodes.length; i++) {
6465 			var child = node.childNodes[i];
6466 			if (hui.dom.isDefinedText(child)) {
6467 				hui.dom.addText(cell,child.nodeValue);
6468 			} else if (hui.dom.isElement(child,'break')) {
6469 				cell.appendChild(document.createElement('br'));
6470 			} else if (hui.dom.isElement(child,'icon')) {
6471 				cell.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(child.getAttribute('icon'),1));
6472 			} else if (hui.dom.isElement(child,'line')) {
6473 				var line = hui.build('p',{'class':'hui_list_line'});
6474 				if (child.getAttribute('dimmed')=='true') {
6475 					hui.addClass(line,'hui_list_dimmed')
6476 				}
6477 				cell.appendChild(line);
6478 				this.parseCell(child,line);
6479 			} else if (hui.dom.isElement(child,'object')) {
6480 				var obj = hui.build('div',{'class':'object'});
6481 				if (child.getAttribute('icon')) {
6482 					obj.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(child.getAttribute('icon'),1));
6483 				}
6484 				if (child.firstChild && child.firstChild.nodeType==hui.TEXT_NODE && child.firstChild.nodeValue.length>0) {
6485 					hui.dom.addText(obj,child.firstChild.nodeValue);
6486 				}
6487 				cell.appendChild(obj);
6488 			} else if (hui.dom.isElement(child,'icons')) {
6489 				var icons = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_list_icons'});
6490 				this.parseCell(child,icons);
6491 				cell.appendChild(icons);
6492 			} else if (hui.dom.isElement(child,'button')) {
6493 				var button = hui.ui.Button.create({text:child.getAttribute('text'),small:true,rounded:true});
6494 				button.click(function() {
6495 					this._buttonClick(button);
6496 				}.bind(this))
6497 				cell.appendChild(button.getElement());
6498 			}
6499 		};
6500 	},
6501 	_buttonClick : function(button) {
6502 		var row = hui.firstParentByTag(button.getElement(),'tr');
6503 		var obj = this.rows[parseInt(row.getAttribute('data-index'),10)];
6504 		this.fire('buttonClick',obj,button);
6505 	},
6506 	/** @private */
6507 	parseWindow : function(doc) {
6508 		var wins = doc.getElementsByTagName('window');
6509 		if (wins.length>0) {
6510 			var win = wins[0];
6511 			this.window.total = parseInt(win.getAttribute('total'));
6512 			this.window.size = parseInt(win.getAttribute('size'));
6513 			this.window.page = parseInt(win.getAttribute('page'));
6514 		} else {
6515 			this.window.total = 0;
6516 			this.window.size = 0;
6517 			this.window.page = 0;
6518 		}
6519 	},
6520 	/** @private */
6521 	buildNavigation : function() {
6522 		var self = this;
6523 		var pages = this.window.size>0 ? Math.ceil(this.window.total/this.window.size) : 0;
6524 		if (pages<2) {
6525 			this.navigation.style.display='none';
6526 			return;
6527 		}
6528 		this.navigation.style.display='block';
6529 		var from = ((this.window.page)*this.window.size+1);
6530 		hui.dom.setText(this.count,(from+'-'+Math.min((this.window.page+1)*this.window.size,this.window.total)+' / '+this.window.total));
6531 		var pageBody = this.windowPageBody;
6532 		pageBody.innerHTML='';
6533 		if (pages<2) {
6534 			this.windowPage.style.display='none';	
6535 		} else {
6536 			var indices = this.buildPages(pages,this.window.page);
6537 			for (var i=0; i < indices.length; i++) {
6538 				var index = indices[i];
6539 				if (index==='') {
6540 					pageBody.appendChild(hui.build('span',{text:''}));
6541 				} else {
6542 					var a = document.createElement('a');
6543 					a.appendChild(document.createTextNode(index+1));
6544 					a.setAttribute('data-index',index);
6545 					a.onmousedown = function() {
6546 						self.windowPageWasClicked(this);
6547 						return false;
6548 					}
6549 					if (index==self.window.page) {
6550 						a.className='selected';
6551 					}
6552 					pageBody.appendChild(a);
6553 				}
6554 			}
6555 			this.windowPage.style.display='block';
6556 		}
6557 	},
6558 	/** @private */
6559 	buildPages : function(count,selected) {
6560 		var pages = [];
6561 		var x = false;
6562 		for (var i=0;i<count;i++) {
6563 			if (i<1 || i>count-2 || Math.abs(selected-i)<5) {
6564 				pages.push(i);
6565 				x=false;
6566 			} else {
6567 				if (!x) {
6568 					pages.push('')
6569 				};
6570 				x=true;
6571 			}
6572 		}
6573 		return pages;
6574 	},
6575 	/** @private */
6576 	setData : function(data) {
6577 		this.selected = [];
6578 		var win = data.window || {};
6579 		this.window.total = win.total || 0;
6580 		this.window.size = win.size || 0;
6581 		this.window.page = win.page || 0;
6582 		this.buildNavigation();
6583 		this.buildHeaders(data.headers);
6584 		this.buildRows(data.rows);
6585 	},
6586 	/** @private */
6587 	buildHeaders : function(headers) {
6588 		hui.dom.clear(this.head);
6589 		this.columns = [];
6590 		var tr = hui.build('tr',{parent:this.head});
6591 		hui.each(headers,function(h,i) {
6592 			var th = hui.build('th');
6593 			if (h.width) {
6594 				th.style.width = h.width+'%';
6595 			}
6596 			if (h.sortable) {
6597 				hui.listen(th,'click',function() {this.sort(i)}.bind(this));
6598 				hui.addClass(th,'sortable');
6599 			}
6600 			th.appendChild(hui.build('span',{text:h.title}));
6601 			tr.appendChild(th);
6602 			this.columns.push(h);
6603 		}.bind(this));
6604 	},
6605 	/** @private */
6606 	buildRows : function(rows) {
6607 		var self = this;
6608 		hui.dom.clear(this.body);
6609 		this.rows = [];
6610 		if (!rows) return;
6611 		hui.each(rows,function(r,i) {
6612 			var tr = hui.build('tr');
6613 			var icon = r.icon;
6614 			var title = r.title;
6615 			hui.each(r.cells,function(c) {
6616 				var td = hui.build('td');
6617 				if (c.icon) {
6618 					td.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(c.icon,1));
6619 					icon = icon || c.icon;
6620 				}
6621 				if (c.text) {
6622 					td.appendChild(document.createTextNode(c.text))
6623 					title = title || c.text;
6624 				}
6625 				tr.appendChild(td);
6626 			})
6627 			self.body.appendChild(tr);
6628 			// TODO: Memory leak!
6629 			var info = {id:r.id,kind:r.kind,icon:icon,title:title,index:i};
6630 			tr.dragDropInfo = info;
6631 			self.rows.push({id:r.id,kind:r.kind,icon:icon,title:title,index:i,data:r.data});
6632 			this.addRowBehavior(tr,i);
6633 		}.bind(this));
6634 	},
6635 	/** @private */
6636 	setObjects : function(objects) {
6637 		this.selected = [];
6638 		hui.dom.clear(this.body);
6639 		this.rows = [];
6640 		for (var i=0; i < objects.length; i++) {
6641 			var row = hui.build('tr');
6642 			var obj = objects[i];
6643 			var title = null;
6644 			for (var j=0; j < this.columns.length; j++) {
6645 				var cell = hui.build('td');
6646 				if (this.builder) {
6647 					cell.appendChild(this.builder.buildColumn(this.columns[j],obj));
6648 				} else {
6649 					var value = obj[this.columns[j].key] || '';
6650 					if (hui.isArray(value)) {
6651 						for (var k=0; k < value.length; k++) {
6652 							if (value[k].constructor == Object) {
6653 								cell.appendChild(this.createObject(value[k]));
6654 							} else {
6655 								cell.appendChild(hui.build('div',{text:value}));
6656 							}
6657 						};
6658 					} else if (value.constructor == Object) {
6659 						cell.appendChild(this.createObject(value[j]));
6660 					} else {
6661 						hui.dom.addText(cell,value);
6662 						title = title==null ? value : title;
6663 					}
6664 				}
6665 				row.appendChild(cell);
6666 			};
6667 			var info = {id:obj.id,kind:obj.kind,title:title};
6668 			row.dragDropInfo = info;
6669 			this.body.appendChild(row);
6670 			this.addRowBehavior(row,i);
6671 			this.rows.push(obj);
6672 		};
6673 	},
6674 	/** @private */
6675 	createObject : function(object) {
6676 		var node = hui.build('div',{'class':'object'});
6677 		if (object.icon) {
6678 			node.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(object.icon,1));
6679 		}
6680 		hui.dom.addText(node,object.text || object.name || '')
6681 		return node;
6682 	},
6683 	/** @private */
6684 	addRowBehavior : function(row,index) {
6685 		var self = this;
6686 		row.onmousedown = function(e) {
6687 			if (self.busy) {return};
6688 			self.rowDown(index);
6689 			hui.ui.startDrag(e,row);
6690 			return false;
6691 		}
6692 		row.ondblclick = function() {
6693 			if (self.busy) {return};
6694 			self.rowDoubleClick(index);
6695 			return false;
6696 		}
6697 	},
6698 	/** @private */
6699 	changeSelection : function(indexes) {
6700 		var rows = this.body.getElementsByTagName('tr'),
6701 			i;
6702 		for (i=0;i<this.selected.length;i++) {
6703 			hui.removeClass(rows[this.selected[i]],'selected');
6704 		}
6705 		for (i=0;i<indexes.length;i++) {
6706 			hui.addClass(rows[indexes[i]],'selected');
6707 		}
6708 		this.selected = indexes;
6709 		this.fire('selectionChanged',this.rows[indexes[0]]);
6710 	},
6711 	/** @private */
6712 	rowDown : function(index) {
6713 		this.changeSelection([index]);
6714 	},
6715 	/** @private */
6716 	rowDoubleClick : function(index) {
6717 		this.fire('listRowWasOpened',this.getFirstSelection());
6718 	},
6719 	/** @private */
6720 	windowPageWasClicked : function(tag) {
6721 		var index = parseInt(tag.getAttribute('data-index'));
6722 		this.window.page = index;
6723 		hui.ui.firePropertyChange(this,'window',this.window);
6724 		hui.ui.firePropertyChange(this,'window.page',this.window.page);
6725 	}
6726 };

6865 hui.ui.ObjectList.prototype = {
6866 	ignite : function() {
6867 		this.addObject({});
6868 	},
6869 	addObject : function(data,addToEnd) {
6870 		var obj;
6871 		if (this.objects.length==0 || addToEnd) {
6872 			obj = new hui.ui.ObjectList.Object(this.objects.length,data,this);
6873 			this.objects.push(obj);
6874 			this.body.appendChild(obj.getElement());
6875 		} else {
6876 			var last = this.objects[this.objects.length-1];
6877 			hui.removeFromArray(this.objects,last);
6878 			obj = new hui.ui.ObjectList.Object(last.index,data,this);
6879 			last.index++;
6880 			this.objects.push(obj);
6881 			this.objects.push(last);
6882 			this.body.insertBefore(obj.getElement(),last.getElement())
6883 		}
6884 	},
6885 	reset : function() {
6886 		for (var i=0; i < this.objects.length; i++) {
6887 			var element = this.objects[i].getElement();
6888 			if (!element.parentNode) {
6889 				hui.log('no parent for...');
6890 				hui.log(element);
6891 			} else {
6892 				element.parentNode.removeChild(element);
6893 			}
6894 		};
6895 		this.objects = [];
6896 		this.addObject({});
6897 	},
6898 	addObjects : function(data) {
6899 		for (var i=0; i < data.length; i++) {
6900 			this.addObject(data[i]);
6901 		};
6902 	},
6903 	setObjects : function(data) {
6904 		this.reset();
6905 		this.addObjects(data);
6906 	},
6907 	getObjects : function(data) {
6908 		var list = [];
6909 		for (var i=0; i < this.objects.length-1; i++) {
6910 			list.push(this.objects[i].getData());
6911 		};
6912 		return list;
6913 	},
6914 	getValue : function() {
6915 		return this.getObjects();
6916 	},
6917 	setValue : function(data) {
6918 		this.setObjects(data);
6919 	},
6920 	registerTemplateItem : function(item) {
6921 		this.template.push(item);
6922 	},
6923 	objectDidChange : function(obj) {
6924 		if (obj.index>=this.objects.length-1) {
6925 			this.addObject({},true);
6926 		}
6927 	},

7055 /**
7056  * Creates a new instance of an alert
7057  * <br/><strong>options:</strong> { name: String, title: String, text: String, emotion: 'smile' | 'gasp', modal: Boolean}
7058  * @static
7059  */
7060 hui.ui.Alert.create = function(options) {
7061 	options = hui.override({title:'',text:'',emotion:null,title:null},options);
7062 	
7063 	var element = options.element = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_alert'});
7064 	var body = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_alert_body',parent:element});
7065 	hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_alert_content',parent:body});
7066 	document.body.appendChild(element);
7067 	var obj = new hui.ui.Alert(options);
7068 	if (options.emotion) {
7069 		obj.setEmotion(options.emotion);
7070 	}
7071 	if (options.title) {
7072 		obj.setTitle(options.title);
7073 	}
7074 	if (options.text) {
7075 		obj.setText(options.text);
7076 	}
7077 	
7078 	return obj;
7079 }

7081 hui.ui.Alert.prototype = {
7082 	/** Shows the alert */
7083 	show : function() {
7084 		var zIndex = hui.ui.nextAlertIndex();
7085 		if (this.options.modal) {
7086 			hui.ui.showCurtain({widget:this,zIndex:zIndex});
7087 			zIndex++;
7088 		}
7089 		this.element.style.zIndex=zIndex;
7090 		this.element.style.display='block';
7091 		this.element.style.top=(hui.getScrollTop()+100)+'px';
7092 		hui.animate(this.element,'opacity',1,200);
7093 		hui.animate(this.element,'margin-top','40px',600,{ease:hui.ease.elastic});
7094 	},
7095 	/** Hides the alert */
7096 	hide : function() {
7097 		hui.animate(this.element,'opacity',0,200,{hideOnComplete:true});
7098 		hui.animate(this.element,'margin-top','0px',200);
7099 		hui.ui.hideCurtain(this);
7100 	},
7101 	/** Sets the alert title */
7102 	setTitle : function(/**String*/ text) {

7104 			this.title = hui.build('h1',{parent:this.content});
7105 		}
7106 		hui.dom.setText(this.title,text);
7107 		
7108 	},

7111 		if (!this.text) {
7112 			this.text = hui.build('p',{parent:this.content});
7113 		}
7114 		hui.dom.setText(this.text,text || '');
7115 	},

7117 	setEmotion : function(/**String*/ emotion) {
7118 		if (this.emotion) {
7119 			hui.removeClass(this.body,this.emotion);
7120 		}
7121 		this.emotion = emotion;
7122 		hui.addClass(this.body,emotion);
7123 	},
7124 	/** Updates multiple properties
7125 	 * @param {Object} options {title: String, text: String, emotion: 'smile' | 'gasp'}
7126 	 */
7127 	update : function(options) {
7128 		options = options || {};
7129 		this.setTitle(options.title || null);
7130 		this.setText(options.text || null);
7131 		this.setEmotion(options.emotion || null);
7132 	},
7133 	/** Adds a Button to the alert */
7134 	addButton : function(button) {
7135 		if (!this.buttons) {
7136 			this.buttons = hui.ui.Buttons.create({align:'right'});
7137 			this.body.appendChild(this.buttons.element);
7138 		}
7139 		this.buttons.add(button);
7140 	}
7141 }

7156 /**
7157  * Creates a new button
7158  */
7159 hui.ui.Button.create = function(o) {
7160 	o = hui.override({text:'',highlighted:false,enabled:true},o);
7161 	var className = 'hui_button'+(o.highlighted ? ' hui_button_highlighted' : '');
7162 	if (o.small && o.rounded) {
7163 		className+=' hui_button_small_rounded';
7164 	}
7165 	if (!o.enabled) {
7166 		className+=' hui_button_disabled';
7167 	}
7168 	var element = o.element = hui.build('a',{'class':className,href:'#'});
7169 	var element2 = document.createElement('span');
7170 	element.appendChild(element2);
7171 	var element3 = document.createElement('span');
7172 	element2.appendChild(element3);
7173 	if (o.icon) {
7174 		var icon = hui.build('em',{'class':'hui_button_icon',style:'background-image:url('+hui.ui.getIconUrl(o.icon,1)+')'});
7175 		if (!o.text || o.text.length==0) {
7176 			hui.addClass(icon,'hui_button_icon_notext');
7177 		}
7178 		element3.appendChild(icon);
7179 	}
7180 	if (o.text && o.text.length>0) {
7181 		hui.dom.addText(element3,o.text);
7182 	}
7183 	if (o.title && o.title.length>0) {
7184 		hui.dom.addText(element3,o.title);
7185 	}
7186 	return new hui.ui.Button(o);
7187 }
7188 
7189 hui.ui.Button.prototype = {
7190 	/** @private */
7191 	addBehavior : function() {
7192 		var self = this;
7193 		hui.listen(this.element,'mousedown',function(e) {
7194 			hui.stop(e);
7195 		});
7196 		hui.listen(this.element,'click',function(e) {
7197 			hui.stop(e);
7198 			self.clicked();
7199 		});
7200 	},
7201 	/** @private */
7202 	clicked : function() {
7203 		if (this.enabled) {
7204 			if (this.options.confirm) {
7205 				hui.ui.confirmOverlay({
7206 					widget:this,
7207 					text:this.options.confirm.text,
7208 					okText:this.options.confirm.okText,
7209 					cancelText:this.options.confirm.cancelText,
7210 					onOk:this.fireClick.bind(this)
7211 				});
7212 			} else {
7213 				this.fireClick();
7214 			}
7215 		} else {
7216 			this.element.blur();
7217 		}
7218 	},
7219 	/** @private */
7220 	fireClick : function() {
7221 		this.fire('click');
7222 		if (this.options.submit) {
7223 			var form = hui.ui.getAncestor(this,'hui_formula');
7224 			if (form) {form.submit();}
7225 		}
7226 	},
7227 	/** Registers a function as a click listener or issues a click */
7228 	click : function(func) {
7229 		if (func) {
7230 			this.listen({$click:func});
7231 			return this;
7232 		} else {
7233 			this.clicked();
7234 		}
7235 	},
7236 	focus : function() {
7237 		this.element.focus();
7238 	},
7239 	/** Registers a function as a click handler */
7240 	onClick : function(func) {
7241 		this.listen({$click:func});
7242 	},
7243 	/** Enables or disables the button */
7244 	setEnabled : function(enabled) {
7245 		this.enabled = enabled;
7246 		this.updateUI();
7247 	},
7248 	/** Enables the button */
7249 	enable : function() {
7250 		this.setEnabled(true);
7251 	},
7252 	/** Disables the button */
7253 	disable : function() {
7254 		this.setEnabled(false);
7255 	},
7256 	/** Sets whether the button is highlighted */
7257 	setHighlighted : function(highlighted) {
7258 		hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_button_highlighted',highlighted);
7259 	},
7260 	/** @private */
7261 	updateUI : function() {
7262 		hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_button_disabled',!this.enabled);
7263 	},
7264 	/** Sets the button text */
7265 	setText : function(text) {
7266 		hui.dom.setText(this.element.getElementsByTagName('span')[1], text);
7267 	}
7268 }

7306  */
7307 hui.ui.Selection = function(options) {
7308 	this.options = hui.override({value:null},options);
7309 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
7310 	this.name = options.name;
7311 	this.items = [];
7312 	this.subItems = [];
7313 	this.selection=null;
7314 	if (this.options.value!=null) {
7315 		this.selection = {value:this.options.value};
7316 	}
7317 	hui.ui.extend(this);
7318 }

7320 /**
7321  * Creates a new selection widget
7322  * @param {Object} options The options : {width:0}

7324 hui.ui.Selection.create = function(options) {

7329 	}
7330 	return new hui.ui.Selection(options);
7331 }
7332 
7333 hui.ui.Selection.prototype = {
7334 	/** Get the selected item
7335 	 * @returns {Object} The selected item, null if no selection */
7336 	getValue : function() {
7337 		return this.selection;
7338 	},
7339 	valueForProperty : function(p) {
7340 		if (p==='value') {
7341 			return this.selection ? this.selection.value : null;
7342 		} else if (p==='kind') {
7343 			return this.selection ? this.selection.kind : null;
7344 		}
7345 		return undefined;
7346 	},
7347 	/** Set the selected item
7348 	 * @param {Object} value The selected item */
7349 	setValue : function(value) {
7350 		var item = this.getSelectionWithValue(value);
7351 		if (item===null) {
7352 			this.selection = null;
7353 		} else {
7354 			this.selection = item;
7355 			this.kind=item.kind;
7356 		}
7357 		this.updateUI();
7358 		this.fireChange();
7359 	},
7360 	/** @private */
7361 	getSelectionWithValue : function(value) {
7362 		var i;
7363 		for (i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7364 			if (this.items[i].value==value) {
7365 				return this.items[i];
7366 			}
7367 		};
7368 		for (i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
7369 			var items = this.subItems[i].items;
7370 			for (var j=0; j < items.length; j++) {
7371 				if (items[j].value==value) {
7372 					return items[j];
7373 				}
7374 			};
7375 		};
7376 		return null;
7377 	},
7378 	/** Set the value to null */
7379 	reset : function() {
7380 		this.setValue(null);
7381 	},
7382 	/** @private */
7383 	updateUI : function() {
7384 		var i;
7385 		for (i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7386 			hui.setClass(this.items[i].element,'hui_selected',this.isSelection(this.items[i]));
7387 		};
7388 		for (i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
7389 			this.subItems[i].updateUI();
7390 		};
7391 	},
7392 	/** @private */
7393 	changeSelection : function(item) {
7394 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
7395 			this.subItems[i].selectionChanged(this.selection,item);
7396 		};
7397 		this.selection = item;
7398 		this.updateUI();
7399 		this.fireChange();
7400 	},
7401 	/** @private */
7402 	fireChange : function() {
7403 		this.fire('selectionChanged',this.selection);
7404 		this.fireProperty('value',this.selection ? this.selection.value : null);
7405 		this.fireProperty('kind',this.selection ? this.selection.kind : null);
7406 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
7407 			this.subItems[i].parentValueChanged();
7408 		};
7409 	},
7410 	/** @private */
7411 	registerItems : function(items) {
7412 		items.parent = this;
7413 		this.subItems.push(items);
7414 	},
7415 	/** @private */
7416 	registerItem : function(id,title,icon,badge,value,kind) {
7417 		var element = hui.get(id);
7418 		var item = {id:id,title:title,icon:icon,badge:badge,element:element,value:value,kind:kind};
7419 		this.items.push(item);
7420 		this.addItemBehavior(element,item);
7421 		this.selection = this.getSelectionWithValue(this.options.value);
7422 	},
7423 	/** @private */
7424 	addItemBehavior : function(node,item) {
7425 		hui.listen(node,'click',function() {
7426 			this.itemWasClicked(item);
7427 		}.bind(this));
7428 		hui.listen(node,'dblclick',function() {
7429 			this.itemWasDoubleClicked(item);
7430 		}.bind(this));
7431 		node.dragDropInfo = item;
7432 	},
7433 	/** Untested!! */
7434 	setObjects : function(items) {
7435 		this.items = [];
7436 		hui.each(items,function(item) {
7437 			this.items.push(item);
7438 			var node = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_selection_item'});
7439 			item.element = node;
7440 			this.element.appendChild(node);
7441 			var inner = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_selection_label',text:item.title});
7442 			if (item.icon) {
7443 				node.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(item.icon,1));
7444 			}
7445 			node.appendChild(inner);
7446 			hui.listen(node,'click',function() {
7447 				this.itemWasClicked(item);
7448 			}.bind(this));
7449 			hui.listen(node,'dblclick',function(e) {
7450 				hui.stop(e);
7451 				this.itemWasDoubleClicked(item);
7452 			}.bind(this));
7453 		}.bind(this));
7454 	},
7455 	/** @private */
7456 	isSelection : function(item) {
7457 		if (this.selection===null) {
7458 			return false;
7459 		}
7460 		var selected = item.value==this.selection.value;
7461 		if (this.selection.kind) {
7462 			selected = selected && item.kind==this.selection.kind;
7463 		}
7464 		return selected;
7465 	},
7466 	
7467 	/** @private */
7468 	itemWasClicked : function(item) {
7469 		this.changeSelection(item);
7470 	},
7471 	/** @private */
7472 	itemWasDoubleClicked : function(item) {
7473 		this.fire('selectionWasOpened',item);
7474 	}
7475 }

7477 /////////////////////////// Items ///////////////////////////
7478 
7479 /**
7480  * @constructor
7481  * A group of items loaded from a source
7482  * @param {Object} options The options : {element,name,source}
7483  */
7484 hui.ui.Selection.Items = function(options) {
7485 	this.options = hui.override({source:null},options);
7486 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
7487 	this.title = hui.get(this.element.id+'_title');
7488 	this.name = options.name;
7489 	this.parent = null;
7490 	this.items = [];
7491 	hui.ui.extend(this);
7492 	if (this.options.source) {
7493 		this.options.source.listen(this);
7494 	}
7495 }
7496 
7497 hui.ui.Selection.Items.prototype = {
7498 	/**
7499 	 * Refresh the underlying source
7500 	 */
7501 	refresh : function() {
7502 		if (this.options.source) {
7503 			this.options.source.refresh();
7504 		}
7505 	},
7506 	/** @private */
7507 	$objectsLoaded : function(objects) {
7508 		this.$itemsLoaded(objects);
7509 	},
7510 	/** @private */
7511 	$itemsLoaded : function(items) {
7512 		this.items = [];
7513 		this.element.innerHTML='';
7514 		this.buildLevel(this.element,items,0);
7515 		if (this.title) {
7516 			this.title.style.display=this.items.length>0 ? 'block' : 'none';
7517 		}
7518 		this.parent.updateUI();
7519 	},
7520 	/** @private */
7521 	buildLevel : function(parent,items,inc) {
7522 		if (!items) return;
7523 		var hierarchical = this.isHierarchy(items);
7524 		var open = inc==0;
7525 		var level = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_selection_level',style:(open ? 'display:block' : 'display:none'),parent:parent});
7526 		hui.each(items,function(item) {
7527 			if (item.type=='title') {
7528 				hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_selection_title',html:'<span>'+item.title+'</span>',parent:level});
7529 				return;
7530 			}
7531 			var hasChildren = item.children && item.children.length>0;
7532 			var left = inc*16+6;
7533 			if (!hierarchical && inc>0 || hierarchical && !hasChildren) left+=13;
7534 			var node = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_selection_item'});
7535 			node.style.paddingLeft = left+'px';
7536 			if (item.badge) {
7537 				node.appendChild(hui.build('strong',{'class':'hui_selection_badge',text:item.badge}));
7538 			}
7539 			if (hierarchical && hasChildren) {
7540 				var self = this;
7541 				var x = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_disclosure',parent:node});
7542 				hui.listen(x,'click',function(e) {
7543 					hui.stop(e);
7544 					self.toggle(x);
7545 				});
7546 			}
7547 			var inner = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_selection_label',text:item.title});
7548 			if (item.icon) {
7549 				node.appendChild(hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_icon_1',style:'background-image: url('+hui.ui.getIconUrl(item.icon,1)+')'}));
7550 			}
7551 			node.appendChild(inner);
7552 			hui.listen(node,'click',function(e) {
7553 				this.parent.itemWasClicked(item);
7554 			}.bind(this));
7555 			hui.listen(node,'dblclick',function(e) {
7556 				this.parent.itemWasDoubleClicked(item);
7557 			}.bind(this));
7558 			level.appendChild(node);
7559 			var info = {title:item.title,icon:item.icon,badge:item.badge,kind:item.kind,element:node,value:item.value};
7560 			node.dragDropInfo = info;
7561 			this.items.push(info);
7562 			this.buildLevel(level,item.children,inc+1);
7563 		}.bind(this));
7564 	},
7565 	/** @private */
7566 	toggle : function(node) {
7567 		if (hui.hasClass(node,'hui_disclosure_open')) {
7568 			hui.getNext(node.parentNode).style.display='none';
7569 			hui.removeClass(node,'hui_disclosure_open');
7570 		} else {
7571 			hui.getNext(node.parentNode).style.display='block';
7572 			hui.addClass(node,'hui_disclosure_open');
7573 		}
7574 	},
7575 	/** @private */
7576 	isHierarchy : function(items) {
7577 		if (!items) {return false};
7578 		for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
7579 			if (items[i]!==null && items[i].children && items[i].children.length>0) {
7580 				return true;
7581 			}
7582 		};
7583 		return false;
7584 	},
7585 	/** Get the selection of this items group
7586 	 * @returns {Object} The selected item or null */
7587 	getValue : function() {
7588 		if (this.parent.selection==null) {
7589 			return null;
7590 		}
7591 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7592 			if (this.items[i].value == this.parent.selection.value) {
7593 				return this.items[i];
7594 			}
7595 		};
7596 		return null;
7597 	},
7598 	/** @private */
7599 	updateUI : function() {
7600 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7601 			hui.setClass(this.items[i].element,'hui_selected',this.parent.isSelection(this.items[i]));
7602 		};
7603 	},
7604 	/** @private */
7605 	selectionChanged : function(oldSelection,newSelection) {
7606 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7607 			var value = this.items[i].value;
7608 			if (value == newSelection.value) {
7609 				this.fireProperty('value',newSelection.value);
7610 				return;
7611 			}
7612 		};
7613 		this.fireProperty('value',null);
7614 	},
7615 	/**
7616 	 * Called when the parent changes value, must fire its new value
7617 	 * @private
7618 	 */
7619 	parentValueChanged : function() {
7620 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7621 			if (this.parent.isSelection(this.items[i])) {
7622 				this.fireProperty('value',this.items[i].value);
7623 				return;
7624 			}
7625 		};
7626 		this.fireProperty('value',null);
7627 	}
7628 }

7713 hui.ui.Toolbar.Icon.create = function(options) {
7714 	var element = options.element = hui.build('a',{'class':'hui_toolbar_icon'});
7715 	var icon = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_icon',style:'background-image: url('+hui.ui.getIconUrl(options.icon,2)+')'});
7716 	var inner = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_toolbar_inner_icon',parent:element});
7717 	var innerest = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_toolbar_inner_icon',parent:inner});
7718 	var title = hui.build('strong',{text:options.title});
7719 	if (options.overlay) {
7720 		hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_icon_overlay',parent:icon,style:'background-image: url('+hui.ui.getIconUrl('overlay/'+options.overlay,2)+')'});
7721 	}
7722 	innerest.appendChild(icon);
7723 	innerest.appendChild(title);
7724 	return new hui.ui.Toolbar.Icon(options);
7725 }

7727 hui.ui.Toolbar.Icon.prototype = {
7728 	/** @private */
7729 	addBehavior : function() {

7732 			self.wasClicked();
7733 		}
7734 	},
7735 	/** Sets wether the icon should be enabled */

7737 		this.enabled = enabled;
7738 		this.element.tabIndex=enabled ? 0 : -1;
7739 		hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_toolbar_icon_disabled',!this.enabled);
7740 	},

7744 	},

7748 	},

7751 		hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_toolbar_icon_selected',selected);

7755 		if (this.enabled) {

7758 					widget:this,
7759 					text:this.options.confirm.text,
7760 					okText:this.options.confirm.okText,
7761 					cancelText:this.options.confirm.cancelText,
7762 					onOk:this.fireClick.bind(this)
7763 				});
7764 			} else {
7765 				this.fireClick();
7766 			}
7767 		}
7768 	},
7769 	/** @private */
7770 	fireClick : function() {
7771 		hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'toolbarIconWasClicked');
7772 		hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'click');

7848 /* EOF *//**
7849 	Used to choose an image
7850 	@constructor
7851 */
7852 hui.ui.ImagePicker = function(o) {
7853 	this.name = o.name;
7854 	this.options = o || {};
7855 	this.element = hui.get(o.element);
7856 	this.images = [];
7857 	this.object = null;
7858 	this.thumbnailsLoaded = false;
7859 	hui.ui.extend(this);
7860 	this.addBehavior();
7861 }
7862 
7863 hui.ui.ImagePicker.prototype = {
7864 	/** @private */
7865 	addBehavior : function() {
7866 		this.element.onclick = this.showPicker.bind(this);
7867 	},
7868 	setObject : function(obj) {
7869 		this.object = obj;
7870 		this.updateUI();
7871 	},
7872 	getObject : function() {
7873 		return this.object;
7874 	},
7875 	reset : function() {
7876 		this.object = null;
7877 		this.updateUI();
7878 	},
7879 	/** @private */
7880 	updateUI : function() {
7881 		if (this.object==null) {
7882 			this.element.style.backgroundImage='';
7883 		} else {
7884 			var url = hui.ui.resolveImageUrl(this,this.object,48,48);
7885 			this.element.style.backgroundImage='url('+url+')';
7886 		}
7887 	},
7888 	/** @private */
7889 	showPicker : function() {
7890 		if (!this.picker) {
7891 			var self = this;
7892 			this.picker = hui.ui.BoundPanel.create();
7893 			this.content = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_imagepicker_thumbs'});
7894 			var buttons = hui.ui.Buttons.create({align:'right'});
7895 			var close = hui.ui.Button.create({text:'Luk',highlighted:true});
7896 			close.listen({
7897 				$click:function() {self.hidePicker()}
7898 			});
7899 			var remove = hui.ui.Button.create({text:'Fjern'});
7900 			remove.listen({
7901 				$click:function() {self.setObject(null);self.hidePicker()}
7902 			});
7903 			buttons.add(remove).add(close);
7904 			this.picker.add(this.content);
7905 			this.picker.add(buttons);
7906 		}
7907 		this.picker.position(this.element);
7908 		this.picker.show();
7909 		if (!this.thumbnailsLoaded) {
7910 			this.updateImages();
7911 			this.thumbnailsLoaded = true;
7912 		}
7913 	},
7914 	/** @private */
7915 	hidePicker : function() {
7916 		this.picker.hide();
7917 	},
7918 	/** @private */
7919 	updateImages : function() {
7920 		var self = this;
7921 		hui.request({
7922 			onSuccess:function(t) {
7923 				self.parse(t.responseXML);
7924 			},
7925 			url:this.options.source
7926 		});
7927 	},
7928 	/** @private */
7929 	parse : function(doc) {
7930 		this.content.innerHTML='';
7931 		var images = doc.getElementsByTagName('image');
7932 		var self = this;
7933 		for (var i=0; i < images.length; i++) {
7934 			var id = images[i].getAttribute('id');
7935 			var img = {id:images[i].getAttribute('id')};
7936 			var url = hui.ui.resolveImageUrl(this,img,48,48);
7937 			var thumb = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_imagepicker_thumbnail',style:'background-image:url('+url+')'});
7938 			thumb.huiObject = {'id':id};
7939 			thumb.onclick = function() {
7940 				self.setObject(this.huiObject);
7941 				self.hidePicker();
7942 			}
7943 			this.content.appendChild(thumb);
7944 		};
7945 	}
7946 }

7949  * A bound panel is a panel that is shown at a certain place
7950  * @constructor
7951  * @param {Object} options { element: Node | id, name: String }
7952  */
7953 hui.ui.BoundPanel = function(options) {
7954 	this.options = options;
7955 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
7956 	this.name = options.name;
7957 	this.visible = false;
7958 	this.content = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_boundpanel_content');
7959 	this.arrow = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_boundpanel_arrow');
7960 	hui.ui.extend(this);
7961 }
7962 
7963 /**
7964  * Creates a new bound panel
7965  * <br/><strong>options:</strong> { name: String, top: pixels, left: pixels, padding: pixels, width: pixels }
7966  * @param {Object} options The options
7967  */
7968 hui.ui.BoundPanel.create = function(options) {
7969 	options = hui.override({name:null, top:0, left:0, width:null, padding: null}, options);
7970 
7971 	
7972 	var html = 
7973 		'<div class="hui_boundpanel_arrow"></div>'+
7974 		'<div class="hui_boundpanel_top"><div><div></div></div></div>'+
7975 		'<div class="hui_boundpanel_body"><div class="hui_boundpanel_body"><div class="hui_boundpanel_body"><div class="hui_boundpanel_content" style="';
7976 	if (options.width) {
7977 		html+='width:'+options.width+'px;';
7978 	}
7979 	if (options.padding) {
7980 		html+='padding:'+options.padding+'px;';
7981 	}
7982 	html+='"></div></div></div></div>'+
7983 		'<div class="hui_boundpanel_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>';
7984 
7985 	options.element = hui.build(
7986 		'div',{
7987 			'class':'hui_boundpanel',
7988 			style:'display:none;zIndex:'+hui.ui.nextPanelIndex()+';top:'+options.top+'px;left:'+options.left+'px',
7989 			html:html,
7990 			parent:document.body
7991 		}
7992 	);
7993 	return new hui.ui.BoundPanel(options);
7994 }

7996 /********************************* Public methods ***********************************/
7997 
7998 hui.ui.BoundPanel.prototype = {
7999 	toggle : function() {
8000 		if (!this.visible) {
8001 			this.show();
8002 		} else {
8003 			this.hide();
8004 		}
8005 	},
8006 	/** Shows the panel */
8007 	show : function() {
8008 		if (!this.visible) {
8009 			if (this.options.target) {
8010 				this.position(hui.ui.get(this.options.target));
8011 			}
8012 			if (hui.browser.opacity) {
8013 				hui.setOpacity(this.element,0);
8014 			}
8015 			var vert;
8016 			if (this.relativePosition=='left') {
8017 				vert = false;
8018 				this.element.style.marginLeft='30px';
8019 			} else if (this.relativePosition=='right') {
8020 				vert = false;
8021 				this.element.style.marginLeft='-30px';
8022 			} else if (this.relativePosition=='top') {
8023 				vert = true;
8024 				this.element.style.marginTop='30px';
8025 			} else if (this.relativePosition=='bottom') {
8026 				vert = true;
8027 				this.element.style.marginTop='-30px';
8028 			}
8029 			hui.setStyle(this.element,{
8030 				visibility : 'hidden', display : 'block'
8031 			})
8032 			var width = this.element.clientWidth;
8033 			hui.setStyle(this.element,{
8034 				width : width+'px' , visibility : 'visible'
8035 			});
8036 			this.element.style.display='block';
8037 			if (hui.browser.opacity) {
8038 				hui.animate(this.element,'opacity',1,400,{ease:hui.ease.fastSlow});
8039 			}
8040 			hui.animate(this.element,vert ? 'margin-top' : 'margin-left','0px',800,{ease:hui.ease.bounce});
8041 		}
8042 		this.element.style.zIndex = hui.ui.nextPanelIndex();
8043 		this.visible=true;
8044 	},
8045 	/** Hides the panel */
8046 	hide : function() {
8047 		if (hui.browser.msie) {
8048 			this.element.style.display='none';
8049 		} else {
8050 			hui.animate(this.element,'opacity',0,300,{ease:hui.ease.slowFast,hideOnComplete:true});
8051 		}
8052 		this.visible=false;
8053 	},
8054 	/**
8055 	 * Adds a widget or element to the panel
8056 	 * @param {Node | Widget} child The object to add
8057 	 */
8058 	add : function(child) {
8059 		if (child.getElement) {
8060 			this.content.appendChild(child.getElement());
8061 		} else {
8062 			this.content.appendChild(child);
8063 		}
8064 	},
8065 	/**
8066 	 * Adds som vertical space to the panel
8067 	 * @param {pixels} height The height of the space in pixels
8068 	 */
8069 	addSpace : function(height) {
8070 		this.add(hui.build('div',{style:'font-size:0px;height:'+height+'px'}));
8071 	},
8072 	/** @private */
8073 	getDimensions : function() {
8074 		var width, height;
8075 		if (this.element.style.display=='none') {
8076 			this.element.style.visibility='hidden';
8077 			this.element.style.display='block';
8078 			width = this.element.clientWidth;
8079 			height = this.element.clientHeight;
8080 			this.element.style.display='none';
8081 			this.element.style.visibility='';
8082 		} else {
8083 			width = this.element.clientWidth;
8084 			height = this.element.clientHeight;
8085 		}
8086 		return {width:width,height:height};
8087 	},
8088 	/** Position the panel at a node
8089 	 * @param {Node} node The node the panel should be positioned at 
8090 	 */
8091 	position : function(node) {
8092 		if (node.getElement) {
8093 			node = node.getElement();
8094 		}
8095 		node = hui.get(node);
8096 		var offset = {left:hui.getLeft(node),top:hui.getTop(node)};
8097 		var scrollOffset = {left:hui.getScrollLeft(),top:hui.getScrollTop()};
8098 		var dims = this.getDimensions();
8099 		var viewportWidth = hui.getViewPortWidth();
8100 		var viewportHeight = hui.getViewPortHeight();
8101 		var nodeLeft = offset.left-scrollOffset.left+hui.getScrollLeft();
8102 		var nodeWidth = node.clientWidth;
8103 		var nodeHeight = node.clientHeight;
8104 		var nodeTop = offset.top-scrollOffset.top+hui.getScrollTop();
8105 		var arrowLeft, arrowTop, left, top;
8106 		var vertical = (nodeTop-scrollOffset.top)/viewportHeight;
8107 		
8108 		if (vertical<.1) {
8109 			this.relativePosition='top';
8110 			this.arrow.className = 'hui_boundpanel_arrow hui_boundpanel_arrow_top';
8111 			arrowTop = -16;
8112 			left = Math.min(viewportWidth-dims.width,Math.max(0,nodeLeft+(nodeWidth/2)-((dims.width)/2)));
8113 			arrowLeft = (nodeLeft+nodeWidth/2)-left-18;
8114 			top = nodeTop+nodeHeight+8;
8115 		}
8116 		else if (vertical>.9) {
8117 			this.relativePosition='bottom';
8118 			this.arrow.className='hui_boundpanel_arrow hui_boundpanel_arrow_bottom';
8119 			arrowTop = dims.height-6;
8120 			left = Math.min(viewportWidth-dims.width,Math.max(0,nodeLeft+(nodeWidth/2)-((dims.width)/2)));
8121 			arrowLeft = (nodeLeft+nodeWidth/2)-left-18;
8122 			top = nodeTop-dims.height-5;
8123 		}
8124 		else if ((nodeLeft+nodeWidth/2)/viewportWidth<.5) {
8125 			this.relativePosition='left';
8126 			left = nodeLeft+nodeWidth+10;
8127 			this.arrow.className='hui_boundpanel_arrow hui_boundpanel_arrow_left';
8128 			arrowLeft=-14;
8129 			top = Math.max(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2);
8130 			arrowTop = (dims.height-32)/2+Math.min(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2);
8131 		} else {
8132 			this.relativePosition='right';
8133 			left = nodeLeft-dims.width-10;
8134 			this.arrow.className='hui_boundpanel_arrow hui_boundpanel_arrow_right';
8135 			arrowLeft=dims.width-4;
8136 			top = Math.max(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2);
8137 			arrowTop = (dims.height-32)/2+Math.min(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2);
8138 		}
8139 		this.arrow.style.marginTop = arrowTop+'px';
8140 		this.arrow.style.marginLeft = arrowLeft+'px';
8141 		if (this.visible) {
8142 			hui.animate(this.element,'top',top+'px',500,{ease:hui.ease.fastSlow});
8143 			hui.animate(this.element,'left',left+'px',500,{ease:hui.ease.fastSlow});
8144 		} else {
8145 			this.element.style.top=top+'px';
8146 			this.element.style.left=left+'px';
8147 		}
8148 	}
8149 }

8197 hui.ui.RichText.replaceInput = function(options) {

8204 	obj.ignite();
8205 }

8207 hui.ui.RichText.create = function(options) {
8208 	options = options || {};
8209 	options.element = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_richtext',html:'<div class="hui_richtext_toolbar"><div class="hui_richtext_inner_toolbar"><div class="hui_richtext_toolbar_content"></div></div></div>'});
8210 	return new hui.ui.RichText(options);

8212 
8213 hui.ui.RichText.prototype = {
8214 	isCompatible : function() {
8215 	    var agt=navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
8216 		return true;
8217 		return (agt.indexOf('msie 6')>-1 || agt.indexOf('msie 7')>-1 || (agt.indexOf('gecko')>-1 && agt.indexOf('safari')<0));
8218 	},
8219 	ignite : function() {
8220 		var self = this;
8221 		this.editor.observe("wysihat:loaded", function(event) {
8222 			if (this.ignited) {
8223 				return;
8224 			}
8225 			this.editor.setStyle(this.options.style);
8226 			this.editor.setRawContent(this.value);
8227 			this.document = this.editor.getDocument();
8228 			if (this.document.body) {
8229 				this.document.body.style.minHeight='100%';
8230 				this.document.body.style.margin='0';
8231 				this.document.documentElement.style.cursor='text';
8232 				this.document.documentElement.style.minHeight='100%';
8233 				Element.setStyle(this.document.body,this.options.style);
8234 			}
8235 			this.window = this.editor.getWindow();
8236 			Event.observe(this.window,'focus',function() {self.documentFocused()});
8237 			Event.observe(this.window,'blur',function() {self.documentBlurred()});
8238 			this.document.body.focus();
8239 			this.ignited = true;
8240      	}.bind(this));
8241 		this.editor.observe("wysihat:change", function(event) {
8242         	this.documentChanged();
8243      	}.bind(this));
8244 	},

8247 	},

8250 			var r = this.document.createRange();
8251 			r.selectNodeContents(this.document.body);
8252 			this.window.getSelection().addRange(r);
8253 		} catch (ignore) {}

8255 	},

8270 		this.toolbar.onmouseup = function() {this.toolbarMouseDown=false}.bind(this);

8276 			} else {

8279 				div.huiRichTextAction = actions[i]

8281 				var img = hui.build('img');

8284 					div.style.backgroundImage='url('+hui.ui.getIconUrl(actions[i].icon,1)+')';
8285 				}
8286 				div.appendChild(img);
8287 				this.toolbarContent.appendChild(div);
8288 				div.onmousedown = hui.ui.RichText.stopEvent;
8289 			}
8290 		};
8291 	},
8292 	documentFocused : function() {
8293 		if (hui.browser.msie) {

8295 			return;
8296 		}

8300 			this.toolbar.style.display='block';

8302 			hui.ani(this.toolbar,'margin-top','-32px',300);
8303 		}
8304 	},

8307 		if (this.toolbarMouseDown) return;
8308 		if (this.options.autoHideToolbar) {
8309 			if (hui.browser.msie) {
8310 				var self = this;
8311 				window.setTimeout(function() {
8312 					self.toolbar.style.display='none';
8313 				},100);
8314 				return;
8315 			}

8317 			hui.ani(this.toolbar,'margin-top','-40px',300);
8318 		}

8320 		hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'richTextDidChange');
8321 	},

8333 			evt.returnValue = false;
8334 		} else if (evt.preventDefault) {

8389 hui.ui.ImageViewer = function(options) {
8390 	this.options = hui.override({
8391 		maxWidth:800,maxHeight:600,perimeter:100,sizeSnap:100,
8392 		margin:0,
8393 		ease:hui.ease.slowFastSlow,
8394 		easeEnd:hui.ease.bounce,
8395 		easeAuto:hui.ease.slowFastSlow,
8396 		easeReturn:hui.ease.cubicInOut,transition:400,transitionEnd:1000,transitionReturn:300
8397 		},options);
8398 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
8399 	this.box = this.options.box;
8400 	this.viewer = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_viewer');
8401 	this.innerViewer = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_inner_viewer');
8402 	this.status = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_status');
8403 	this.previousControl = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_previous');
8404 	this.controller = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_controller');
8405 	this.nextControl = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_next');
8406 	this.playControl = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_play');
8407 	this.closeControl = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_close');
8408 	this.text = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_imageviewer_text');
8409 	this.dirty = false;
8410 	this.width = 600;
8411 	this.height = 460;
8412 	this.index = 0;
8413 	this.playing=false;
8414 	this.name = options.name;
8415 	this.images = [];
8416 	this.box.listen(this);
8417 	this.addBehavior();
8418 	hui.ui.extend(this);
8419 }

8421 hui.ui.ImageViewer.create = function(options) {
8422 	options = options || {};
8423 	var element = options.element = hui.build('div',
8424 		{'class':'hui_imageviewer',
8425 		html:
8426 		'<div class="hui_imageviewer_viewer"><div class="hui_imageviewer_inner_viewer"></div></div>'+
8427 		'<div class="hui_imageviewer_text"></div>'+
8428 		'<div class="hui_imageviewer_status"></div>'+
8429 		'<div class="hui_imageviewer_controller"><div><div>'+
8430 		'<a class="hui_imageviewer_previous"></a>'+
8431 		'<a class="hui_imageviewer_play"></a>'+
8432 		'<a class="hui_imageviewer_next"></a>'+
8433 		'<a class="hui_imageviewer_close"></a>'+
8434 		'</div></div></div>'});
8435 	var box = hui.ui.Box.create({absolute:true,modal:true,closable:true});
8436 	box.add(element);
8437 	box.addToDocument();
8438 	options.box=box;
8439 	return new hui.ui.ImageViewer(options);

8442 hui.ui.ImageViewer.prototype = {
8443 	/** @private */
8444 	addBehavior : function() {
8445 		var self = this;
8446 		this.nextControl.onclick = function() {
8447 			self.next(true);
8448 		}
8449 		this.previousControl.onclick = function() {
8450 			self.previous(true);
8451 		}
8452 		this.playControl.onclick = function() {
8453 			self.playOrPause();
8454 		}
8455 		this.closeControl.onclick = this.hide.bind(this);
8456 		hui.listen(this.viewer,'click',this.zoom.bind(this));
8457 		this.timer = function() {
8458 			self.next(false);
8459 		}
8460 		this.keyListener = function(e) {
8461 			e = hui.event(e);
8462 			if (e.rightKey) {
8463 				self.next(true);
8464 			} else if (e.leftKey) {
8465 				self.previous(true);
8466 			} else if (e.escapeKey) {
8467 				self.hide();
8468 			} else if (e.returnKey) {
8469 				self.playOrPause();
8470 			}
8471 		},
8472 		hui.listen(this.viewer,'mousemove',this.mouseMoveEvent.bind(this));
8473 		hui.listen(this.controller,'mouseover',function() {
8474 			self.overController = true;
8475 		});
8476 		hui.listen(this.controller,'mouseout',function() {
8477 			self.overController = false;
8478 		});
8479 		hui.listen(this.viewer,'mouseout',function(e) {
8480 			if (!hui.ui.isWithin(e,this.viewer)) {
8481 				self.hideController();
8482 			}
8483 		}.bind(this));
8484 	},
8485 	/** @private */
8486 	mouseMoveEvent : function() {
8487 		window.clearTimeout(this.ctrlHider);
8488 		if (this.shouldShowController()) {
8489 			this.ctrlHider = window.setTimeout(this.hideController.bind(this),2000);
8490 			if (hui.browser.msie) {
8491 				this.controller.show();
8492 			} else {
8493 				hui.ui.fadeIn(this.controller,200);
8494 			}
8495 		}
8496 	},
8497 	/** @private */
8498 	hideController : function() {
8499 		if (!this.overController) {
8500 			if (hui.browser.msie) {
8501 				this.controller.hide();
8502 			} else {
8503 				hui.ui.fadeOut(this.controller,500);
8504 			}
8505 		}
8506 	},
8507 	/** @private */
8508 	zoom : function(e) {
8509 		var img = this.images[this.index];
8510 		if (img.width<=this.width && img.height<=this.height) {
8511 			return; // Don't zoom if small
8512 		}
8513 		if (!this.zoomer) {
8514 			this.zoomer = hui.build('div',{
8515 				'class' : 'hui_imageviewer_zoomer',
8516 				style : 'width:'+this.viewer.clientWidth+'px;height:'+this.viewer.clientHeight+'px'
8517 			});
8518 			this.element.insertBefore(this.zoomer,hui.firstByTag(this.element,'*'));
8519 			hui.listen(this.zoomer,'mousemove',this.zoomMove.bind(this));
8520 			hui.listen(this.zoomer,'click',function() {
8521 				this.style.display='none';
8522 			});
8523 		}
8524 		this.pause();
8525 		var size = this.getLargestSize({width:2000,height:2000},img);
8526 		var url = hui.ui.resolveImageUrl(this,img,size.width,size.height);
8527 		this.zoomer.innerHTML = '<div style="width:'+size.width+'px;height:'+size.height+'px;"><img src="'+url+'"/></div>';
8528 		this.zoomer.style.display = 'block';
8529 		this.zoomInfo = {width:size.width,height:size.height};
8530 		this.zoomMove(e);
8531 	},
8532 	zoomMove : function(e) {
8533 		e = new hui.Event(e);
8534 		if (!this.zoomInfo) {
8535 			return;
8536 		}
8537 		var offset = {left:hui.getLeft(this.zoomer),top:hui.getTop(this.zoomer)};
8538 		var x = (e.left()-offset.left)/this.zoomer.clientWidth*(this.zoomInfo.width-this.zoomer.clientWidth);
8539 		var y = (e.top()-offset.top)/this.zoomer.clientHeight*(this.zoomInfo.height-this.zoomer.clientHeight);
8540 		this.zoomer.scrollLeft = x;
8541 		this.zoomer.scrollTop = y;
8542 	},
8543 	/** @private */
8544 	getLargestSize : function(canvas,image) {
8545 		if (image.width<=canvas.width && image.height<=canvas.height) {
8546 			return {width:image.width,height:image.height};
8547 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height>image.width/image.height) {
8548 			return {width:Math.round(canvas.height/image.height*image.width),height:canvas.height};
8549 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height<image.width/image.height) {
8550 			return {width:canvas.width,height:Math.round(canvas.width/image.width*image.height)};
8551 		} else {
8552 			return {width:canvas.width,height:canvas.height};
8553 		}
8554 	},
8555 	/** @private */
8556 	calculateSize : function() {
8557 		var snap = this.options.sizeSnap;
8558 		var newWidth = hui.getViewPortWidth()-this.options.perimeter;
8559 		newWidth = Math.floor(newWidth/snap)*snap;
8560 		newWidth = Math.min(newWidth,this.options.maxWidth);
8561 		var newHeight = hui.getViewPortHeight()-this.options.perimeter;
8562 		newHeight = Math.floor(newHeight/snap)*snap;
8563 		newHeight = Math.min(newHeight,this.options.maxHeight);
8564 		var maxWidth = 0;
8565 		var maxHeight = 0;
8566 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8567 			var dims = this.getLargestSize({width:newWidth,height:newHeight},this.images[i]);
8568 			maxWidth = Math.max(maxWidth,dims.width);
8569 			maxHeight = Math.max(maxHeight,dims.height);
8570 		};
8571 		newHeight = Math.floor(Math.min(newHeight,maxHeight));
8572 		newWidth = Math.floor(Math.min(newWidth,maxWidth));
8573 		
8574 		if (newWidth!=this.width || newHeight!=this.height) {
8575 			this.width = newWidth;
8576 			this.height = newHeight;
8577 			this.dirty = true;
8578 		}
8579 	},
8580 	adjustSize : function() {
8581 		
8582 	},
8583 	showById: function(id) {
8584 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8585 			if (this.images[i].id==id) {
8586 				this.show(i);
8587 				break;
8588 			}
8589 		};
8590 	},
8591 	show: function(index) {
8592 		this.index = index || 0;
8593 		this.calculateSize();
8594 		this.updateUI();
8595 		var margin = this.options.margin;
8596 		hui.setStyle(this.element, {width:(this.width+margin)+'px',height:(this.height+margin*2-1)+'px'});
8597 		hui.setStyle(this.viewer, {width:(this.width+margin)+'px',height:(this.height-1)+'px'});
8598 		hui.setStyle(this.innerViewer, {width:((this.width+margin)*this.images.length)+'px',height:(this.height-1)+'px'});
8599 		hui.setStyle(this.controller, {marginLeft:((this.width-180)/2+margin*0.5)+'px',display:'none'});
8600 		this.box.show();
8601 		this.goToImage(false,0,false);
8602 		hui.listen(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
8603 	},
8604 	hide: function(index) {
8605 		this.pause();
8606 		this.box.hide();
8607 		hui.unListen(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
8608 	},
8609 	/** @private */
8610 	$boxCurtainWasClicked : function() {
8611 		this.hide();
8612 	},
8613 	/** @private */
8614 	$boxWasClosed : function() {
8615 		this.hide();
8616 	},
8617 	/** @private */
8618 	updateUI : function() {
8619 		if (this.dirty) {
8620 			this.innerViewer.innerHTML='';
8621 			for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8622 				var element = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_imageviewer_image'});
8623 				hui.setStyle(element,{'width':(this.width+this.options.margin)+'px','height':(this.height-1)+'px'});
8624 				this.innerViewer.appendChild(element);
8625 			};
8626 			if (this.shouldShowController()) {
8627 				this.controller.style.display='block';
8628 			} else {
8629 				this.controller.style.display='none';
8630 			}
8631 			this.dirty = false;
8632 			this.preload();
8633 		}
8634 	},
8635 	/** @private */
8636 	shouldShowController : function() {
8637 		return this.images.length>1;
8638 	},
8639 	/** @private */
8640 	goToImage : function(animate,num,user) {	
8641 		if (animate) {
8642 			if (num>1) {
8643 				hui.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+this.options.margin),Math.min(num*this.options.transitionReturn,2000),{ease:this.options.easeReturn});				
8644 			} else {
8645 				var end = this.index==0 || this.index==this.images.length-1;
8646 				var ease = (end ? this.options.easeEnd : this.options.ease);
8647 				if (!user) {
8648 					ease = this.options.easeAuto;
8649 				}
8650 				hui.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+this.options.margin),(end ? this.options.transitionEnd : this.options.transition),{ease:ease});
8651 			}
8652 		} else {
8653 			this.viewer.scrollLeft=this.index*(this.width+this.options.margin);
8654 		}
8655 		var text = this.images[this.index].text;
8656 		if (text) {
8657 			this.text.innerHTML=text;
8658 			this.text.style.display='block';
8659 		} else {
8660 			this.text.innerHTML='';
8661 			this.text.style.display='none';
8662 		}
8663 	},
8664 	clearImages : function() {
8665 		this.images = [];
8666 		this.dirty = true;
8667 	},
8668 	addImages : function(images) {
8669 		for (var i=0; i < images.length; i++) {
8670 			this.addImage(images[i]);
8671 		};
8672 	},
8673 	addImage : function(img) {
8674 		this.images.push(img);
8675 		this.dirty = true;
8676 	},
8677 	play : function() {
8678 		if (!this.interval) {
8679 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
8680 		}
8681 		this.next(false);
8682 		this.playing=true;
8683 		this.playControl.className='hui_imageviewer_pause';
8684 	},
8685 	pause : function() {
8686 		window.clearInterval(this.interval);
8687 		this.interval = null;
8688 		this.playControl.className='hui_imageviewer_play';
8689 		this.playing = false;
8690 	},
8691 	playOrPause : function() {
8692 		if (this.playing) {
8693 			this.pause();
8694 		} else {
8695 			this.play();
8696 		}
8697 	},
8698 	resetPlay : function() {
8699 		if (this.playing) {
8700 			window.clearInterval(this.interval);
8701 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
8702 		}
8703 	},
8704 	previous : function(user) {
8705 		var num = 1;
8706 		this.index--;
8707 		if (this.index<0) {
8708 			this.index=this.images.length-1;
8709 			num = this.images.length-1;
8710 		}
8711 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
8712 		this.resetPlay();
8713 	},
8714 	next : function(user) {
8715 		var num = 1;
8716 		this.index++;
8717 		if (this.index==this.images.length) {
8718 			this.index=0;
8719 			num = this.images.length-1;
8720 		}
8721 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
8722 		this.resetPlay();
8723 	},
8724 	/** @private */
8725 	preload : function() {
8726 		var guiLoader = new hui.Preloader();
8727 		guiLoader.addImages(hui.ui.context+'hui/gfx/imageviewer_controls.png');
8728 		var self = this;
8729 		guiLoader.setDelegate({allImagesDidLoad:function() {self.preloadImages()}});
8730 		guiLoader.load();
8731 	},
8732 	/** @private */
8733 	preloadImages : function() {
8734 		var loader = new hui.Preloader();
8735 		loader.setDelegate(this);
8736 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8737 			var url = hui.ui.resolveImageUrl(this,this.images[i],this.width,this.height);
8738 			if (url!==null) {
8739 				loader.addImages(url);
8740 			}
8741 		};
8742 		this.status.innerHTML = '0%';
8743 		this.status.style.display='';
8744 		loader.load(this.index);
8745 	},
8746 	/** @private */
8747 	allImagesDidLoad : function() {
8748 		this.status.style.display='none';
8749 	},
8750 	/** @private */
8751 	imageDidLoad : function(loaded,total,index) {
8752 		this.status.innerHTML = Math.round(loaded/total*100)+'%';
8753 		var url = hui.ui.resolveImageUrl(this,this.images[index],this.width,this.height);
8754 		url = url.replace(/&/g,'&');
8755 		this.innerViewer.childNodes[index].style.backgroundImage="url('"+url+"')";
8756 		hui.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'hui_imageviewer_image_abort',false);
8757 		hui.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'hui_imageviewer_image_error',false);
8758 	},
8759 	/** @private */
8760 	imageDidGiveError : function(loaded,total,index) {
8761 		hui.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'hui_imageviewer_image_error',true);
8762 	},
8763 	/** @private */
8764 	imageDidAbort : function(loaded,total,index) {
8765 		hui.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'hui_imageviewer_image_abort',true);
8766 	}
8767 }

8770 hui.ui.Picker = function(o) {
8771 	o = this.options = hui.override({itemWidth:100,itemHeight:150,itemsVisible:null,shadow:true,valueProperty:'value'},o);
8772 	this.element = hui.get(o.element);
8773 	this.name = o.name;
8774 	this.container = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_picker_container');
8775 	this.content = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_picker_content');
8776 	this.title = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_picker_title');
8777 	this.objects = [];
8778 	this.selected = null;
8779 	this.value = null;
8780 	this.addBehavior();
8781 	hui.ui.extend(this);
8782 }
8783 
8784 hui.ui.Picker.create = function(o) {
8785 	o = hui.override({shadow:true},o);
8786 	o.element = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_picker',
8787 		html:'<div class="hui_picker_top"><div><div></div></div></div>'+
8788 		'<div class="hui_picker_middle"><div class="hui_picker_middle">'+
8789 		(o.title ? '<div class="hui_picker_title">'+o.title+'</div>' : '')+
8790 		'<div class="hui_picker_container"><div class="hui_picker_content"></div></div>'+
8791 		'</div></div>'+
8792 		'<div class="hui_picker_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>'});
8793 	if (o.shadow==true) {
8794 		hui.addClass(o.element,'hui_picker_shadow')
8795 	}
8796 	return new hui.ui.Picker(o);
8797 }

8799 hui.ui.Picker.prototype = {
8800 	addBehavior : function() {
8801 		var self = this;
8802 		hui.listen(this.content,'mousedown',function(e) {
8803 			self.startDrag(e);
8804 			return false;
8805 		});
8806 	},
8807 	setObjects : function(objects) {
8808 		this.selected = null;
8809 		this.objects = objects || [];
8810 		this.updateUI();
8811 	},
8812 	setValue : function(value) {
8813 		this.value = value;
8814 		this.updateSelection();
8815 	},
8816 	getValue : function() {
8817 		return this.value;
8818 	},
8819 	reset : function() {
8820 		this.value = null;
8821 		this.updateSelection();
8822 	},
8823 	updateUI : function() {
8824 		var self = this,
8825 			width;
8826 		this.content.innerHTML='';
8827 		this.container.scrollLeft=0;
8828 		if (this.options.itemsVisible) {
8829 			width = this.options.itemsVisible*(this.options.itemWidth+14);
8830 		} else {
8831 			width = this.container.clientWidth;
8832 		}
8833 		hui.setStyle(this.container,{width:width+'px',height:(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px'});
8834 		this.content.style.width=(this.objects.length*(this.options.itemWidth+14))+'px';
8835 		this.content.style.height=(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px';
8836 		hui.each(this.objects,function(object,i) {
8837 			var item = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_picker_item',title:object.title});
8838 			if (self.value!=null && object[self.options.valueProperty]==self.value) {
8839 				 hui.addClass(item,'hui_picker_item_selected');
8840 			}
8841 			item.innerHTML = '<div class="hui_picker_item_middle"><div class="hui_picker_item_middle">'+
8842 				'<div style="width:'+self.options.itemWidth+'px;height:'+self.options.itemHeight+'px; overflow: hidden; background-image:url(\''+object.image+'\')"><strong>'+hui.escape(object.title)+'</strong></div>'+
8843 				'</div></div>'+
8844 				'<div class="hui_picker_item_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>';
8845 			hui.listen(item,'mouseup',function() {
8846 				self.selectionChanged(object[self.options.valueProperty])
8847 			});
8848 			self.content.appendChild(item);
8849 		});
8850 	},
8851 	updateSelection : function() {
8852 		var children = this.content.childNodes;
8853 		for (var i=0; i < children.length; i++) {
8854 			hui.setClass(children[i],'hui_picker_item_selected',this.value!=null && this.objects[i][this.options.valueProperty]==this.value);
8855 		};
8856 	},
8857 	selectionChanged : function(value) {
8858 		if (this.dragging) return;
8859 		if (this.value==value) return;
8860 		this.value = value;
8861 		this.updateSelection();
8862 		this.fire('selectionChanged',value);
8863 	},
8864 	
8865 	// Dragging
8866 	startDrag : function(e) {
8867 		e = new hui.Event(e);
8868 		e.stop();
8869 		var self = this;
8870 		this.dragX = e.left();
8871 		this.dragScroll = this.container.scrollLeft;
8872 		hui.ui.Picker.mousemove = function(e) {self.drag(e);return false;}
8873 		hui.ui.Picker.mouseup = hui.ui.Picker.mousedown = function(e) {self.endDrag(e);return false;}
8874 		hui.listen(window.document,'mousemove',hui.ui.Picker.mousemove);
8875 		hui.listen(window.document,'mouseup',hui.ui.Picker.mouseup);
8876 		hui.listen(window.document,'mousedown',hui.ui.Picker.mouseup);
8877 	},
8878 	drag : function(e) {
8879 		e = new hui.Event(e);
8880 		e.stop();
8881 		this.dragging = true;
8882 		this.container.scrollLeft=this.dragX-e.left()+this.dragScroll;
8883 	},
8884 	endDrag : function(e) {
8885 		this.dragging = false;
8886 		hui.stop(e);
8887 		hui.unListen(window.document,'mousemove',hui.ui.Picker.mousemove);
8888 		hui.unListen(window.document,'mouseup',hui.ui.Picker.mouseup);
8889 		hui.unListen(window.document,'mousedown',hui.ui.Picker.mouseup);
8890 		var size = this.options.itemWidth+14;
8891 		hui.ani(this.container,'scrollLeft',Math.round(this.container.scrollLeft/size)*size,500,{ease:hui.ease.bounceOut});
8892 	},
8893 	$visibilityChanged : function() {
8894 		this.container.style.display='none';
8895 		var width;
8896 		if (this.options.itemsVisible) {
8897 			width = this.options.itemsVisible*(this.options.itemWidth+14);
8898 		} else {
8899 			width = this.container.parentNode.clientWidth-12;
8900 		}
8901 		width = Math.max(width,0);
8902 		hui.setStyle(this.container,{width:width+'px',display:'block'});
8903 	}
8904 }

8928 hui.ui.Editor.prototype = {
8929 	ignite : function() {
8930 		this.reload();
8931 	},
8932 	addPartController : function(key,title,controller) {
8933 		this.partControllers.push({key:key,'title':title,'controller':controller});
8934 	},
8935 	setOptions : function(options) {
8936 		hui.override(this.options,options);
8937 	},
8938 	getPartController : function(key) {
8939 		var ctrl = null;
8940 		hui.each(this.partControllers,function(item) {
8941 			if (item.key==key) {ctrl=item};
8942 		});
8943 		return ctrl;
8944 	},
8945 	reload : function() {
8946 		if (this.partControls) {
8947 			this.partControls.hide();
8948 		}
8949 		var self = this;
8950 		this.parts = [];
8951 		var rows = hui.byClass(document.body,this.options.partClass);
8952 		hui.each(rows,function(row,i) {
8953 			var columns = hui.byClass(row,self.options.columnClass);
8954 			self.reloadColumns(columns,i);
8955 			hui.each(columns,function(column,j) {
8956 				var parts = column.select('.'+self.options.partClass);
8957 				self.reloadParts(parts,i,j);
8958 			});
8959 		});
8960 		var parts = hui.byClass(document.body,this.options.partClass);
8961 		hui.each(this.parts,function(part) {
8962 			var i = parts.indexOf(part.element);
8963 			if (i!=-1) {
8964 				delete(parts[i]);
8965 			}
8966 		});
8967 		this.reloadParts(parts,-1,-1);
8968 	},
8969 	partExists : function(element) {
8970 		
8971 	},
8972 	reloadColumns : function(columns,rowIndex) {
8973 		var self = this;
8974 		hui.each(columns,function(column,columnIndex) {
8975 			hui.lsiten(column,'mouseover',function() {
8976 				self.hoverColumn(column);
8977 			});
8978 			hui.listen(column,'mouseout',function() {
8979 				self.blurColumn();
8980 			});
8981 			hui.listen(column,'contextmenu',function(e) {
8982 				self.contextColumn(column,rowIndex,columnIndex,e);
8983 			});
8984 		});
8985 	},
8986 	reloadParts : function(parts,row,column) {
8987 		var self = this;
8988 		var reg = new RegExp(this.options.partClass+"_([\\w]+)","i");
8989 		hui.each(parts,function(element,partIndex) {
8990 			if (!element) return;
8991 			var match = element.className.match(reg);
8992 			if (match && match[1]) {
8993 				var handler = self.getPartController(match[1]);
8994 				if (handler) {
8995 					var part = new handler.controller(element,row,column,partIndex);
8996 					part.type=match[1];
8997 					hui.listen(element,'click',function() {
8998 						self.editPart(part);
8999 					});
9000 					hui.listen(element,'mouseover',function(e) {
9001 						self.hoverPart(part);
9002 					});
9003 					hui.listen(element,'mouseout',function(e) {
9004 						self.blurPart(e);
9005 					});
9006 					hui.listen(element,'mousedown',function(e) {
9007 						self.startPartDrag(e);
9008 					});
9009 					self.parts.push(part);
9010 				}
9011 			}
9012 		});
9013 	},
9014 	activate : function() {
9015 		this.active = true;
9016 	},
9017 	deactivate : function() {
9018 		this.active = false;
9019 		if (this.activePart) {
9020 			this.activePart.deactivate();
9021 		}
9022 		if (this.partControls) this.partControls.hide();
9023 	},

9043 			menu.addItem({title:'Rediger kolonne',value:'editColumn'});

9047 			for (var i=0; i < this.partControllers.length; i++) {

9050 			};

9067 		}

9350 hui.ui.Editor.getPartId = function(element) {
9351 	var m = element.id.match(/part\-([\d]+)/i);
9352 	if (m && m.length>0) return m[1];

9496 hui.ui.Menu.prototype = {
9497 	/** @private */
9498 	addBehavior : function() {
9499 		var self = this;
9500 		this.hider = function() {
9501 			self.hide();
9502 		}
9503 		if (this.options.autoHide) {
9504 			var x = function(e) {
9505 				if (!hui.ui.isWithin(e,self.element) && (!self.options.parentElement || !hui.ui.isWithin(e,self.options.parentElement))) {
9506 					if (!self.isSubMenuVisible()) {
9507 						self.hide();
9508 					}
9509 				}
9510 			};
9511 			hui.listen(this.element,'mouseout',x);
9512 			if (this.options.parentElement) {
9513 				hui.listen(this.options.parentElement,'mouseout',x);
9514 			}
9515 		}
9516 	},
9517 	addDivider : function() {
9518 		hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_menu_divider',parent:this.element});
9519 	},
9520 	addItem : function(item) {
9521 		var self = this;
9522 		var element = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_menu_item',text:item.title});
9523 		hui.listen(element,'click',function(e) {
9524 			hui.stop(e);
9525 			self.itemWasClicked(item.value);
9526 		});
9527 		if (item.children) {
9528 			var sub = hui.ui.Menu.create({autoHide:true,parentElement:element});
9529 			sub.addItems(item.children);
9530 			hui.listen(element,'mouseover',function(e) {
9531 				sub.showAtElement(element,e,'horizontal');
9532 			});
9533 			self.subMenus.push(sub);
9534 			hui.addClass(element,'hui_menu_item_children');
9535 		}
9536 		this.element.appendChild(element);
9537 	},
9538 	addItems : function(items) {
9539 		for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
9540 			if (items[i]==null) {
9541 				this.addDivider();
9542 			} else {
9543 				this.addItem(items[i]);
9544 			}
9545 		};
9546 	},
9547 	getValue : function() {
9548 		return this.value;
9549 	},
9550 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
9551 		this.value = value;
9552 		this.fire('itemWasClicked',value);
9553 		this.fire('select',value);
9554 		this.hide();
9555 	},
9556 	showAtPointer : function(e) {
9557 		e = hui.event(e);
9558 		e.stop();
9559 		this.showAtPoint({'top' : e.getTop(),'left' : e.getLeft()});
9560 	},
9561 	showAtElement : function(element,event,position) {
9562 		event = hui.event(event);
9563 		event.stop();
9564 		element = hui.get(element);
9565 		var point = hui.getPosition(element);
9566 		if (position=='horizontal') {
9567 			point.left += element.clientWidth;
9568 		} else if (position=='vertical') {
9569 			point.top += element.clientHeight;
9570 		}
9571 		this.showAtPoint(point);
9572 	},
9573 	showAtPoint : function(pos) {
9574 		var innerWidth = hui.getViewPortWidth();
9575 		var innerHeight = hui.getViewPortHeight();
9576 		var scrollTop = hui.getScrollTop();
9577 		var scrollLeft = hui.getScrollLeft();
9578 		if (!this.visible) {
9579 			hui.setStyle(this.element,{'display':'block','visibility':'hidden',opacity:0});
9580 		}
9581 		var width = this.element.clientWidth;
9582 		var height = this.element.clientHeight;
9583 		var left = Math.min(pos.left,innerWidth-width-26+scrollLeft);
9584 		var top = Math.max(0,Math.min(pos.top,innerHeight-height-20+scrollTop));
9585 		hui.setStyle(this.element,{'top':top+'px','left':left+'px','visibility':'visible',zIndex:hui.ui.nextTopIndex()});
9586 		if (!this.element.style.width) {
9587 			this.element.style.width=(width+6)+'px';
9588 		}
9589 		if (!this.visible) {
9590 			hui.setStyle(this.element,{opacity:1});
9591 			this.addHider();
9592 			this.visible = true;
9593 		}
9594 	},
9595 	hide : function() {
9596 		if (!this.visible) return;
9597 		var self = this;
9598 		hui.animate(this.element,'opacity',0,200,{onComplete:function() {
9599 			self.element.style.display='none';
9600 		}});
9601 		this.removeHider();
9602 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
9603 			this.subMenus[i].hide();
9604 		};
9605 		this.visible = false;
9606 	},
9607 	isSubMenuVisible : function() {
9608 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
9609 			if (this.subMenus[i].visible) return true;
9610 		};
9611 		return false;
9612 	},
9613 	addHider : function() {
9614 		hui.listen(document.body,'click',this.hider);
9615 	},
9616 	removeHider : function() {
9617 		hui.unListen(document.body,'click',this.hider);
9618 	}
9619 }

9647 hui.ui.Overlay.prototype = {

9650 		var self = this;
9651 		this.hider = function(e) {
9652 			if (self.boundElement) {
9653 				if (hui.ui.isWithin(e,self.boundElement) || hui.ui.isWithin(e,self.element)) return;
9654 				// TODO: should be unreg'ed but it fails
9655 				//self.boundElement.stopObserving(self.hider);
9656 				hui.removeClass(self.boundElement,'hui_overlay_bound');

9660 		}
9661 		hui.listen(this.element,'mouseout',this.hider);
9662 	},

9664 		var self = this;

9667 		hui.listen(element,'click',function(e) {
9668 			self.iconWasClicked(key,e);
9669 		});

9671 		this.content.appendChild(element);
9672 	},
9673 	addText : function(text) {

9675 	},
9676 	add : function(widget) {

9678 	},
9679 	hideIcons : function(keys) {
9680 		for (var i=0; i < keys.length; i++) {
9681 			this.icons[keys[i]].style.display='none';
9682 		};
9683 	},
9684 	showIcons : function(keys) {
9685 		for (var i=0; i < keys.length; i++) {
9686 			this.icons[keys[i]].style.display='';
9687 		};
9688 	},
9689 	iconWasClicked : function(key,e) {
9690 		hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'iconWasClicked',key,e);
9691 	},
9692 	showAtElement : function(element,options) {
9693 		options = options || {};
9694 		hui.ui.positionAtElement(this.element,element,options);
9695 		if (this.visible) return;
9696 		if (hui.browser.msie) {
9697 			this.element.style.display='block';
9698 		} else {
9699 			hui.setStyle(this.element,{'display':'block','opacity':0});
9700 			hui.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,150);
9701 		}
9702 		this.visible = true;
9703 		if (options.autoHide) {
9704 			this.boundElement = element;
9705 			hui.listen(element,'mouseout',this.hider);
9706 			hui.addClass(element,'hui_overlay_bound');
9707 		}
9708 		if (this.options.modal) {
9709 			var zIndex = hui.ui.nextAlertIndex();
9710 			this.element.style.zIndex=zIndex+1;
9711 			hui.ui.showCurtain({widget:this,zIndex:zIndex});
9712 		}
9713 		return;
9714 	},
9715 	show : function(options) {
9716 		options = options || {};
9717 		if (!this.visible) {
9718 			hui.setStyle(this.element,{'display':'block',visibility:'hidden'});
9719 		}
9720 		if (options.element) {
9721 			hui.place({
9722 				source:{element:this.element,vertical:0,horizontal:.5},
9723 				target:{element:options.element,vertical:.5,horizontal:.5},
9724 				insideViewPort:true
9725 			});
9726 		}
9727 		if (this.visible) return;
9728 		hui.ui.bounceIn(this.element);
9729 		this.visible = true;
9730 		if (options.autoHide && options.element) {
9731 			this.boundElement = options.element;
9732 			hui.listen(options.element,'mouseout',this.hider);
9733 			hui.addClass(options.element,'hui_overlay_bound');
9734 		}
9735 		if (this.options.modal) {
9736 			var zIndex = hui.ui.nextAlertIndex();
9737 			this.element.style.zIndex=zIndex+1;
9738 			var color = hui.getStyle(document.body,'background-color');
9739 			hui.ui.showCurtain({widget:this,zIndex:zIndex,color:color});
9740 		}
9741 	},
9742 	/** private */
9743 	$curtainWasClicked : function() {
9744 		this.hide();
9745 	},
9746 	hide : function() {
9747 		hui.ui.hideCurtain(this);
9748 		this.element.style.display='none';
9749 		this.visible = false;
9750 	},
9751 	clear : function() {
9752 		hui.ui.destroyDescendants(this.content);
9753 		this.content.innerHTML='';
9754 	}
