9806 hui.ui.Upload.prototype = {
9807 	/** @private */
9808 	addBehavior : function() {
9809 		if (!this.useFlash) {
9810 			this.createIframeVersion();
9811 			return;
9812 		}
9813 		hui.ui.onReady(this.createFlashVersion.bind(this));
9814 	},
9815 	/**
9816 	 * Change a parameter
9817 	 */
9818 	setParameter : function(name,value) {
9819 		if (this.useFlash) {
9820 			alert('Not implemented for flash');
9821 		} else {
9822 			var existing = this.form.getElementsByTagName('input');
9823 			for (var i=0; i < existing.length; i++) {
9824 				if (existing[i].name==name) {
9825 					existing[i].value = value;
9826 					return;
9827 				}
9828 			};
9829 			this.form.appendChild(hui.build('input',{'type':'hidden','name':name,'value':value}));
9830 		}
9831 	},
9832 	
9833 	/////////////////////////// Iframe //////////////////////////
9834 	
9835 	/** @private */
9836 	createIframeVersion : function() {
9837 		hui.ui.Upload.nameIndex++;
9838 		var frameName = 'hui_upload_'+hui.ui.Upload.nameIndex;
9839 		
9840 		var form = this.form = hui.build('form');
9841 		form.setAttribute('action',this.options.url || '');
9842 		form.setAttribute('method','post');
9843 		form.setAttribute('enctype','multipart/form-data');
9844 		form.setAttribute('encoding','multipart/form-data');
9845 		form.setAttribute('target',frameName);
9846 		if (this.options.parameters) {
9847 			for (var key in this.options.parameters) {
9848 				var hidden = hui.build('input',{'type':'hidden','name':key});
9849 				hidden.value = this.options.parameters[key];
9850 				form.appendChild(hidden);
9851 			}
9852 		}
9853 		var iframe = this.iframe = hui.build('iframe',{name:frameName,id:frameName,src:hui.ui.context+'/hui/html/blank.html'});
9854 		iframe.style.display='none';
9855 		this.element.appendChild(iframe);
9856 		this.fileInput = hui.build('input',{'type':'file','class':'file','name':this.options.fieldName});
9857 		hui.listen(this.fileInput,'change',this.iframeSubmit.bind(this));
9858 		form.appendChild(this.fileInput);
9859 		var buttonContainer = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_upload_button'});
9860 		var span = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_upload_button_input'});
9861 		span.appendChild(form);
9862 		buttonContainer.appendChild(span);

9868 				buttonContainer.appendChild(w.element);
9869 			}.bind(this));
9870 		}

9872 	},

9874 	iframeUploadComplete : function() {
9875 		if (!this.uploading) return;
9876 		hui.log('iframeUploadComplete uploading: '+this.uploading+' ('+this.name+')');
9877 		this.uploading = false;
9878 		this.form.reset();
9879 		var doc = hui.getFrameDocument(this.iframe);
9880 		var last = this.items[this.items.length-1];
9881 		if (doc.body.innerHTML.indexOf('SUCCESS')!=-1) {
9882 			if (last) {
9883 				last.update({progress:1,filestatus:'Frdig'});
9884 			}
9885 			this.fire('uploadDidComplete',{}); // TODO: Send the correct file
9886 			hui.log('Iframe upload succeeded');
9887 		} else if (last) {
9888 			last.setError('Upload af filen fejlede!');
9889 			hui.log('Iframe upload failed!');
9890 			this.fire('uploadDidFail',{}); // TODO: Send the correct file
9891 		}
9892 		this.fire('uploadDidCompleteQueue');
9893 		this.iframe.src=hui.ui.context+'/hui/html/blank.html';
9894 		this.endIframeProgress();
9895 	},

9900 		// IE: set value of parms again since they disappear
9901 		if (hui.browser.msie) {

9903 				this.form[key].value = value;
9904 			}.bind(this));
9905 		}
9906 		this.form.submit();
9907 		this.fire('uploadDidStartQueue');
9908 		var fileName = this.fileInput.value.split('\\').pop();
9909 		this.addItem({name:fileName,filestatus:'I gang'}).setWaiting();
9910 		hui.log('Iframe upload started!');
9911 	},

9940 		var loc = new String(document.location);
9941 		var url = loc.slice(0,loc.lastIndexOf('/'));
9942 		while (relative.indexOf('../')===0) {
9943 			relative=relative.substring(3);
9944 			url = url.slice(0,url.lastIndexOf('/'));
9945 		}
9946 		url += '/'+relative;
9947 		return url;
9948 	},

9971 			this.element.appendChild(buttonContainer);
9972 		}
9973 		
9974 		var self = this;

9977 			flash_url : hui.ui.context+"/hui/lib/swfupload/swfupload.swf",

9983 			debug : true,

10099 			this.status.style.display='block';
10100 		}
10101 		hui.log(s);
10102 	}

10279 hui.ui.Gallery.prototype = {
10280 	setObjects : function(objects) {
10281 		this.objects = objects;
10282 		this.render();
10283 		this.fire('selectionReset');
10284 	},
10285 	getObjects : function() {
10286 		return this.objects;
10287 	},
10288 	/** @private */
10289 	$objectsLoaded : function(objects) {
10290 		this.setObjects(objects);
10291 	},
10292 	/** @private */
10293 	$itemsLoaded : function(objects) {
10294 		this.setObjects(objects);
10295 	},
10296 	/** @private */
10297 	render : function() {
10298 		this.nodes = [];
10299 		this.maxRevealed=0;
10300 		this.body.innerHTML='';
10301 		var self = this;
10302 		hui.each(this.objects,function(object,i) {
10303 			var url = self.resolveImageUrl(object),
10304 				top = 0;
10305 			if (url!==null) {
10306 				url = url.replace(/&/,'&');
10307 			}
10308 			if (!self.revealing && object.height<object.width) {
10309 				top = (self.height-(self.height*object.height/object.width))/2;
10310 			}
10311 			var img = hui.build('img',{style:'margin:'+top+'px auto 0px'});
10312 			img.setAttribute(self.revealing ? 'data-src' : 'src', url );
10313 			if (self.revealing) {
10314 			//	img.style.visibility='hidden';
10315 			}
10316 			var item = hui.build('div',{'class' : 'hui_gallery_item',style:'width:'+self.width+'px; height:'+self.height+'px'});
10317 			item.appendChild(img);
10318 			hui.listen(item,'click',function() {
10319 				self.itemClicked(i);
10320 			});
10321 			item.dragDropInfo = {kind:'image',icon:'common/image',id:object.id,title:object.name || object.title};
10322 			item.onmousedown=function(e) {
10323 				hui.ui.startDrag(e,item);
10324 				return false;
10325 			};
10326 			hui.listen(item,'dblclick',function() {
10327 				self.itemDoubleClicked(i);
10328 			});
10329 			self.body.appendChild(item);
10330 			self.nodes.push(item);
10331 		});
10332 		this._reveal();
10333 	},
10334 	$$layout : function() {
10335 		if (this.nodes.length>0) {
10336 			this._reveal();
10337 		}
10338 	},
10339 	_reveal : function() {
10340 		if (!this.revealing) {return}
10341 		var container = this.element.parentNode;
10342 		var limit = container.scrollTop+container.clientHeight;
10343 		if (limit<=this.maxRevealed) {
10344 			return;
10345 		}
10346 		this.maxRevealed = limit;
10347 		for (var i=0,l=this.nodes.length; i < l; i++) {
10348 			var item = this.nodes[i];
10349 			if (item.revealed) {continue}
10350 			if (item.offsetTop<limit) {
10351 				var img = item.getElementsByTagName('img')[0];
10352 				item.className = 'hui_gallery_item hui_gallery_item_busy';
10353 				var self = this;
10354 				img.onload = function() {
10355 					this.parentNode.className = 'hui_gallery_item';
10356 					if (this.height<this.width) {
10357 						var top = (self.height-(self.height*this.height/this.width))/2;
10358 						this.style.marginTop = top+'px';
10359 					}
10360 				}
10361 				img.onerror = function() {
10362 					this.parentNode.className = 'hui_gallery_item hui_gallery_item_error';
10363 				}
10364 				img.src = img.getAttribute('data-src');
10365 				item.revealed = true;
10366 			}
10367 		};
10368 	},
10369 	/** @private */
10370 	updateUI : function() {
10371 		var s = this.selected;
10372 		for (var i=0; i < this.nodes.length; i++) {
10373 			hui.setClass(this.nodes[i],'hui_gallery_item_selected',hui.inArray(s,i));
10374 		};
10375 	},
10376 	/** @private */
10377 	resolveImageUrl : function(img) {
10378 		return hui.ui.resolveImageUrl(this,img,this.width,this.height);
10379 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
10380 			if (this.delegates[i]['$resolveImageUrl']) {
10381 				return this.delegates[i]['$resolveImageUrl'](img,this.width,this.height);
10382 			}
10383 		};
10384 		return '';
10385 	},
10386 	/** @private */
10387 	itemClicked : function(index) {
10388 		if (this.busy) {
10389 			return;
10390 		}
10391 		this.selected = [index];
10392 		this.fire('selectionChanged');
10393 		this.updateUI();
10394 	},
10395 	getFirstSelection : function() {
10396 		if (this.selected.length>0) {
10397 			return this.objects[this.selected[0]];

10463 hui.ui.Calendar.prototype = {
10464 	show : function() {

10477 		date.setHours(0);
10478 		date.setMinutes(0);
10479 		date.setSeconds(0);
10480 		return date;
10481 	},
10482 	/** @private */

10484 		var date = new Date(this.date.getTime());
10485 		date.setDate(date.getDate()-date.getDay()+7);
10486 		date.setHours(23);
10487 		date.setMinutes(59);
10488 		date.setSeconds(59);
10489 		return date;
10490 	},
10491 	clearEvents : function() {
10492 		this.events = [];
10493 		var nodes = hui.byClass(this.element,'hui_calendar_event');
10494 		for (var i=0; i < nodes.length; i++) {
10495 			hui.dom.remove(nodes[i]);
10496 		};
10497 		this.hideEventViewer();
10498 	},
10499 	$objectsLoaded : function(data) {
10500 		try {
10501 			this.setEvents(data);
10502 		} catch (e) {
10503 			hui.log(e);
10504 		}
10505 	},
10506 	$sourceIsBusy : function() {
10507 		this.setBusy(true);
10508 	},
10509 	$sourceShouldRefresh : function() {
10510 		return this.element.style.display!='none';
10511 	},
10512 	setEvents : function(events) {
10513 		events = events || [];
10514 		for (var i=0; i < events.length; i++) {
10515 			var e = events[i];
10516 			if (typeof(e.startTime)!='object') {
10517 				e.startTime = new Date(parseInt(e.startTime)*1000);
10518 			}
10519 			if (typeof(e.endTime)!='object') {
10520 				e.endTime = new Date(parseInt(e.endTime)*1000);
10521 			}
10522 		};
10523 		this.setBusy(false);
10524 		this.clearEvents();
10525 		this.events = events;
10526 		var self = this;
10527 		var pixels = (this.options.endHour-this.options.startHour)*40;
10528 		var week = this.getFirstDay().getWeekOfYear();
10529 		var year = this.getFirstDay().getYear();
10530 		hui.each(this.events,function(event) {
10531 			var day = hui.byClass(self.body,'hui_calendar_day')[event.startTime.getDay()-1];
10532 			if (!day) {
10533 				return;
10534 			}
10535 			if (event.startTime.getWeekOfYear()!=week || event.startTime.getYear()!=year) {
10536 				return;
10537 			}
10538 			var node = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_calendar_event',parent:day});
10539 			var top = ((event.startTime.getHours()*60+event.startTime.getMinutes())/60-self.options.startHour)*40-1;
10540 			var height = (event.endTime.getTime()-event.startTime.getTime())/1000/60/60*40+1;
10541 			height = Math.min(pixels-top,height);
10542 			hui.setStyle(node,{'marginTop':top+'px','height':height+'px',visibility:'hidden'});
10543 			var content = hui.build('div',{parent:node});
10544 			hui.build('p',{'class':'hui_calendar_event_time',text:event.startTime.dateFormat('H:i'),parent:content});
10545 			hui.build('p',{'class':'hui_calendar_event_text',text:event.text,parent:content});
10546 			if (event.location) {
10547 				hui.build('p',{'class':'hui_calendar_event_location',text:event.location,parent:content});
10548 			}
10549 			
10550 			window.setTimeout(function() {
10551 				hui.ui.bounceIn(node);
10552 			},Math.random()*200)
10553 			hui.listen(node,'click',function() {
10554 				self.eventWasClicked(node);
10555 			});
10556 		});
10557 	},

10561 	},

10705 hui.ui.DatePicker = function(options) {

10712 	this.today = new Date();

10721 hui.ui.DatePicker.create = function(options) {
10722 	var element = options.element = hui.build('div',{
10723 		'class' : 'hui_datepicker',
10724 		html : '<div class="hui_datepicker_header"><a class="hui_datepicker_next"></a><a class="hui_datepicker_previous"></a><strong></strong></div>'
10725 		}),
10726 		table = hui.build('table',{parent:element}),
10727 		thead = hui.build('thead',{parent:table}),
10728 		head = hui.build('tr',{parent:thead});
10729 	for (var i=0;i<7;i++) {
10730 		head.appendChild(hui.build('th',{text:Date.dayNames[i].substring(0,3)}));
10731 	}
10732 	var body = hui.build('tbody',{parent:table});
10733 	for (var j=0;j<6;j++) {
10734 		var row = hui.build('tr',{parent:body});
10735 		for (var k=0;k<7;k++) {
10736 			hui.build('td',{parent:row});
10737 		}
10738 	}
10739 	return new hui.ui.DatePicker(options);
10740 }

10742 hui.ui.DatePicker.prototype = {
10743 	_addBehavior : function() {
10744 		var self = this;
10745 		this.cells = hui.byTag(this.element,'td');
10746 		hui.each(this.cells,function(cell,index) {
10747 			hui.listen(cell,'mousedown',function() {self._selectCell(index)});
10748 		})
10749 		var next = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_datepicker_next');
10750 		var previous = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_datepicker_previous');
10751 		hui.listen(next,'mousedown',function() {self.next()});
10752 		hui.listen(previous,'mousedown',function() {self.previous()});
10753 	},
10754 	/** Set the date
10755 	  * @param date The js Date to set
10756 	  */
10757 	setValue : function(date) {
10758 		this.value = new Date(date.getTime());
10759 		this.viewDate = new Date(date.getTime());
10760 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
10761 		this._updateUI();
10762 	},
10763 	_updateUI : function() {
10764 		hui.dom.setText(this.title,this.viewDate.dateFormat('F Y'));
10765 		var isSelectedYear =  this.value.getFullYear()==this.viewDate.getFullYear();
10766 		var month = this.viewDate.getMonth();
10767 		for (var i=0; i < this.cells.length; i++) {
10768 			var date = this._indexToDate(i);
10769 			var cell = this.cells[i];
10770 			if (date.getMonth()<month) {
10771 				cell.className = 'hui_datepicker_dimmed';
10772 			} else if (date.getMonth()>month) {
10773 				cell.className = 'hui_datepicker_dimmed';
10774 			} else {
10775 				cell.className = '';
10776 			}
10777 			if (date.getDate()==this.value.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.value.getMonth() && isSelectedYear) {
10778 				hui.addClass(cell,'hui_datepicker_selected');
10779 			}
10780 			if (date.getDate()==this.today.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.today.getMonth() && date.getFullYear()==this.today.getFullYear()) {
10781 				hui.addClass(cell,'hui_datepicker_today');
10782 			}
10783 			hui.dom.setText(cell,date.getDate());
10784 		};
10785 	},
10786 	_getPreviousMonth : function() {
10787 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
10788 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()-1);
10789 		return previous;
10790 	},
10791 	_getNextMonth : function() {
10792 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
10793 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()+1);
10794 		return previous;
10795 	},
10796 
10797 	////////////////// Events ///////////////
10798 	/** Change to previous month */
10799 	previous : function() {
10800 		this.viewDate = this._getPreviousMonth();
10801 		this._updateUI();
10802 	},
10803 	/** Change to next month */
10804 	next : function() {
10805 		this.viewDate = this._getNextMonth();
10806 		this._updateUI();
10807 	},
10808 	_selectCell : function(index) {
10809 		this.value = this._indexToDate(index);
10810 		this.viewDate = new Date(this.value.getTime());
10811 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
10812 		this._updateUI();
10813 		hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'dateChanged',this.value);
10814 	},
10815 	_indexToDate : function(index) {
10816 		var first = this.viewDate.getDay(),
10817 			days = this.viewDate.getDaysInMonth(),
10818 			previousDays = this._getPreviousMonth().getDaysInMonth(),
10819 			date;
10820 		if (index<first) {
10821 			date = this._getPreviousMonth();
10822 			date.setDate(previousDays-first+index+1);
10823 		} else if (index>first+days-1) {
10824 			date = this._getPreviousMonth();
10825 			date.setDate(index-first-days+1);
10826 		} else {
10827 			date = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
10828 			date.setDate(index+1-first);
10829 		}
10830 		return date;
10831 	}
10832 }

10867 hui.ui.Layout.prototype = {
10868 	$$layout : function() {
10869 		if (hui.browser.gecko) {
10870 			var center = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_layout_center');
10871 			if (center) {
10872 				center.style.height='100%';
10873 			}
10874 		}
10875 		if (!hui.browser.msie7 && !hui.browser.msie8 && !hui.browser.msie9) {
10876 			return;
10877 		}
10878 		if (this.diff===undefined) {
10879 			var head = hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_layout_top');
10880 			var top = hui.firstByTag(head,'*').clientHeight;
10881 			var foot = hui.firstByTag(hui.firstByTag(this.element,'tfoot'),'td');
10882 			var bottom = 0;
10883 			if (foot) {
10884 				bottom = hui.firstByTag(foot,'*').clientHeight;
10885 			}
10886 			top += hui.getTop(this.element);
10887 			this.diff = bottom+top;
10888 			if (this.element.parentNode!==document.body) {
10889 				this.diff+=15;
10890 			} else {
10891 			}
10892 		}
10893 		var tbody = hui.firstByTag(this.element,'tbody');
10894 		var cell = hui.firstByTag(tbody,'td');
10895 		cell.style.height = (hui.getViewPortHeight()-this.diff+5)+'px';
10896 	}
10897 };

10956 	//	this.iframe.contentWindow.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function() {this._load();hui.log('Fast path!')}.bind(this));
10957 	//}
10958 	this.name = options.name;
10959 	hui.ui.extend(this);
10960 	this.diff = -69;
10961 	if (this.options.tabs) {
10962 		this.diff-=15;
10963 	}
10964 	this.busy = true;
10965 	hui.ui.listen(this);
10966 }

11115 hui.ui.Wizard.prototype = {
11116 	/** @private */
11117 	addBehavior : function() {
11118 		var self = this;
11119 		hui.each(this.anchors,function(node,i) {
11120 			hui.listen(node,'mousedown',function(e) {
11121 				hui.stop(e);
11122 				self.goToStep(i)
11123 			});
11124 			hui.listen(node,'click',function(e) {
11125 				hui.stop(e);
11126 			});
11127 		});
11128 	},
11129 	/** Goes to the step with the index */
11130 	goToStep : function(index) {
11131 		var c = this.container;
11132 		c.style.height=c.clientHeight+'px';
11133 		hui.removeClass(this.anchors[this.selected],'hui_selected');
11134 		this.steps[this.selected].style.display='none';
11135 		hui.addClass(this.anchors[index],'hui_selected');
11136 		this.steps[index].style.display='block';
11137 		this.selected=index;
11138 		hui.ani(c,'height',this.steps[index].clientHeight+'px',500,{ease:hui.ease.slowFastSlow,onComplete:function() {
11139 			c.style.height='';
11140 		}});
11141 		hui.ui.callVisible(this);
11142 	},
11143 	/** Goes to the next step */
11144 	next : function() {
11145 		if (this.selected<this.steps.length-1) {
11146 			this.goToStep(this.selected+1);
11147 		}
11148 	},
11149 	/** Goes to the previous step */
11150 	previous : function() {
11151 		if (this.selected>0) {
11152 			this.goToStep(this.selected-1);
11153 		}
11154 	}
11155 }

11209 hui.ui.TextField = function(options) {

11212 	this.element.setAttribute('autocomplete','off');

11214 	this.isPassword = this.element.type=='password';
11215 	this.name = options.name;
11216 	hui.ui.extend(this);
11217 	this.addBehavior();
11218 	if (this.options.placeholderElement && this.value!='') {
11219 		hui.ui.fadeOut(this.options.placeholderElement,0);
11220 	}
11221 	this.checkPlaceholder();
11222 	try { // IE hack
11223 		if (e==document.activeElement) {
11224 			this.focused();
11225 		}
11226 	} catch (e) {}

11229 hui.ui.TextField.prototype = {
11230 	addBehavior : function() {
11231 		var e = this.element;
11232 		hui.listen(e,'keyup',this.keyDidStrike.bind(this));
11233 		var p = this.options.placeholderElement;
11234 		hui.listen(e,'blur',this.onBlur.bind(this));
11235 		if (p) {
11236 			hui.listen(e,'focus',this.focused.bind(this));
11237 			hui.listen(e,'blur',this.checkPlaceholder.bind(this));
11238 			if (p) {
11239 				p.style.cursor='text';
11240 				hui.listen(p,'mousedown',this.focus.bind(this));
11241 				hui.listen(p,'click',this.focus.bind(this));
11242 			}
11243 		}
11244 	},
11245 	focused : function() {
11246 		var e = this.element,p = this.options.placeholderElement;
11247 		if (p && e.value=='') {
11248 			hui.ui.fadeOut(p,0);
11249 		}
11250 	},
11251 	/** @private */
11252 	validate : function(value) {
11253 		var validator = this.options.validator, result;
11254 		if (validator) {
11255 			result = validator.validate(value);
11256 			hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_invalid',!result.valid);
11257 			return result.value;
11258 		}
11259 		return value;
11260 	},
11261 	checkPlaceholder : function() {
11262 		if (this.options.placeholderElement && this.value=='') {
11263 			hui.ui.fadeIn(this.options.placeholderElement,200);
11264 		}
11265 		if (this.isPassword && !hui.browser.msie) {
11266 			this.element.type='password';
11267 		}
11268 	},
11269 	/** @private */
11270 	keyDidStrike : function() {
11271 		if (this.value!==this.element.value) {
11272 			var newValue = this.validate(this.element.value);
11273 			var changed = newValue!==this.value;
11274 			this.value = newValue;
11275 			if (changed) {
11276 				this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
11277 			}
11278 		}
11279 	},
11280 	/** @private */
11281 	onBlur : function() {
11282 		hui.removeClass(this.element,'hui_invalid');
11283 		this.element.value = this.value || '';
11284 	},
11285 	getValue : function() {
11286 		return this.value;
11287 	},
11288 	setValue : function(value) {
11289 		if (value===undefined || value===null) {
11290 			value='';
11291 		}
11292 		this.element.value = value;
11293 		this.value = this.validate(value);
11294 	},
11295 	isEmpty : function() {
11296 		return this.value=='';
11297 	},
11298 	isBlank : function() {
11299 		return this.value.strip()=='';
11300 	},
11301 	focus : function() {
11302 		this.element.focus();
11303 	},
11304 	setError : function(error) {
11305 		var isError = error ? true : false;
11306 		hui.setClass(this.element,'hui_field_error',isError);
11307 		if (typeof(error) == 'string') {
11308 			hui.ui.showToolTip({text:error,element:this.element,key:this.name});
11309 		}
11310 		if (!isError) {
11311 			hui.ui.hideToolTip({key:this.name});
11312 		}
11313 	}
11314 };

11337 hui.ui.InfoView.prototype = {
11338 	addHeader : function(text) {
11339 		var row = hui.build('tr',{parent:this.body});
11340 		hui.build('th',{'class' : 'hui_infoview_header',colspan:'2',text:text,parent:row});
11341 	},
11342 	addProperty : function(label,text) {
11343 		var row = hui.build('tr',{parent:this.body});
11344 		hui.build('th',{parent:row,text:label});
11345 		hui.build('td',{parent:row,text:text});
11346 	},
11347 	addObjects : function(label,objects) {
11348 		if (!objects || objects.length==0) return;
11349 		var row = hui.build('tr',{parent:this.body});
11350 		row.appendChild(hui.build('th',{text:label}));
11351 		var cell = hui.build('td',{parent:row});
11352 		var click = this.options.clickObjects;
11353 		hui.each(objects,function(obj) {
11354 			var node = hui.build('div',{text:obj.title,parent:cell});
11355 			if (click) {
11356 				hui.addClass(node,'hui_infoview_click')
11357 				hui.listen(node,'click',function() {
11358 					hui.ui.callDelegates(this,'objectWasClicked',obj);
11359 				});
11360 			}
11361 		});
11362 	},
11363 	setBusy : function(busy) {
11364 		hui.setClass(this,element,'hui_infoview_busy',busy);
11365 	},
11366 	clear : function() {
11367 		hui.dom.clear(this.body);
11368 	},
11369 	update : function(data) {
11370 		this.clear();
11371 		for (var i=0; i < data.length; i++) {
11372 			switch (data[i].type) {
11373 				case 'header': this.addHeader(data[i].value); break;
11374 				case 'property': this.addProperty(data[i].label,data[i].value); break;
11375 				case 'objects': this.addObjects(data[i].label,data[i].value); break;
11376 			}
11377 		};
11378 	}
11379 }

11402 hui.ui.Overflow.prototype = {
11403 	calculate : function() {
11404 		var top,bottom,parent,viewport;
11405 		viewport = hui.getViewPortHeight();
11406 		parent = this.element.parentNode;
11407 		top = hui.getTop(this.element);
11408 		bottom = hui.getTop(parent)+parent.clientHeight;
11409 		var sibs = hui.getAllNext(this.element);
11410 		for (var i=0; i < sibs.length; i++) {
11411 			bottom-=sibs[i].clientHeight;
11412 		};
11413 		this.diff=-1*(top+(viewport-bottom));
11414 		if (hui.browser.webkit) {
11415 			this.diff++;
11416 		}
11417 	},
11418 	add : function(widgetOrNode) {
11419 		if (widgetOrNode.getElement) {
11420 			this.element.appendChild(widgetOrNode.getElement());
11421 		} else {
11422 			this.element.appendChild(widgetOrNode);
11423 		}
11424 		return this;
11425 	},
11426 	$$layout : function() {
11427 		var height;
11428 		if (!this.options.dynamic) {
11429 			if (this.options.vertical) {
11430 				height = hui.getViewPortHeight();
11431 				this.element.style.height = Math.max(0,height-this.options.vertical)+'px';
11432 			}
11433 			return;
11434 		}
11435 		if (this.diff===undefined) {
11436 			this.calculate();
11437 		}
11438 		height = hui.getViewPortHeight();
11439 		this.element.style.height = Math.max(0,height+this.diff)+'px';
11440 	}
11441 }

11469 hui.ui.SearchField.prototype = {

11478 		hui.listen(this.element,'mouseup',focus);

11496 			}

11498 				hui.ani(self.element,'width',self.initialWidth+'px',500,{ease:hui.ease.slowFastSlow,delay:100});
11499 			}
11500 		}
11501 	},

11503 		this.fieldChanged();

11505 			this.fire('submit');
11506 		}
11507 	},
11508 	setValue : function(value) {
11509 		this.field.value=value===undefined || value===null ? '' : value;
11510 		this.fieldChanged();

11517 	},
11518 	isBlank : function() {
11519 		return this.field.value.strip()=='';
11520 	},
11521 	reset : function() {
11522 		this.field.value='';
11523 		this.fieldChanged();
11524 	},
11525 	/** @private */
11526 	updateClass : function() {
11527 		var className = 'hui_searchfield';
11528 		if (this.adaptive) {
11529 			className+=' hui_searchfield_adaptive';
11530 		}
11531 		if (this.focused && this.value!='') {
11532 			className+=' hui_searchfield_focus_dirty';
11533 		} else if (this.focused) {
11534 			className+=' hui_searchfield_focus';
11535 		} else if (this.value!='') {
11536 			className+=' hui_searchfield_dirty';
11537 		}
11538 		this.element.className=className;
11539 	},
11540 	/** @private */
11541 	fieldChanged : function() {
11542 		if (this.field.value!=this.value) {
11543 			this.value=this.field.value;
11544 			this.updateClass();
11545 			this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
11546 			hui.ui.firePropertyChange(this,'value',this.value);
11547 		}
11548 	}
11549 }

11585 hui.ui.LocationPicker.prototype = {
11586 	show : function(options) {
11587 		if (!this.panel) {
11588 			var panel = this.panel = hui.ui.BoundPanel.create({width:300});
11589 			var mapContainer = hui.build('div',{style:'width:300px;height:300px'});
11590 			panel.add(mapContainer);
11591 			var buttons = hui.ui.Buttons.create({align:'right',top:5});
11592 			var button = hui.ui.Button.create({text:'Luk'});
11593 			button.listen({$click:function() {panel.hide()}});
11594 			panel.add(buttons.add(button));
11595 			hui.setStyle(panel.element,{left:'-10000px',top:'-10000px',display:''});
11596 		    var mapOptions = {
11597 		      zoom: 15,
11598 		      mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.TERRAIN
11599 		    }
11600 		    this.map = new google.maps.Map(mapContainer, mapOptions);
11601 			google.maps.event.addListener(this.map, 'click', function(obj) {
11602 				var loc = {latitude:obj.latLng.lat(),longitude:obj.latLng.lng()};
11603     			this.setLocation(loc);
11604 				this.fire('locationChanged',loc);
11605   			}.bind(this));
11606 			panel.element.style.display = 'none';
11607 		}
11608 		this.setLocation(options.location);
11609 		if (options.node) {
11610 			this.panel.position(options.node);
11611 		}
11612 		this.panel.show();
11613 	},
11614 	setLocation : function(loc) {
11615 		if (!loc && this.marker) {
11616 			this.marker.setMap(null);
11617 			this.map.setCenter(this.defaultCenter);
11618 			return;
11619 		}
11620 		loc = this.buildLatLng(loc);
11621 		if (!this.marker) {
11622 		    this.marker = new google.maps.Marker({
11623 		        position: loc, 
11624 		        map: this.map
11625 		    });
11626 		} else {
11627     		this.marker.setPosition(loc);
11628 			this.marker.setMap(this.map);
11629 		}
11630 		this.map.setCenter(loc);
11631 	},
11632 	/** @private */
11633 	buildLatLng : function(loc) {
11634 		if (!loc) {
11635 			loc = {latitude:57.0465, longitude:9.9185};
11636 		}
11637 		return new google.maps.LatLng(loc.latitude, loc.longitude);
11638 	}
11639 }

11790 hui.ui.VideoPlayer.prototype = {
11791 	setVideo : function(video) {
11792 		if (this.placeholder) {
11793 			this.placeholder.style.display='none';
11794 		}
11795 		this.handler = this.getHandler(video);
11796 		this.element.appendChild(this.handler.element);
11797 		if (this.handler.showController()) {
11798 			this.buildController();
11799 		}
11800 	},
11801 	getHandler : function(video) {
11802 		for (var i=0; i < this.handlers.length; i++) {
11803 			var handler = this.handlers[i];
11804 			if (handler.isSupported(video)) {
11805 				return new handler(video,this);
11806 			}
11807 		};
11808 	},
11809 	buildController : function() {
11810 		var e = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_videoplayer_controller',parent:this.element});
11811 		this.playButton = hui.build('a',{href:'javascript:void(0);','class':'hui_videoplayer_playpause',text:'wait!',parent:e});
11812 		hui.listen(this.playButton,'click',this.playPause.bind(this));
11813 		this.status = hui.build('span',{'class':'hui_videoplayer_status',parent:e});
11814 	},
11815 	onCanPlay : function() {
11816 		this.playButton.update('Play');
11817 	},
11818 	onLoad : function() {
11819 		this.state.loaded = this.state.duration;
11820 		this.updateStatus();
11821 	},
11822 	onDurationChange : function(duration) {
11823 		this.state.duration = duration;
11824 		this.updateStatus();
11825 	},
11826 	onTimeChange : function(time) {
11827 		this.state.time = time;
11828 		this.updateStatus();
11829 	},
11830 	onLoadProgressChange : function(progress) {
11831 		this.state.loaded = progress;
11832 		this.updateStatus();
11833 	},
11834 	playPause : function() {
11835 		if (this.handler.isPlaying()) {
11836 			this.pause();
11837 		} else {
11838 			this.play();
11839 		}
11840 	},
11841 	play : function() {
11842 		this.handler.play();
11843 	},
11844 	pause : function() {
11845 		this.handler.pause();
11846 	},
11847 	updateStatus : function() {
11848 		this.status.innerHTML = this.state.time+' / '+this.state.duration+' / '+this.state.loaded;
11849 	}
11850 }

11979 hui.ui.Segmented = function(options) {
11980 	this.options = hui.override({value:null,allowNull:false},options);
11981 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
11982 	this.name = options.name;
11983 	this.value = this.options.value;
11984 	hui.ui.extend(this);
11985 	hui.listen(this.element,'mousedown',this.onClick.bind(this));

11988 hui.ui.Segmented.prototype = {
11989 	/** @private */
11990 	onClick : function(e) {
11991 		e = new hui.Event(e);
11992 		var a = e.findByTag('a');
11993 		if (a) {
11994 			var changed = false;
11995 			var value = a.getAttribute('rel');
11996 			var x = hui.byClass(this.element,'hui_segmented_selected');
11997 			for (var i=0; i < x.length; i++) {
11998 				hui.removeClass(x[i],'hui_segmented_selected');
11999 			};
12000 			if (value===this.value && this.options.allowNull) {
12001 				changed=true;
12002 				this.value = null;
12003 				this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
12004 			} else {
12005 				hui.addClass(a,'hui_segmented_selected');
12006 				changed=this.value!== value;
12007 				this.value = value;
12008 			}
12009 			if (changed) {
12010 				this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
12011 			}
12012 		}
12013 	},
12014 	setValue : function(value) {
12015 		if (value===undefined) {
12016 			value=null;
12017 		}
12018 		var as = this.element.getElementsByTagName('a');
12019 		this.value = null;
12020 		for (var i=0; i < as.length; i++) {
12021 			if (as[i].getAttribute('rel')===value) {
12022 				hui.addClass(as[i],'hui_segmented_selected');
12023 				this.value=value;
12024 			} else {
12025 				hui.removeClass(as[i],'hui_segmented_selected');
12026 			}
12027 		};
12028 	},
12029 	getValue : function() {
12030 		return this.value;
12031 	}
12032 }
12033 
12034 /* EOF *//** @namespace */
12035 hui.ui.Flash = {
12036 	
12037 	fullVersion:undefined,
12038 	
12039 	/** Gets the major version of flash */
12040 	getMajorVersion : function() {
12041 		var full = this.getFullVersion();
12042 		if (full===null || full===undefined) {
12043 			return null;
12044 		}
12045 		var matched = (full+'').match(/[0-9]+/gi);
12046 		return matched.length>0 ? parseInt(matched[0]) : null;
12047 	},
12048 	
12049 	getFullVersion : function() {
12050 		if (this.fullVersion!==undefined) {
12051 			return this.fullVersion;
12052 		}
12053 		// NS/Opera version >= 3 check for Flash plugin in plugin array
12054 		var flashVer = null;
12055 	
12056 		if (navigator.plugins != null && navigator.plugins.length > 0) {
12057 			if (navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash 2.0"] || navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash"]) {
12058 				var swVer2 = navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash 2.0"] ? " 2.0" : "";
12059 				var flashDescription = navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash" + swVer2].description;
12060 				var descArray = flashDescription.split(" ");
12061 				var tempArrayMajor = descArray[2].split(".");			
12062 				var versionMajor = tempArrayMajor[0];
12063 				var versionMinor = tempArrayMajor[1];
12064 				var versionRevision = descArray[3];
12065 				if (versionRevision == "") {
12066 					versionRevision = descArray[4];
12067 				}
12068 				if (versionRevision[0] == "d") {
12069 					versionRevision = versionRevision.substring(1);
12070 				} else if (versionRevision[0] == "r") {
12071 					versionRevision = versionRevision.substring(1);
12072 					if (versionRevision.indexOf("d") > 0) {
12073 						versionRevision = versionRevision.substring(0, versionRevision.indexOf("d"));
12074 					}
12075 				}
12076 				flashVer = versionMajor + "." + versionMinor + "." + versionRevision;
12077 			}
12078 		}
12079 		// MSN/WebTV 2.6 supports Flash 4
12080 		else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("webtv/2.6") != -1) flashVer = 4;
12081 		// WebTV 2.5 supports Flash 3
12082 		else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("webtv/2.5") != -1) flashVer = 3;
12083 		// older WebTV supports Flash 2
12084 		else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("webtv") != -1) flashVer = 2;
12085 		else if ( hui.browser.msie ) {
12086 			flashVer = this.getActiveXVersion();
12087 		}
12088 		this.fullVersion = flashVer;
12089 		return flashVer;
12090 	},
12091 	/** @private */
12092 	getActiveXVersion : function() {
12093 		var version;
12094 		var axo;
12095 		var e;
12096 
12097 		// NOTE : new ActiveXObject(strFoo) throws an exception if strFoo isn't in the registry
12098 
12099 		try {
12100 			// version will be set for 7.X or greater players
12101 			axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.7");
12102 			version = axo.GetVariable("$version");
12103 		} catch (e) {
12104 		}
12105 
12106 		if (!version)
12107 		{
12108 			try {
12109 				// version will be set for 6.X players only
12110 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.6");
12111 			
12112 				// installed player is some revision of 6.0
12113 				// GetVariable("$version") crashes for versions 6.0.22 through 6.0.29,
12114 				// so we have to be careful. 
12115 			
12116 				// default to the first public version
12117 				version = "WIN 6,0,21,0";
12118 
12119 				// throws if AllowScripAccess does not exist (introduced in 6.0r47)		
12120 				axo.AllowScriptAccess = "always";
12121 
12122 				// safe to call for 6.0r47 or greater
12123 				version = axo.GetVariable("$version");
12124 
12125 			} catch (e) {
12126 			}
12127 		}
12128 
12129 		if (!version)
12130 		{
12131 			try {
12132 				// version will be set for 4.X or 5.X player
12133 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.3");
12134 				version = axo.GetVariable("$version");
12135 			} catch (e) {
12136 			}
12137 		}
12138 
12139 		if (!version)
12140 		{
12141 			try {
12142 				// version will be set for 3.X player
12143 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.3");
12144 				version = "WIN 3,0,18,0";
12145 			} catch (e) {
12146 			}
12147 		}
12148 
12149 		if (!version)
12150 		{
12151 			try {
12152 				// version will be set for 2.X player
12153 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash");
12154 				version = "WIN 2,0,0,11";
12155 			} catch (e) {
12156 				version = -1;
12157 			}
12158 		}
12159 	
12160 		return version;
12161 	}
12162 }

12205 hui.ui.Links.prototype = {
12206 	addBehavior : function() {
12207 		hui.listen(this.element,'click',this.onClick.bind(this));
12208 		hui.listen(this.element,'dblclick',this.onDblClick.bind(this));
12209 	},
12210 	reset : function() {
12211 		this.setValue([]);
12212 	},
12213 	setValue : function(items) {
12214 		this.items = items;
12215 		this.selectedIndex = null;
12216 		this.build();
12217 	},
12218 	getValue : function() {
12219 		return this.items;
12220 	},
12221 	onDblClick : function(e) {
12222 		e = new hui.Event(e);
12223 		hui.selection.clear();
12224 		e.stop(e);
12225 		var link = this.selectAndGetRow(e);
12226 		var values = {text:link.text};
12227 		values[link.kind]=link.value;
12228 		this.editedLink = link;
12229 		var win = this.getEditWindow();
12230 		this.editForm.reset();
12231 		this.editForm.setValues(values);
12232 		win.show();
12233 	},
12234 	onClick : function(e) {
12235 		e = new hui.Event(e);
12236 		e.stop();
12237 		var element = e.getElement();
12238 		if (hui.hasClass(element,'hui_links_remove')) {
12239 			var row = e.findByClass('hui_links_row');
12240 			hui.ui.confirmOverlay({element:element,text:'Vil du fjerne linket?',okText:'Ja, fjern',cancelText:'Annuller',onOk:function() {
12241 				this.items.splice(row.hui_index,1);
12242 				if (this.selectedIndex===row.hui_index) {
12243 					this.selectedIndex=null;
12244 				}
12245 				this.build();				
12246 			}.bind(this)});
12247 		} else {
12248 			this.selectAndGetRow(e);
12249 		}
12250 	},
12251 	selectAndGetRow : function(event) {
12252 		var row = event.findByClass('hui_links_row');
12253 		if (row) {
12254 			var idx = row.hui_index;
12255 			if (this.selectedIndex!==null) {
12256 				var x = hui.byClass(this.element,'hui_links_row')[this.selectedIndex];
12257 				hui.removeClass(x,'hui_links_row_selected')
12258 			}
12259 			this.selectedIndex = idx;
12260 			hui.addClass(row,'hui_links_row_selected');
12261 			return this.items[idx];
12262 		}
12263 	},
12264 	build : function() {
12265 		var list = this.list || hui.firstByClass(this.element,'hui_links_list'),
12266 			i,item,row,infoNode,text,remove;
12267 		list.innerHTML='';
12268 		for (i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
12269 			item = this.items[i];
12270 			row = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_links_row'});
12271 			row.hui_index = i;
12272 			
12273 			row.appendChild(hui.ui.createIcon(item.icon,1));
12274 			text = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_links_text',text:item.text});
12275 			row.appendChild(text);
12276 
12277 			infoNode = hui.build('div',{'class':'hui_links_info',text:hui.wrap(item.info)});
12278 			row.appendChild(infoNode);
12279 			remove = hui.ui.createIcon('monochrome/round_x',1);
12280 			hui.addClass(remove,'hui_links_remove');
12281 			row.appendChild(remove);
12282 
12283 			list.appendChild(row);
12284 		};
12285 	},
12286 	addLink : function() {
12287 		this.editedLink = null;
12288 		this.getEditWindow().show();
12289 		this.editForm.reset();
12290 		this.editForm.focus();
12291 	},
12292 	getEditWindow : function() {
12293 		if (!this.editWindow) {
12294 			var win = this.editWindow = hui.ui.Window.create({title:'Link',width:300,padding:5});
12295 			var form = this.editForm = hui.ui.Formula.create();
12296 			var g = form.buildGroup({above:false},[
12297 				{type:'Text',options:{label:'Tekst',key:'text'}}
12298 			]);
12299 			
12300 			var url = hui.ui.Formula.Text.create({label:'URL',key:'url'});
12301 			g.add(url);
12302 			this.inputs['url']=url;
12303 			
12304 			var email = hui.ui.Formula.Text.create({label:'E-mail',key:'email'});
12305 			g.add(email);
12306 			this.inputs['email']=email;
12307 			
12308 			page = hui.ui.Formula.DropDown.create({label:'Side',key:'page',source:this.options.pageSource});
12309 			g.add(page);
12310 			this.inputs['page']=page;
12311 			
12312 			file = hui.ui.Formula.DropDown.create({label:'Fil',key:'file',source:this.options.fileSource});
12313 			g.add(file);
12314 			this.inputs['file']=file;
12315 			
12316 			var self = this;
12317 			hui.each(this.inputs,function(key,value) {
12318 				value.listen({$valueChanged:function(){self.changeType(key)}});
12319 			});
12320 			
12321 			g.createButtons().add(hui.ui.Button.create({text:'Gem',submit:true,highlighted:true}));
12322 			this.editForm.listen({$submit:this.saveLink.bind(this)});
12323 			win.add(form);
12324 			if (this.options.pageSource) {
12325 				this.options.pageSource.refresh();
12326 			}
12327 			if (this.options.fileSource) {
12328 				this.options.fileSource.refresh();
12329 			}
12330 		}
12331 		return this.editWindow;
12332 	},
12333 	saveLink : function() {
12334 		var v = this.editForm.getValues();
12335 		var link = this.valuesToLink(v);
12336 		var edited = this.editedLink;
12337 		if (edited) {
12338 			hui.override(edited,link);
12339 		} else {
12340 			this.items.push(link);
12341 		}
12342 		this.build();
12343 		this.editForm.reset();
12344 		this.editWindow.hide();
12345 		this.editedLink = null;
12346 	},
12347 	valuesToLink : function(values) {
12348 		var link = {};
12349 		link.text = values.text;
12350 		if (values.email!='') {
12351 			link.kind='email';
12352 			link.value=values.email;
12353 			link.info=values.email;
12354 			link.icon='monochrome/email';
12355 		} else if (values.url!='') {
12356 			link.kind='url';
12357 			link.value=values.url;
12358 			link.info=values.url;
12359 			link.icon='monochrome/globe';
12360 		} else if (hui.isDefined(values.page)) {
12361 			link.kind='page';
12362 			link.value=values.page;
12363 			link.info=this.inputs['page'].getItem().title;
12364 			link.icon='common/page';
12365 		} else if (hui.isDefined(values.file)) {
12366 			link.kind='file';
12367 			link.value=values.file;
12368 			link.info=this.inputs['file'].getItem().title;
12369 			link.icon='monochrome/file';
12370 		}
12371 		return link;
12372 	},
12373 	changeType : function(type) {
12374 		hui.each(this.inputs,function(key,value) {
12375 			if (key!=type) {
12376 				value.setValue();
12377 			}
12378 		});
12379 	}
12380 }

12385 hui.ui.MarkupEditor = function(options) {
12386 	this.name = options.name;
12387 	this.options = hui.override({debug:false,value:'',autoHideToolbar:true,style:'font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 11px;'},options);
12388 	if (options.replace) {
12389 		options.replace = hui.get(options.replace);
12390 		options.element = hui.build('div',{className:'hui_markupeditor'});
12391 		options.replace.parentNode.insertBefore(options.element,options.replace);
12392 		options.replace.style.display='none';
12393 		options.value = options.replace.innerHTML;
12394 	}
12395 	this.ready = false;
12396 	this.pending = [];
12397 	this.element = hui.get(options.element);
12398 	if (hui.browser.msie) {
12399 		this.impl = hui.ui.MarkupEditor.MSIE;
12400 	} else {
12401 		this.impl = hui.ui.MarkupEditor.webkit;
12402 	}
12403 	this.impl.initialize({element:this.element,controller:this});
12404 	if (this.options.value) {
12405 		this.setValue(this.options.value);
12406 	}
12407 	hui.ui.extend(this);
12408 }

12423 		};

12434 	},

12438 	},

12441 	},

12451 	_whenReady : function(func) {

12453 			func();
12454 		} else {
12455 			this.pending.push(func);
12456 		}

12458 	_showBar : function() {
12459 		if (!this.bar) {
12460 			var things = [
12461 				{key:'bold',icon:'edit/text_bold'},
12462 				{key:'italic',icon:'edit/text_italic'},
12463 				{key:'color',icon:'common/color'},
12464 				/*{key:'image',icon:'common/image'},*/
12465 				{key:'addLink',icon:'common/link'},
12466 				{key:'align',value:'left',icon:'edit/text_align_left'},
12467 				{key:'align',value:'center',icon:'edit/text_align_center'},
12468 				{key:'align',value:'right',icon:'edit/text_align_right'},

12470 				{key:'clear',icon:'edit/clear'}/*,
12471 				{key:'strong',icon:'edit/text_bold'}*/
12472

12475 				{key:'insert-table',icon:'edit/text_italic'}*/
12476 			]

12495 		} else if (info.key=='addLink') {
12496 			this._showLinkEditor();
12497 		} else if (info.key=='align') {
12498 			this.impl.align(info.value);
12499 		} else if (info.key=='clear') {
12500 			this.impl.removeFormat();
12501 		} else {
12502 			this.impl.format(info);
12503 		}
12504 		this._valueChanged();

12506 	},

12560 /** @private */
12561 hui.ui.MarkupEditor.webkit = {
12562 	initialize : function(options) {
12563 		this.element = options.element;
12564 		this.element.style.overflow='auto';
12565 		this.element.contentEditable = true;
12566 		var ctrl = this.controller = options.controller;
12567 		hui.listen(this.element,'focus',function() {
12568 			ctrl.implFocused();
12569 		});
12570 		hui.listen(this.element,'blur',function() {
12571 			ctrl.implBlurred();
12572 		});
12573 		hui.listen(this.element,'keyup',this._keyUp.bind(this));
12574 		ctrl.implIsReady();
12575 	},
12576 	saveSelection : function() {
12577 		
12578 	},
12579 	restoreSelection : function(callback) {
12580 		if (callback) {callback()}
12581 	},
12582 	focus : function() {
12583 		this.element.focus();
12584 	},
12585 	format : function(info) {
12586 		if (info.key=='strong' || info.key=='em') {
12587 			this._wrapInTag(info.key);
12588 		} else if (info.key=='insert-table') {
12589 			this._insertHTML('<table><tbody><tr><td>Lorem ipsum dolor</td><td>Lorem ipsum dolor</td></tr></tbody></table>');
12590 		} else {
12591 			document.execCommand(info.key,null,info.value);
12592 		}
12593 	},
12594 	getOrCreateLink : function() {
12595 		var node = this._getSelectedNode();
12596 		if (node && node.tagName.toLowerCase()=='a') {
12597 			return node;
12598 		}
12599 		document.execCommand('createLink',null,'#');
12600 		return this._getSelectedNode();
12601 	},
12602 	_getSelectedNode : function() {
12603 		var selection = window.getSelection();
12604 		var range = selection.getRangeAt(0);
12605 		var ancestor = range.commonAncestorContainer;
12606 		if (!hui.dom.isElement(ancestor)) {
12607 			ancestor = ancestor.parentNode;
12608 		}
12609 		return ancestor;
12610 	},
12611 	colorize : function(color) {
12612 		document.execCommand('forecolor',null,color);
12613 	},
12614 	align : function(value) {
12615 		var x = {center:'justifycenter',justify:'justifyfull',left:'justifyleft',right:'justifyright'};
12616 		document.execCommand(x[value],null,null);
12617 	},
12618 	_keyUp : function() {
12619 		this.controller.implValueChanged();
12620 		this._selectionChanged();
12621 	},
12622 	_wrapInTag : function(tag) {
12623 		var selection = window.getSelection();
12624 		if (selection.rangeCount<1) {return}
12625 		var range = selection.getRangeAt(0);
12626 		var ancestor = range.commonAncestorContainer;
12627 		if (!hui.dom.isElement(ancestor)) {
12628 			ancestor = ancestor.parentNode;
12629 		}
12630 		if (ancestor.tagName.toLowerCase()==tag) {
12631 			this._unWrap(ancestor);
12632 		} else {
12633 			var node = document.createElement(tag);
12634 			range.surroundContents(node);
12635 			selection.selectAllChildren(node);
12636 		}
12637 		//document.execCommand('inserthtml',null,'<'+tag+'>'+hui.escape(hui.getSelectedText())+'</'+tag+'>');
12638 	},
12639 	_getInlineTag : function() {
12640 		var selection = window.getSelection();
12641 		if (selection.rangeCount<1) {return}
12642 		
12643 	},
12644 	_unWrap : function(node) {
12645 		var c = node.childNodes;
12646 		for (var i=0; i < c.length; i++) {
12647 			node.parentNode.insertBefore(c[i],node);
12648 		};
12649 		node.parentNode.removeChild(node);
12650 	},
12651 	_insertHTML : function(html) {
12652 		document.execCommand('inserthtml',null,html);
12653 	},
12654 	_selectionChanged : function() {
12655 		hui.log({
12656 			bold : document.queryCommandState('bold'),
12657 			italic : document.queryCommandState('italic')
12658 		});
12659 	},
12660 	removeFormat : function() {
12661 		document.execCommand('removeFormat',null,null);
12662 	},
12663 	setHTML : function(html) {
12664 		this.element.innerHTML = html;
12665 	},
12666 	getHTML : function() {
12667 		var cleaned = hui.ui.MarkupEditor.util.clean(this.element);
12668 		return cleaned.innerHTML;
12669 	}
12670 }

12672 /** @private */
12673 hui.ui.MarkupEditor.MSIE = {
12674 	initialize : function(options) {
12675 		this.element = options.element;
12676 		this.iframe = hui.build('iframe',{style:'display:block; width: 100%; border: 0;',parent:this.element})
12677 		hui.listen(this.iframe,'load',this._load.bind(this));
12678 		this.controller = options.controller;
12679 	},
12680 	saveSelection : function() {
12681 		this.savedRange = this.document.selection.createRange();
12682 		//this.savedSelection = this.document.selection.createRange().getBookmark();
12683 	},
12684 	restoreSelection : function(callback) {
12685 		window.setTimeout(function() {
12686 			this.body.focus();
12687 			this.savedRange.select();
12688 			if (callback) {callback()};
12689 		}.bind(this));
12690 	},
12691 	_load : function() {
12692 		this.document = hui.getFrameDocument(this.iframe);
12693 		this.body = this.document.body;
12694 		this.body.contentEditable = true;
12695 		hui.listen(this.body,'keyup',this._keyUp.bind(this));
12696 		hui.listen(this.body,'mouseup',this._mouseUp.bind(this));
12697 		this.controller.implIsReady();
12698 	},
12699 	_keyUp : function() {
12700 		this.controller.implValueChanged();

12709 	},

12712 		this.document.execCommand(x[value],null,null);
12713 	},

12717 		} else if (info.key=='insert-table') {

12719 		} else {

12721 		}
12722 	},

12745 /** @private */
12746 hui.ui.MarkupEditor.util = {
12747 	clean : function(node) {
12748 		var copy = node.cloneNode(true);
12749 		this.replaceNodes(copy,{b:'strong',i:'em',font:'span'});
12750 
12751 		var apples = hui.byClass(copy,'Apple-style-span');
12752 		for (var i = apples.length - 1; i >= 0; i--){
12753 			apples[i].removeAttribute('class');
12754 		};
12755 		this.convertAttributesToStyle(copy);
12756 		return copy;
12757 	},
12758 	replaceNodes : function(node,recipe) {
12759 		for (var key in recipe) {
12760 			var bs = node.getElementsByTagName(key);
12761 			for (var i = bs.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
12762 				var replacement = document.createElement(recipe[key]);
12763 				var color = bs[i].getAttribute('color');
12764 				if (color) {
12765 					replacement.style.color=color;
12766 				}
12767 				hui.dom.replaceNode(bs[i],replacement);
12768 			};
12769 		}
12770 	},
12771 	convertAttributesToStyle : function(node) {
12772 		var all = node.getElementsByTagName('*');
12773 		for (var i=0; i < all.length; i++) {
12774 			var n = all[i];
12775 			var align = n.getAttribute('align');
12776 			if (align) {
12777 				n.style.textAlign = align;
12778 				n.removeAttribute('align');
12779 			}
12780 		};
12781 	}
12782 }

12807 		c, hex, j;

12869 		hui.listen(this.wheel2,'mousemove',this._hoverWheel2.bind(this));
12870 		hui.listen(this.wheel2,'click',this._pickColor.bind(this));
12871 		hui.listen(this.wheel3,'mousemove',this._hoverWheel3.bind(this));

12875 		})

12882 	$click : function(button) {

12884 			i;
12885 		for (i = this.pages.length - 1; i >= 0; i--){

12887 		};

12889 			this.buttons[i].setSelected(this.buttons[i]==button);
12890 		};

12895 	//	return;

12897 		if (input) {input.focus()}
12898 	},
12899 	/** @private */
12900 	_pickColor : function(e) {
12901 		hui.stop(e);
12902 		this.fire('colorWasSelected',this.color);
12903 	},
12904 	_hoverColor : function(color) {
12905 		this.preview.style.background = color;
12906 		this.color = color;
12907 		this.fire('colorWasHovered',this.color);
12908 		this.input.value = color;
12909 	},
12910 	/** @private */
12911 	buildData : function() {
12912 		var addary = new Array();           //red
12913 		addary[0] = new Array(0,1,0);   //red green
12914 		addary[1] = new Array(-1,0,0);  //green
12915 		addary[2] = new Array(0,0,1);   //green blue
12916 		addary[3] = new Array(0,-1,0);  //blue
12917 		addary[4] = new Array(1,0,0);   //red blue
12918 		addary[5] = new Array(0,0,-1);  //red
12919 		addary[6] = new Array(255,1,1);
12920 		var clrary = new Array(360);
12921 		for(var i = 0; i < 6; i++) {
12922 			for(var j = 0; j < 60; j++) {
12923 				clrary[60 * i + j] = new Array(3);
12924 				for(var k = 0; k < 3; k++) {
12925 					clrary[60 * i + j][k] = addary[6][k];
12926 					addary[6][k] += (addary[i][k] * 4);
12927 				}
12928 			}
12929 		}
12930 		this.colorArray = clrary;
12931 	},
12932 	/** @private */
12933 	_hoverWheel1 : function(e) {
12934 		e = hui.event(e);
12935 		var pos = hui.getPosition(this.wheel1);
12936 		var x = 4 * (e.getLeft() - pos.left);
12937 		var y = 4 * (e.getTop() - pos.top);
12938 
12939 		var sx = x - 512;
12940 		var sy = y - 512;
12941 		var qx = (sx < 0)?0:1;
12942 		var qy = (sy < 0)?0:1;
12943 		var q = 2 * qy + qx;
12944 		var quad = new Array(-180,360,180,0);
12945 		var xa = Math.abs(sx);
12946 		var ya = Math.abs(sy);
12947 		var d = ya * 45 / xa;
12948 		if(ya > xa) {
12949 			 d = 90 - (xa * 45 / ya);
12950 		}
12951 		var deg = Math.floor(Math.abs(quad[q] - d));
12952 		sx = Math.abs(x - 512);
12953 		sy = Math.abs(y - 512);
12954 		var r = Math.sqrt((sx * sx) + (sy * sy));
12955 		if(x == 512 & y == 512) {
12956 			var c = "000000";
12957 		} else {
12958 			var n = 0;
12959 			for(var i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
12960 				var r2 = this.colorArray[deg][i] * r / 256;
12961 				if(r > 256) r2 += Math.floor(r - 256);
12962 				if(r2 > 255) r2 = 255;
12963 				n = 256 * n + Math.floor(r2);
12964 			}
12965 			c = n.toString(16);
12966 		}
12967 		while(c.length < 6) c = "0" + c;
12968 		this._hoverColor('#'+c);
12969 	},
12970 	_hoverWheel2 : function(e) {
12971 		var rgb,sat,val;
12972 		e = hui.event(e);
12973 		var pos = hui.getPosition(this.wheel2);
12974 		var x = (e.getLeft() - pos.left);
12975 		var y = (e.getTop() - pos.top);
12976 
12977 		if (y > 256) {return}
12978 
12979 	    var cartx = x - 128;
12980 	    var carty = 128 - y;
12981 	    var cartx2 = cartx * cartx;
12982 	    var carty2 = carty * carty;
12983 	    var rraw = Math.sqrt(cartx2 + carty2);       //raw radius
12984 	    var rnorm = rraw/128;                        //normalized radius
12985 	    if (rraw == 0) {
12986 			sat = 0;
12987 			val = 0;
12988 			rgb = new Array(0,0,0);
12989 		} else {
12990 			var arad = Math.acos(cartx/rraw);            //angle in radians 
12991 			var aradc = (carty>=0)?arad:2*Math.PI - arad;  //correct below axis
12992 			var adeg = 360 * aradc/(2*Math.PI);  //convert to degrees
12993 			if (rnorm > 1) {    // outside circle
12994 				rgb = new Array(255,255,255);
12995 				sat = 1;
12996 				val = 1;            
12997 			} else if (rnorm >= .5) {
12998 				sat = 1 - ((rnorm - .5) *2);
12999 				val = 1;
13000 				rgb = hui.Color.hsv2rgb(adeg,sat,val);
13001 			} else {
13002 				sat = 1;
13003 				val = rnorm * 2;
13004 				rgb = hui.Color.hsv2rgb(adeg,sat,val);
13005 			}
13006 		}
13007 		this._hoverColor(hui.Color.rgb2hex(rgb));
13008 	},
13009 	_hoverWheel3 : function(e) {
13010 		var rgb,sat,val;
13011 		e = hui.event(e);
13012 		var pos = hui.getPosition(this.wheel3);
13013 		var x = (e.getLeft() - pos.left);
13014 		var y = (e.getTop() - pos.top);
13015 
13016 		if (y > 256) {return}
13017 
13018 	    var cartx = x - 128;
13019 	    var carty = 128 - y;
13020 	    var cartx2 = cartx * cartx;
13021 	    var carty2 = carty * carty;
13022 	    var rraw = Math.sqrt(cartx2 + carty2);       //raw radius
13023 	    var rnorm = rraw/128;                        //normalized radius
13024 	    if (rraw == 0) {
13025 			sat = 0;
13026 			val = 0;
13027 			rgb = new Array(0,0,0);
13028 		} else {
13029 			var arad = Math.acos(cartx/rraw);            //angle in radians 
13030 			var aradc = (carty>=0) ? arad : 2*Math.PI - arad;  //correct below axis
13031 			var adeg = 360 * aradc/(2*Math.PI);  //convert to degrees
13032 			if (rnorm > 1) {    // outside circle
13033 				rgb = new Array(255,255,255);
13034 				sat = 1;
13035 				val = 1;            
13036 			} else {
13037 				sat = rnorm;// - ((rnorm - .5) *2);
13038 				val = 1;
13039 				rgb = hui.Color.hsv2rgb(adeg,sat,val);
13040 			}
13041 		}
13042 		this._hoverColor(hui.Color.rgb2hex(rgb));
13043 	}
13044 }

13149 hui.ui.StyleLength.prototype = {
13150 	/** @private */
13151 	addBehavior : function() {
13152 		var e = this.element;
13153 		hui.listen(this.input,'focus',function() {hui.addClass(e,'hui_number_focused')});
13154 		hui.listen(this.input,'blur',this.blurEvent.bind(this));
13155 		hui.listen(this.input,'keyup',this.keyEvent.bind(this));
13156 		hui.listen(this.up,'mousedown',this.upEvent.bind(this));
13157 		hui.listen(this.down,'mousedown',this.downEvent.bind(this));
13158 	},
13159 	/** @private */
13160 	parseValue : function(value) {
13161 		var num = parseFloat(value,10);
13162 		if (isNaN(num)) {
13163 			return null;
13164 		}
13165 		var parsed = {number: num, unit:this.options.defaultUnit};
13166 		for (var i=0; i < this.options.units.length; i++) {
13167 			var unit = this.options.units[i];
13168 			if (value.indexOf(unit)!=-1) {
13169 				parsed.unit = unit;
13170 				break;
13171 			}
13172 		};
13173 		parsed.number = Math.max(this.options.min,Math.min(this.options.max,parsed.number));
13174 		return parsed;
13175 	},
13176 	/** @private */
13177 	blurEvent : function() {
13178 		hui.removeClass(this.element,'hui_number_focused');
13179 		this.updateInput();
13180 	},
13181 	/** @private */
13182 	keyEvent : function(e) {
13183 		e = e || window.event;
13184 		if (e.keyCode==hui.KEY_UP) {
13185 			hui.stop(e);
13186 			this.upEvent();
13187 		} else if (e.keyCode==hui.KEY_DOWN) {
13188 			this.downEvent();
13189 		} else {
13190 			this.checkAndSetValue(this.parseValue(this.input.value));
13191 		}
13192 	},
13193 	/** @private */
13194 	updateInput : function() {
13195 		this.input.value = this.getValue();
13196 	},
13197 	/** @private */
13198 	checkAndSetValue : function(value) {
13199 		var old = this.value;
13200 		var changed = false;
13201 		if (old===null && value===null) {
13202 			// nothing
13203 		} else if (old!=null && value!=null && old.number===value.number && old.unit===value.unit) {
13204 			// nothing
13205 		} else {
13206 			changed = true;
13207 		}
13208 		this.value = value;
13209 		if (changed) {
13210 			this.fire('valueChanged',this.getValue());
13211 		}
13212 	},
13213 	/** @private */
13214 	downEvent : function() {
13215 		if (this.value) {
13216 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:Math.max(this.options.min,this.value.number-1),unit:this.value.unit});
13217 		} else {
13218 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:this.options.min,unit:this.options.defaultUnit});
13219 		}
13220 		this.updateInput();
13221 	},
13222 	/** @private */
13223 	upEvent : function() {
13224 		if (this.value) {
13225 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:Math.min(this.options.max,this.value.number+1),unit:this.value.unit});
13226 		} else {
13227 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:this.options.min+1,unit:this.options.defaultUnit});
13228 		}
13229 		this.updateInput();
13230 	},
13231 	
13232 	// Public
13233 	
13234 	getValue : function() {
13235 		return this.value ? this.value.number+this.value.unit : '';
13236 	},
13237 	setValue : function(value) {
13238 		this.value = this.parseValue(value);
13239 		this.updateInput();
13240 	}
13241 }
